context:
{
  "id": "line:06cd813",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "In the kingdom of Wyverngarde,[p/] there was a gulf between what was lawful and what was just."
}

{
  "id": "line:0918dd0",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Artificery ran in the houses of the aristocrats.[p/] Disease and vermin ran through the homes of the commonfolk."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f73df",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "People suffered,[p/] people died,[p/] all so the mages of the nobility could keep their plates full and their lives comfortable."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ba2b4",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Nevertheless,[p/] they still wanted us to have the illusion of hope."
}

{
  "id": "line:081064e",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "They challenged us to win,[p/] leaving out the fact that they were the ones setting the rules."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c6b73",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Many just threw up their hands,[p/] and no one could blame them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0121235",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "You could never lose if you never played."
}

{
  "id": "line:0702bdb",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Rhys: I was transporting a client in my carriage that evening."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a1199",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Rhys: We were driving by the McCoy Tavern when we heard a disturbance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a002df",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Rhys: Worried that something was amiss,[p/] I walked into the establishment to see what the commotion was about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0034cf6",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Rhys: That was when I saw the defendant,[p/] lit by the blue glow of the dining room lights![p/] She had stabbed Flinhart,[p/][s/] and her sword was shining with magical energy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0791990",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Tyrion: Mr. Rudolf,[p/] you testified that you saw my client murdering the victim,[p/] and you supposedly saw her casting magic while doing so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f396cc",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Rhys: Yes...[p/] I could never forget it.[p/] It was burned into my memory."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbdbe5",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Tyrion: I see...[p/] It’s funny that you say that."
}

{
  "id": "line:04afd67",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Rhys: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:064042b",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Tyrion: Because your entire testimony was a complete lie!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0165b",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Rhys: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04df7ab",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "AriaC: What are you trying to imply, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09fb479",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind,[p/] think about the state of the crime scene!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c3b09",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Tyrion: The witness couldn’t have seen [i]anything[/i],[p/] much less a homicide!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0808531",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Maybe their rules and institutions [i]were[/i] impossible."
}

{
  "id": "line:05cef68",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Maybe I was just a grain of sand trying to stand against an ocean."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3244b",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "But I would never stop rising—[p/]no matter how many times they tried to drown me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0817a67",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "I would do it again and again if it I meant that I could give hope to even one person."
}

{
  "id": "line:018aa46",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "[i]That[/i] was why I fought."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a3e8f",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "Sweat was soaking through my suit.[p/] The air of the countryside was choking me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6d1d6",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "I fumbled with the leather reins,[p/] tugging at them tightly."
}

{
  "id": "line:06df60b",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "Horse: Where'd this idiot learn how to drive!?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f18410",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "Animals were funny like that.[p/] You'd never know it,[p/] but they were constantly making their objections known."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7daaf",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "I'd caught many complaints like that through my Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c66f6",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "Ruby: Cuthbert, keep the carriage steady."
}

{
  "id": "line:022f5ae",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "Tyrion: Y-[p/][s/]Yes, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:081c2ff",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "My mentor barely looked up from her Runestone.[p/] She was staring at some magical projections—[p/]probably some court files from a case she was working on."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e105d",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "I stared longer than I should have.[p/] I'd just passed the legal certification exam,[p/] which only meant that a Runestone of my own was coming my way."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cdbbf",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "I just had to prove myself,[p/] and this trip was the perfect opportunity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d27cd8",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "Dissidence was brewing in the countryside,[p/] and we were on our way to meet with one of the voices of the revolution."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b46b82",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "The village we were driving to was nearly at the edge of the eastern border,[p/] far from the capital city in the kingdom's center."
}

{
  "id": "line:020826a",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "Here,[p/] we ran the risk of running into the military forces deployed to silence voices like his."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c967d",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "Whoever this \"Flinhart McCoy\" was,[p/] Ms. Tymora’s business with him must've been worth all this trouble."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8ecd9",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "Tyrion: M-[p/][s/]Ms. Tymora,[p/] maybe you should switch with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:018de93",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "Ruby: And what would you learn if I did that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:065ea94",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "...Maybe I [i]was[/i] worried about nothing.[p/] Practical experience was always a key part of learning whenever she was involved."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d0865",
  "node": "Carriage",
  "text": "Why else would she quietly sit there,[p/] immersed in her court files?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07154d9",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "Child: Agh!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0198104",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "...Did that rock just scream out in pain?"
}

{
  "id": "line:011075b",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "I grabbed the reins and pulled them with everything I had.[p/] The horses slowed to a stop."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d7049",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "The child was lying face down in the dirt.[p/] A puddle of red was pooling under her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a92f71",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "Tyrion: Scaled Lord..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cea711",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "I wasn't sure what to do.[p/] I wished I'd never procrastinated reading those first-aid books."
}

{
  "id": "line:03fce9a",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "I looked to my mentor.[p/] She'd approached the scene quietly and slowly."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b1eb6",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "Her eyes went to the child,[p/] then to the surrounding forest.[p/] She seemed to be searching for something."
}

{
  "id": "line:078675d",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "She was wearing the same expression she used when inspecting a crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:00799e3",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Why would a kid be out in the middle of nowhere?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa3748",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Ms. Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:028eaff",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "Ruby: I say we keep driving and never speak of this again."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fe8ab",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora![p/][s/] She’s just a child!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce6984",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "Child: Oh...[p/] The pain... [p/]I can see the light... [h=\"Where the hell is he?|That was his cue.\" e=\"h\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:08df977",
  "node": "HitChild",
  "text": "...I caught a puzzling thought through my Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:002f86d",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "Late to his cue,[p/] a man clad in plate armor leaped out of some nearby bushes and stumbled towards us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6c7bf",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "He planted his feet firmly on the ground in front of us,[p/] puffing out his chest."
}

{
  "id": "line:065999d",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "Knight: By the Scaled Lord![p/][s/] Look what you’ve done!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a41c2a",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "Child: T-[s/][p/]The Scaled Lord...?[p/] I think I can see him."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ea7cb",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "Child: My family—[p/]who all died of the plague in 589—[p/]they're also there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b236e9",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "...Her lines were historically accurate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0339be8",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "Knight: ... [h=\"Damn it, Alma.|Mentioning that plague is overkill...\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e05748",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "Knight: ...This poor child![p/][s/] She’s [i]dead[/i] because of you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f75690",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "Knight: This is a serious crime![p/][s/] The fine is 10[p/]—no,[p/][s/] [i]20[/i] gold pieces! [h=\"Look at that carriage.|They’re probably aristocrats visiting House Pierce.\" e=\"h\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5866f",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "20 gold pieces?[p/] The average sentence for vehicular manslaughter was two years of imprisonment."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f0026",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "Knight: I’ll have no choice but to arrest you unless you can pay this fine!"
}

{
  "id": "line:078808e",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "Ruby: Oh,[p/] [i]that's[/i] what this is..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af98a8",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "I side-eyed the child—[p/]apparently named Alma.[p/] I spotted tiny tomato seeds in her pool of blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f93f1",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You might want to call someone to retrieve Alma’s body then."
}

{
  "id": "line:031612d",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "Her eyes opened,[p/] and her head whipped up to look at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6c79f",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "We locked eyes for a second before her head fell back to the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0835c76",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "I looked to my mentor again,[p/] but she just leaned her head and gestured towards the two con artists."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a9a9d",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "It appeared that I was being given another learning opportunity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfe703",
  "node": "TheScam",
  "text": "I couldn't complain, though.[p/] I didn’t appreciate being treated like an easy mark."
}

{
  "id": "line:051cf71",
  "node": "Tutorial_Argument",
  "text": "Knight: A-[p/][s/]Anyways, what will it be?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:067f963",
  "node": "Tutorial_Argument",
  "text": "Knight: Will you pay your fine,[p/] or do we need to sort this out at the barracks?"
}

{
  "id": "line:007a2eb",
  "node": "TutElocution",
  "text": "Negotiate [c=\"This was obviously just an accident. Can’t you overlook this?\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:01cce46",
  "node": "TutElocution",
  "text": "Tyrion: This was obviously just an accident.[p/] Can’t you look the other way?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04da264",
  "node": "TutElocution",
  "text": "Knight: Are you insane?![p/][s/] You want me to spit on my [i]honor[/i] as a knight?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09f4ef9",
  "node": "TutElocution",
  "text": "Ruby: ...What are you doing, Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1b575",
  "node": "TutElocution",
  "text": "Tyrion: They clearly worked very hard on this.[p/] I thought it would be rude not to play along."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cbbf9",
  "node": "TutElocution",
  "text": "Ruby: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3ff99",
  "node": "TutElocution",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b5bca",
  "node": "TutElocution",
  "text": "Comply [c=\"Okay, I guess we can spare that much gold.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d78bb7",
  "node": "TutElocution",
  "text": "Tyrion: Okay,[p/] I guess we can spare that much gold."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5255d",
  "node": "TutElocution",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Cuthbert,[p/] what are you doing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05cf313",
  "node": "TutElocution",
  "text": "Tyrion: I just thought arguing with them would be more trouble than it’s worth."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d89fc",
  "node": "TutElocution",
  "text": "Call [c=\"Certainly, why don’t you bring us back to your \\\"barracks\\\"?\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:035cebe",
  "node": "TutElocution2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Certainly,[p/] why don’t you bring us back to your \"barracks\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:043533c",
  "node": "TutElocution2",
  "text": "Knight: What—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:074c268",
  "node": "TutElocution2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But it [i]is[/i] strange that you’d bring us to your barracks instead of the dungeons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e742c9",
  "node": "TutElocution2",
  "text": "Knight: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/][s/] Uh—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ead17c",
  "node": "TutElocution2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You’ll also probably want to call your unit to escort us."
}

{
  "id": "line:03db8f0",
  "node": "TutElocution2",
  "text": "Tyrion: After all,[p/] it'd be dangerous for one knight to transport two \"criminals\" by himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:03929bc",
  "node": "TutElocution2",
  "text": "Knight: S-[p/][s/]Shut up![p/][s/] Don't think you can talk your way out of this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:019b0ca",
  "node": "TutElocution2",
  "text": "Knight: Are you seriously going to make me take you in?![p/][s/] Just pay the damned fine!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7e9d9",
  "node": "TutEvidence",
  "text": "Vehicular Manslaughter"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a2f4a",
  "node": "TutEvidence",
  "text": "Tyrion"
}

{
  "id": "line:0562682",
  "node": "TutEvidence",
  "text": "Knight: ...Who is this?[p/] This is you, isn’t it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09035f1",
  "node": "TutEvidence",
  "text": "Tyrion: It sure is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb8ac5",
  "node": "TutEvidence",
  "text": "Knight: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:010d243",
  "node": "TutEvidence",
  "text": "Tyrion: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:026dad1",
  "node": "TutEvidence",
  "text": "Ruby"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e5062",
  "node": "TutEvidence",
  "text": "Knight: ...Who is this?[p/] Isn’t this the lady standing beside you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9f979",
  "node": "TutEvidence2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Except a \"crime\" like this wouldn’t involve a fine at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:017f738",
  "node": "TutEvidence2",
  "text": "Knight: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:004cd30",
  "node": "TutEvidence2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Vehicular manslaughter has an average sentence of two years of imprisonment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccf255",
  "node": "TutEvidence2",
  "text": "Tyrion: With the death of a child, though,[p/] I could see the Crown pushing for more than that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0257af0",
  "node": "TutEvidence2",
  "text": "Knight: ...Who the hell are you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f9c4f",
  "node": "TutEvidence2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’m a defense attorney.[p/] I could recite every one of the kingdom's laws back to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fcad9",
  "node": "TutEvidence2",
  "text": "The \"knight\" looked nervously between Ms. Tymora and me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e06111",
  "node": "TutEvidence2",
  "text": "Knight: ...That’s it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0120d12",
  "node": "TutEvidence2",
  "text": "His hand shot to the rusty sword hanging from his side."
}

{
  "id": "line:0746d3a",
  "node": "TutEvidence2",
  "text": "He fumbled with it for a bit before pulling it out and waving it at us."
}

{
  "id": "line:089269d",
  "node": "TutEvidence2",
  "text": "I took a step back.[p/] My mentor put herself in front of me."
}

{
  "id": "line:06209f5",
  "node": "TutEvidence2",
  "text": "Knight: Enough talk![p/][s/] Give us the gold,[p/] and I won't have to hurt either of you! [h=\"Come on! Give up!|I can’t move that well in this fake armor...\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb926e",
  "node": "TutInterpret",
  "text": "Logic"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b37463",
  "node": "TutInterpret",
  "text": "Intuition"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e9a0e",
  "node": "TutInterpret",
  "text": "Empathy"
}

{
  "id": "line:03357d3",
  "node": "TutInterpretFail",
  "text": "Tyrion: What you’re saying doesn’t match what you’re thinking."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d51586",
  "node": "TutInterpretFail",
  "text": "Knight: What am I \"thinking\"?[p/] What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0141680",
  "node": "TutInterpretFail",
  "text": "Ruby: Cuthbert,[p/] now is not the time to bluff!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ecfa6",
  "node": "TutInterpretFail",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh, [p/][s/]uh—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0edf220",
  "node": "TutInterpretFail",
  "text": "[i]He[/i] was the one that was bluffing.[p/] I just needed to call him out on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:074e46c",
  "node": "ConArgumentWon",
  "text": "I stared at his plate armor.[p/] On a closer look,[p/] it seemed to be varnished wood,[p/] painted to give off a metallic sheen."
}

{
  "id": "line:013731a",
  "node": "ConArgumentWon",
  "text": "I reached past his sword and knocked on his breastplate.[p/] It let out a hollow thunk instead of a resonant clang."
}

{
  "id": "line:0492877",
  "node": "ConArgumentWon",
  "text": "Knight: Uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0217f84",
  "node": "ConArgumentWon",
  "text": "Tyrion: I didn’t know the kingdom was cutting back.[p/] Would this even protect you in a fight?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c13133",
  "node": "ConArgumentWon",
  "text": "Knight: A-[p/][s/]Are you threatening me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0acf969",
  "node": "ConArgumentWon",
  "text": "Tyrion: With litigation, perhaps."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a8987",
  "node": "ConArgumentWon",
  "text": "Knight: I-[p/][s/]I have a sword!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0b0e5",
  "node": "ConArgumentWon",
  "text": "Tyrion: You won't use it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6d4fb",
  "node": "ConArgumentWon",
  "text": "Knight: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:00cf16b",
  "node": "ConArgumentWon",
  "text": "Tyrion: Look...[p/] Let's just cut the charade.[p/] It's not happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:00071f6",
  "node": "ConArgumentWon",
  "text": "Alma rose from the dead and began wiping the rotten, crushed tomatoes off her shirt."
}

{
  "id": "line:022347a",
  "node": "ConArgumentWon",
  "text": "Child: Sorry,[p/] I thought that stuff about the plague would help... [h=\"I'm tired of eating porridge...\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bd545",
  "node": "ConArgumentWon",
  "text": "Knight: Don’t worry about it...[p/] It’s still morning.[p/] Someone else will come by."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b5c03",
  "node": "ConArgumentWon",
  "text": "Child: The road’s been empty for days.[p/] What if they’re the only ones?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01a5074",
  "node": "KingExpo",
  "text": ":The Kingdom of Wyverngarde:[p/] established 613 years ago by the seven high archmages—[p/]ruled by King Olivier and the mages of his nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5568b",
  "node": "KingExpo",
  "text": "They'll often preach that our large kingdom was a land of prosperity and happiness—[p/]a nation where its people shared the wealth and succor created by its magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe1ca1",
  "node": "KingExpo",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0742e3f",
  "node": "KingExpo",
  "text": "I took out a neatly wrapped sandwich from my satchel and held it out to Alma."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9e5f1",
  "node": "KingExpo",
  "text": "Child: W-[p/]What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c788c8",
  "node": "KingExpo",
  "text": "Tyrion: You’ll probably find this more filling than porridge."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1b947",
  "node": "KingExpo",
  "text": "The man narrowed his eyes,[p/] appraising me like the knight he'd been impersonating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0070f54",
  "node": "KingExpo",
  "text": "He snatched the wrapped sandwich from me,[p/] peeling back the bread to inspect its contents."
}

{
  "id": "line:06980d0",
  "node": "KingExpo",
  "text": "His mouth salivated as he caught a whiff of the sliced deli meat."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b73c1",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "No poison to be found, apparently.[p/] He handed it to Alma,[p/] who eagerly began munching down on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d5de0",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "I was probably the first person to share [i]any[/i] \"wealth or succor\" with them in a long time."
}

{
  "id": "line:01840c2",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "Knight: ...Just tell me one thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0daf88e",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "Knight: What gave it away?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07aec21",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What do you mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0688392",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "Knight: I spent a while sanding this armor down.[p/] I had to go through three attempts just to get it perfectly smooth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7306d",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "Knight: I even mixed the paint myself.[p/] It's got the sheen and everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d6361",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "Knight: How'd you know it was fake?"
}

{
  "id": "line:055150d",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "I thought to myself for a while."
}

{
  "id": "line:004841e",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You clearly went for woad,[p/] madder,[p/] and weld for your paint.[p/] I'm also guessing you used a touch of gall ink for the shadows?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bba4b9",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "Tyrion: They're decent choices if you’re trying to paint a shield,[p/] but they're useless if you’re trying to mimic the complex nooks and edges of plate armor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab72d1",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "He just blinked at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:06449bc",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "Knight: ...Seriously?"
}

{
  "id": "line:092a2e6",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Plate doesn’t tint that way.[p/] Real plate catches the ambient light in cold tones."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba71f6",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your mix was a little too warm."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f19f3",
  "node": "KingExpo2",
  "text": "He shook his head,[p/] wide-eyed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0051ba7",
  "node": "KingExpo3",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Cuthbert,[p/] was that stuff about the paint really true?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecf3f9",
  "node": "KingExpo3",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]*chuckle*[/i][p/] No,[p/] I just read it from his mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:088b4a6",
  "node": "KingExpo3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you see the look on his face?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03fd57a",
  "node": "KingExpo3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I kind of understand why my mom enjoyed fortune-telling so much."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fbd29",
  "node": "KingExpo3",
  "text": "She said nothing in response.[p/] Her eyes were locked on my satchel,[p/] now one meal short."
}

{
  "id": "line:088185f",
  "node": "KingExpo3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I’ll be fine.[p/] They've probably skipped a lot more meals than I have."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ea4d7",
  "node": "KingExpo3",
  "text": "Ruby: In case you’ve forgotten,[p/] they were trying to scam us."
}

{
  "id": "line:019075f",
  "node": "KingExpo3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...If they really wanted to hurt anyone,[p/] they'd throw away that fake armor and just use the sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fbefb",
  "node": "KingExpo3",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should be helping our fellow commoners, right?[p/] Isn't that why we practice law?"
}

{
  "id": "line:015f9df",
  "node": "KingExpo3",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Just don’t expect me to share my lunch with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0baa167",
  "node": "KingExpo3",
  "text": "Ruby: I spent a good fifteen minutes haggling for those sandwiches."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f40c2f",
  "node": "KingExpo3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do we even [i]need[/i] to haggle?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad5ba3",
  "node": "KingExpo3",
  "text": "Ruby: It's a matter of principle.[p/] You give anyone an inch,[p/] and they'll take a mile."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb50e2",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "We arrived at Kornhaven,[p/] but I smelled the stench before I even spotted the village."
}

{
  "id": "line:0676f30",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "The smell of rotting meat and excrement hung in the air.[p/] I had to fight the urge to retch."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a7030",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "But I did my best to swallow my disgust.[p/] I'd been begging Ms. Tymora to take me on her outings for years.[p/] I couldn't show weakness now."
}

{
  "id": "line:057b063",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06185a7",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm fine.[p/] I was just...[p/] surprised."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad2ba6",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "Ruby: Did you expect the ruling lord to install modern plumbing in a village like this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0987023",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I guess I never really thought about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bdc6c",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "Ruby: You'll get used to it once you've traveled more."
}

{
  "id": "line:092054a",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "Ruby: This is just how things are in the outer regions."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ef5ae",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "It really made me appreciate the clean and sanitary streets of the capital."
}

{
  "id": "line:0094189",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "There,[p/] the streets and homes were loaded with artificery."
}

{
  "id": "line:014d118",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "We had clean and running water.[p/] We had lights that didn't rely on oil and flame."
}

{
  "id": "line:016c037",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "It was as if this village existed in a different time period."
}

{
  "id": "line:026d7e5",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "...I reprimanded myself.[p/] I wasn't above this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4507e",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "The people here were commoners,[p/] just like me.[p/] They only lived like this out of a lack of care from the kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:06edda2",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Take a left here.[p/] The tavern should be at the edge of town."
}

{
  "id": "line:0610ccf",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "Ruby: If the reports are right,[p/] this should be the place."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b79ba",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is this really a meeting place for \"dissidents against the Crown\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9bc49",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern",
  "text": "Flinhart had done an amazing job of disguising their headquarters as a rundown shack."
}

{
  "id": "line:08acbfe",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "Ruby: The tavern’s been shut down for a few years."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdfcb2",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "Ruby: Nowadays,[p/] Flinhart McCoy just uses it to host his rallies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0230690",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "Flinhart: Hey![p/][s/] You lot![p/][s/] The McCoy Tavern is closed!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4c54d",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "The dissident leader stormed towards our carriage as we parked."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e5aad",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "He had a roughness to him that matched the state of his tavern.[p/] He was practically growling at us with every word."
}

{
  "id": "line:029ab55",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "He got close to Ms. Tymora’s face,[p/] his feet firmly planted on the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbb697",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "She was unflinching, of course,[p/] standing her ground as he leered at the two of us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d54580",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...I take it you’re Flinhart McCoy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0799beb",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "Flinhart: ...What’s it to [i]you[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1f12f",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "Ruby: Sorry for not writing ahead of time,[p/] but my messages weren’t getting through."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b2d26",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "Ruby: I’m Ruby Tymora.[p/] I’ve been trying to get in touch with you, Flinhart."
}

{
  "id": "line:05289b3",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "Flinhart: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c8f06",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "His eyes narrowed for a bit before widening in recognition of the name."
}

{
  "id": "line:0195732",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "Flinhart: Wait...[p/][s/] Ruby [i]Tymora[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7b969",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "Flinhart: Why didn’t you say so?![p/][s/] Come on in!"
}

{
  "id": "line:019333c",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "His tone flipped to jovial in an instant.[p/] Now it was as if he were greeting an old friend."
}

{
  "id": "line:0543588",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "I was surprised people out here even knew who she was.[p/] I'd have thought her infamy had only spread in the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:09102a0",
  "node": "ArriveAtTavern2",
  "text": "I guess he acknowledged her as an ally.[p/] They both had a common enemy, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c9959",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "Flinhart: Excuse the mess.[p/] We haven't exactly seen a lot of guests."
}

{
  "id": "line:0311d3e",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "Ruby: ...It's fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d464f",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "My mentor looked around warily as she brushed aside a spider web hanging in front of her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6a9d0",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "Flinhart: So what brings you here?[p/] I doubt someone like you has anything to see out here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edafa9",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "Ruby: One of my clients has been trying to talk to you.[p/] We have a proposition that you’ll be interested in."
}

{
  "id": "line:073165d",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "I raised my eyebrow at her.[p/] This was the first time I'd heard of this \"client\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdfe4b",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Is there anywhere where we could talk in private?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f731d",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "Flinhart: I've got a bunch of empty rooms upstairs."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b0462",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "Ruby: Perfect.[p/] Cuthbert,[p/] stay here for a moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:078fcf1",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Don't you need my help?"
}

{
  "id": "line:061407a",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "Ruby: There’s no need for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea5458",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "How was there no need?[p/] The Eye of Horus could extract anything she needed from him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aeb22b",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "That glare overruled my objection before I could get it out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa8024",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "Without another word,[p/] they went up the stairs."
}

{
  "id": "line:000e51e",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "I drummed my hands on the dusty table,[p/] looking around the tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:0694030",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "It definitely had a lot of[p/] personality—[p/]if one counted dust and insects as character traits."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df5ef1",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "Faint murmurs echoed from the ceiling,[p/] slightly stressed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c84a51",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "It sounded like their conversation was becoming more frustrated."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c1582",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "I brought out a small chessboard from my satchel.[p/] Even after a decade,[p/] it had served me well."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e050e",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "Chess could be played with one person—[p/]something that I’d always taken advantage of."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5cf10",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "I had a match with the Duke of Commerce scheduled in a few months."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7e625",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "I wasn't too worried about him,[p/] but I might as well take this opportunity."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ed437",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "Tyrion: Checkmate."
}

{
  "id": "line:049eb3c",
  "node": "EnterTavern",
  "text": "I lost again while playing as white.[p/] That was three times now."
}

{
  "id": "line:026d824",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh...[p/] Hello!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc6bfb",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Statistically,[p/] white was more likely to win.[p/] So why was I performing better as black?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccb282",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Celeste: Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb79e6",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Was I becoming overconfident as white because it had an advantage?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f06ce",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Celeste: Hello?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00da4a9",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "That very advantage could be affecting my choices and making me play suboptimally..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0601af5",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "If a personal quirk was making me play like this,[p/] then I needed to identify and correct it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dddb01",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0547376",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Tyrion: A-[p/][s/]Ah!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a5c7c",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "I nearly toppled out of my seat when she tapped me on the shoulder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac75f9",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "She stepped back and flashed me a soft grin.[p/] Her body swayed playfully,[p/] amused by how flustered I was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4222e",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Her posture was unguarded.[p/] It was as if she'd never felt threatened in her life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e04d08",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "She was holding a large exotic sword in her right hand,[p/] but I barely even noticed it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aff033",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "As her warm and bright aura washed over me,[p/] it pulled away any tension and unease I might have felt."
}

{
  "id": "line:026c701",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Sorry...[p/] I was distracted..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fee78f",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Celeste: You know the McCoy Tavern is closed, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fea6f3",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Celeste: But if you’re okay with keeping things off the books,[p/] I can prepare a room for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:042b9a5",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/]No...[p/] That's fine.[p/] I’m just waiting for my mentor to finish speaking with Flinhart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0740506",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh,[p/] someone’s talking to my dad?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f4793",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Your dad?"
}

{
  "id": "line:017c772",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm Flinhart’s daughter:[p/] Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc7afa",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I'm Tyrion.[p/] Nice to meet you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8098e",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you know when they’ll be done?[p/] I wanted to show him something."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ba9e7",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "The mumbling upstairs was becoming more frustrated."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b01701",
  "node": "CelesteAppears",
  "text": "Celeste tilted her head as she looked at the ceiling,[p/] but she soon got distracted by my chessboard."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c85a78",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] This game is chess, isn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:050e8ea",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you playing against someone?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e18ba5",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh,[p/] I was playing by myself, actually..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4ed1e",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de944a",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Playing alone helps me hone my strategies.[p/] Plenty of professionals do it."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b4e2e",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey,[p/] don’t worry about it.[p/] I’m not the type to shame a man for playing with himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:035602a",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7d598",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "She just chuckled as she drank in my reaction."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3c46c",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "I looked away from her before clearing my throat."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c3e38",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Have you ever played it before?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0019250",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "Celeste: I’ve read about it in some books a while ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2c09a",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] This room is always so dusty..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f8a7b",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "Inviting herself,[p/] she sat down on the chair opposite mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:009f623",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "She brushed off some dust from the table with her sleeve,[p/] and began setting up her side of the board."
}

{
  "id": "line:0539bd0",
  "node": "CelesteNotice",
  "text": "Celeste: Where does the horse go again...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a3962",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Checkmate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc4eba",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "It only took two moves...[p/] She'd fallen into a classic trap."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a3eb5",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "I felt a little guilty,[p/] but my mentor always said that failure was the best teacher."
}

{
  "id": "line:07023a7",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Wait, what?![p/][s/] Already?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0546f25",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Celeste: How did you do that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b51e02",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "I decided against telling her the name of that mate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff11e8",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "She just grumbled under her breath as we both moved our pieces back into place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0185a1d",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Celeste: So...[p/] What kind of business does your mentor have with my dad?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04be2e1",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm honestly not sure.[p/] She doesn't really tell me much."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d2df2",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think it has something to do with his dissidents against the Crown."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f5e1a",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Celeste: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:063156a",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Sorry,[p/] should I not be saying that out loud?"
}

{
  "id": "line:063e11e",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Celeste: ...It's fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:03223ca",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "She stroked her chin as her hand moved and hesitated over each of her pieces."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a5d29",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "...She hadn’t realized that she'd been led into another trap."
}

{
  "id": "line:024626c",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:091089b",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "She moved her knight into position to attack my queen.[p/] She’d blocked my initial assault on her king,[p/] but..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6ac56",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "A Scholar's Mate this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcbbbe",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Celeste: What?![p/][s/] How do you keep doing that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e8f50",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Tyrion: The more you play,[p/] the more you'll be able to recognize specific boards."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8ede3",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Tyrion: You'll get the hang of it in time."
}

{
  "id": "line:075df2b",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "She just glared at the board."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af0e4d",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "I glanced at the ceiling.[p/] Ms. Tymora and Flinhart's argument was only getting worse."
}

{
  "id": "line:07715cf",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "It didn’t sound like they would be done anytime soon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc4c95",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Celeste: I figured out what the problem is!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c889b",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is it that you keep mobilizing your pieces without intention?"
}

{
  "id": "line:063b1fa",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Celeste: It’s food, Tyrion![p/][s/] I need food!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02534b1",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "She stood up and stomped towards the kitchen,[p/] but not before spinning around back to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c26f5",
  "node": "CelesteGame",
  "text": "Celeste: We’re not done![p/][s/] Don’t you dare leave!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf1c77",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "A few minutes later,[p/] she returned carrying a gigantic slab of cooked meat on a small plate."
}

{
  "id": "line:038c382",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "I stared at it for a while,[p/] wondering if she was planning to eat all of that in one sitting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0206935",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "She began setting up her side of the board with one hand while holding a fork [i]and[/i] knife in the other."
}

{
  "id": "line:0050e30",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "She was somehow twirling both utensils in her right hand to switch between them."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b78b8",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "She delicately carved a small bit of meat with the knife before spinning to a fork to bring it to her mouth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0623c44",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "She tilted her head at me and swallowed the bite whole."
}

{
  "id": "line:037e5e6",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Hey, it's your move."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e73ac2",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0faf8ff",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "For someone who had never played before,[p/] she was quickly improving with each game."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9488f",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "It took me a while before I even noticed,[p/] but she was adapting to my strategies and trying to use them against me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0388ecc",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "She caught me unaware a few times."
}

{
  "id": "line:095a8c4",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "At the rate she was learning,[p/] she could easily surpass a nationally ranked noble with enough practice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af3630",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "...But I’d been playing this game far longer than she had,[p/] and I was ranked far above the average noble."
}

{
  "id": "line:02838c4",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "She just narrowed her eyes at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d17f0b",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Celeste: How are you always one step ahead of me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02848f4",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Celeste: It's like you're reading my mind!"
}

{
  "id": "line:071a0a2",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "I could,[p/] but I never allowed myself to when playing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1e10f",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Celeste: I'll get you this time!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd2fe3",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "She began placing the pieces back in place when my stomach groaned loudly."
}

{
  "id": "line:021b7ff",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Celeste blinked at me,[p/] startled for a moment,[p/] then she giggled."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e42797",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Tyrion: E[p/][s/]-Excuse me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06349cc",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Celeste: Have you eaten anything?"
}

{
  "id": "line:096e012",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e360d6",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "She looked around for a moment before her eyes went to her slab of mystery meat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e45f8a",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you want some of this?[p/] We have a lot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c11559",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] I couldn’t possibly—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd5956",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "My stomach reprimanded me with another loud rumble."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8d16c",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Against my protests,[p/] she spun the knife in her hand and carved a bite of meat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2894c",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "She started to playfully wave the fork in front of my face expectantly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4a823",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you have another fork?"
}

{
  "id": "line:026ae2f",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Celeste: Come on,[p/] don't be like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:05106fd",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "I wanted to object,[p/] but I was too hungry to argue."
}

{
  "id": "line:06041a3",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "I just bit down on the fork.[p/] That was when I felt quite the jarring texture."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a51e7",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "The meat was tough and fibrous.[p/] I had to consciously chew through the leathery sinew,[p/] lest I choke on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:04377e9",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "I’d never tasted such a distinct, greasy tang before.[p/] I realized that I never actually asked her where this meat came from."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a7e73",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "How was she eating this so quickly?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6ab11",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Celeste: How is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00820e5",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well...[p/] I-[p/][s/]It’s certainly...[p/] unique."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec7c85",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] Bear meat is kinda weird like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9cdd8",
  "node": "CelesteBear",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Oh.[p/][s/] Okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:05069e4",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "As I questioned every decision that had led me to this point,[p/] Ms. Tymora and Flinhart came down from upstairs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd63c6",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "My mentor’s face was stoic as always,[p/] but some frustration bled through.[p/] That was never a good sign."
}

{
  "id": "line:0842cf1",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Celeste: Hi, Dad!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8e68c",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Flinhart: Oh...[p/] Hello, sweetie."
}

{
  "id": "line:0912eb8",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Flinhart’s expression lit up as his daughter rushed over to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6a8fb",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "My mentor glanced at the chessboard on the table."
}

{
  "id": "line:086d589",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "She never really took an interest in chess,[p/] but she knew that I’d been undefeated since I was ten years old."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a596c3",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Don’t feel too bad about losing to him.[p/] He’s nationally ranked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d403a1",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Celeste: What?![p/][s/] You never told me that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cae7f9",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't believe you'd exploit a newbie!"
}

{
  "id": "line:081d0eb",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Ruby: If only..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04804ce",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Celeste: Is that what your suit is for?[p/] Are you some kind of traveling chess player?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a6ef5",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] Chess is just a hobby.[p/] I’m a defense attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eaf4df",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I didn't even know we had attorneys in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d579b5",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "They were definitely a dying breed—[p/]the competent ones, anyways."
}

{
  "id": "line:0898923",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Speaking of,[p/] we should probably get going."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9641e",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Flinhart: Aye...[p/] I hate to refuse you after you came all this way."
}

{
  "id": "line:06817e1",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Flinhart: I respect what you're doing,[p/] but I won’t work with these mages of yours."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ddcba",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Celeste: ... [h=\"Mages...?\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:076d08c",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Ms. Tymora had mentioned that before.[p/] Was this mystery client a mage?"
}

{
  "id": "line:009e16c",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Celeste: A-[p/]Anyways,[p/] it’s getting late."
}

{
  "id": "line:0422793",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Celeste: If you leave now,[p/] you probably won't get to the city until morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:006bf42",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Flinhart: Aye...[p/] She’s right.[p/] These parts are crawling with brigands and conmen."
}

{
  "id": "line:083e6a9",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Flinhart: You wouldn't want to run into one of them after nightfall."
}

{
  "id": "line:06efa95",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Ruby: ...I guess you have a point."
}

{
  "id": "line:006b82e",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Flinhart: The tavern has plenty of empty rooms.[p/] Why don’t you stay here ‘til morning?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ef48c",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Flinhart: ...It’s the least I can do after you came all this way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fde6dd",
  "node": "RubyFlinDesc",
  "text": "Ruby: Fine.[p/] I’m not exactly in a rush to get back on that carriage."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e0722",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Flinhart: Sweetie...[p/] Can you help me with the—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09dca80",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "He paused,[p/] his eyes focusing on the giant slab of meat on the table."
}

{
  "id": "line:08af591",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Flinhart: ...Did you kill [i]another[/i] bear?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9c02a",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Flinhart: We barely got through the last one!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0b35d",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Flinhart: What are we supposed to do with all of this greasy meat?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:077ea26",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Celeste: Eat it![p/][s/] That’s what it's [i]for[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:093bdb2",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Flinhart: How are you even killing these things?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:085e605",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Celeste: It’s not that hard![p/][s/] You just have to keep up with them!"
}

{
  "id": "line:012b320",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Flinhart: For Lord’s sake,[p/][s/] you’re bloody insane..."
}

{
  "id": "line:022c386",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Flinhart: Oh...[p/] Why did the Scaled Lord curse me with a rabid wolf instead of a daughter?"
}

{
  "id": "line:052321e",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Celeste: This \"rabid wolf\" is keeping your family fed!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01db68e",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you know how many commoners in Wyverngarde are starving?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a3fd0",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Flinhart: Don’t talk to me like [i]I’m[/i] the child!"
}

{
  "id": "line:037c292",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "The two continued their bickering as they went up the staircase."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4cdcb",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Flinhart: How do you expect to find a good husband while you’re out in the woods wrestling bears?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7a153",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Celeste: Excuse me![p/][s/] Men are [i]lining[/i] up to court me![p/][s/] I am a [i]goddess[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:032d737",
  "node": "CelFlinBanter",
  "text": "Flinhart: A goddess of war, more like![p/][s/] You’re always coming home covered in blood and dirt!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0754cc3",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Tyrion: So...[p/] Your talk with Flinhart didn’t go well?"
}

{
  "id": "line:054d831",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Ruby: Why can't he understand that all of this is bigger than him and his vendetta?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9eec5",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I still have one last thing we could use."
}

{
  "id": "line:0911a55",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Ruby: Cuthbert—"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e932f",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Celeste skipped back downstairs,[p/] pausing upon seeing the air between my mentor and me."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a442a",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh—[p/][s/] Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:075abf8",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Celeste: We're done with your rooms.[p/] You can head upstairs if you want to rest up."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fec6c",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Right."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e4251",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Thank you, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6a484",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Silence followed us up the stairs until we arrived at our rooms."
}

{
  "id": "line:0004648",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Ms. Tymora’s hand gripped the handle of the door,[p/] but she never turned it."
}

{
  "id": "line:079ebf6",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Ruby: ...I'm sorry.[p/] I didn't expect our discussion to go for that long."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a7689",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's fine.[p/] I understand."
}

{
  "id": "line:077b46e",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Ruby: I saw you playing chess with Flinhart's daughter earlier.[p/] Was everything okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:088eeac",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0178fa1",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Ruby: ...You're kind of a sore winner when you play."
}

{
  "id": "line:0363920",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Only when my opponent's a noble."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ff268",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She caught on quickly.[p/] She was ridiculously good for a beginner."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a810c1",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension",
  "text": "Tyrion: Playing against her was nice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0575170",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Ruby: Well...[p/] I suppose you [i]are[/i] at that age."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b284cf",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No![p/][s/] That's not what I meant!"
}

{
  "id": "line:057372c",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I never really get to play against other players outside of tournaments…"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f93af",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And [i]you[/i] only ever want to play Shogi against me."
}

{
  "id": "line:076d602",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Ruby: Because Shogi is clearly superior."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6a097",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s complete anarchy,[p/][s/] is what it is!"
}

{
  "id": "line:015e5c2",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You just bring fallen pieces back to life like some kind of necromancer."
}

{
  "id": "line:060262b",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Ruby: It adds depth.[p/][s/] Dropping adds a dimension of play that isn't present in chess."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c90bc",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "We both glared at each other silently,[p/] but all of the tension from before had left."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d21eda",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "After a few moments,[p/] we just both burst out laughing."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d59c7",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...You really have grown up, haven't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f1def",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Ruby: You must’ve been only ten when you suddenly showed up at my house."
}

{
  "id": "line:0510f71",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That was a long time ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0905134",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "She stayed silent for a moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e02026",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...I know that you're just trying to help."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9a7c8",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then why won’t you let me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a90eab",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Ruby: Cuthbert,[p/] it's not the right time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4185c",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’m ready for this, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cb02b",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Ruby: You are.[p/] I know you are."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c6261",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "That just made me raise an eyebrow at her."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f7bff",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Then what's the issue here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07b0764",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Again,[p/] she just stayed silent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7fdba",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Get some rest.[p/] You’ll need to prepare for the journey tomorrow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0857b61",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "I winced at that thought.[p/] I’d completely forgotten that I’d have to wrangle those horses again..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af4181",
  "node": "RubyTyrTension2",
  "text": "I opened the door and fell onto the bed inside."
}

{
  "id": "line:0126cd8",
  "node": "Dream",
  "text": "It wasn't long before night fell.[p/] Between driving that carriage and dealing with those con artists,[p/] I was exhausted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8d78f",
  "node": "Dream",
  "text": "I fell asleep,[p/] but I felt uneasiness creep into me as the night went on."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7bb94",
  "node": "Dream",
  "text": "I felt myself being pulled away,[p/] brought elsewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6021f",
  "node": "Dream",
  "text": "In every direction I looked,[p/] there was nothing—[p/]only the glass-like floor I was standing on."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b15123",
  "node": "Dream",
  "text": "I saw my reflection in the floor.[p/] With each step I took,[p/] it rippled and shimmered."
}

{
  "id": "line:02032f0",
  "node": "Dream",
  "text": "I knew that I was dreaming,[p/] but something deep inside me insisted that there was something real about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7aeeb",
  "node": "Dream",
  "text": "Whispers echoed through the realm.[p/] I spotted the small, dark silhouette of a person in the distance."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ac676",
  "node": "Dream",
  "text": "She was silently staring at me and murmuring something under her breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0741338",
  "node": "Dream",
  "text": "She repeated the same phrase,[p/] almost like a chant."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e1597",
  "node": "Dream",
  "text": "She looked practically giddy in anticipation of...[p/] [i]something[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0054481",
  "node": "Dream",
  "text": "Eris: [j]I've finally found you, heavensborn![/j][p/][p/][p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:04318c3",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "I woke up to the sound of shouting from downstairs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba79bd",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "I clutched at my chest.[p/] My heart was racing,[p/] and I was drenched in sweat."
}

{
  "id": "line:068ad6c",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "That was just a nightmare...[p/] I tried to convince myself of that."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a1dfe",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "I shook my head.[p/] Something else was happening downstairs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0391b3c",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "Those voices sounded like Celeste's and Flinhart's,[p/] and they were only getting louder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdcd92",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "Celeste: Please![p/][s/] Just let me explain!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0e889",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "Flinhart: I don’t want to hear it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c78695",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "They definitely weren’t bickering about the bear meat this time..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af36d6",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "Flinhart: I WANT YOU OUT OF MY HOUSE![p/][s/] GET OUT!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e99ac2",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "After that,[p/] there was only silence,[p/] followed by someone storming out of the tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa5663",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "The front door of the tavern slammed shut,[p/] the entire structure swaying from the force."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e0ca6",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "I lay there silent.[p/] What could they be arguing about this late at night?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfe001",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0437745",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "It really wasn’t any of my business."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc4a0b",
  "node": "TheArgue",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]*sigh*[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da8714",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "The door creaked loudly as I eased it open and stepped out of my room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1bbcb",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "The hallway was completely dark.[p/] Not a single candle was lit."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0522e",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "I stepped forward slowly,[p/] careful not to trip over anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:064692a",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "Flinhart: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02dc908",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "Flinhart was trudging up the stairs when I bumped into him."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e2a2e",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "I couldn’t see his face,[p/] but judging from how he sounded earlier,[p/] I probably didn’t want to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba240b",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "Tyrion: Sorry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b3f98",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "Flinhart: Right...[p/] I forgot you two were—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1ebe9",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "His voice trailed off."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aec51c",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is everything okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0576f03",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "Flinhart: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c648fa",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Sorry,[p/] I’m just going to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:008f944",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "I slid past Flinhart as I went down the stairs.[p/] He barely even noticed."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c0cee",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "I made my way to the dining room.[p/] There weren't any lights in the streets.[p/] It was nearly pitch black."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb9231",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Hello?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3ca29",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "No answer.[p/] I looked at the entrance to the tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:090ff99",
  "node": "FlinhartUp",
  "text": "The door was hanging open.[p/] The wooden frame was cracked."
}

{
  "id": "line:052366d",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "I walked through the village streets,[p/] but there weren't any lights on.[p/] I regretted not taking a lantern on my way out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3b4f4",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "I heard a squelch as I accidentally stepped on something that was disgustingly soft.[p/] I tried my best to ignore it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0255e00",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:041ec28",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste?![p/][s/] Where are you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a3028",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "A groan echoed from one of the nearby shacks.[p/] A lantern flickered to life from behind the wooden door."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d492d7",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "An older man stepped out,[p/] squinting against the darkness of the night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7baec",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Peasant: ...You got any idea what time it is?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0633601",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "He eyed me up and down,[p/] taking notice of how I was dressed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf3ccc",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Peasant: This ain’t the city, boy.[p/] We like our peace and quiet after sundown."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d6531",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right...[p/] Sorry.[p/] I was just looking for Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:007f579",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Peasant: ...Who?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d17122",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste McCoy.[p/] She’s Flinhart’s daughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcbbab",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Something in his expression shifted.[p/] Irritation turned into complete contempt."
}

{
  "id": "line:0850bb6",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you know her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0841ee4",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Peasant: What do you want with that bastard? [h=\"That damned mage...\" e=\"a\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:03231b5",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Tyrion: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab0de3",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Peasant: Those two probably woke up half the town with their yelling."
}

{
  "id": "line:0998c24",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Look,[p/] I just want to make sure that she's safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c59cb",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Peasant: Ha![p/] You've got nothing to worry about there."
}

{
  "id": "line:064f253",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "Before I could get another word in,[p/] he went back into his house in a huff,[p/] slamming the door behind him."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cb0b5",
  "node": "TyrionSearch",
  "text": "I just took a breath and continued searching."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ff9f2",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: Still have that famous temper, I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0addba4",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Flinhart: ...You?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01be1a8",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: Honestly,[p/] I never understood how you could stand living in this gloomy shack."
}

{
  "id": "line:002236d",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: [b]Luxo[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0701791",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Flinhart: How [i]dare[/i] you use that witchcraft in my home?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8eddb",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: From what I've seen,[p/] I'm not the first."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e4975",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: You’ve really been stirring the pot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e27a75",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: The Four Pillars don’t care for what they’ve been hearing from your rallies."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c15d7",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Flinhart: Is that right?[p/] I’ll be sure to bring that up at the next meeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b277ab",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: ...For Lord's sake![p/][s/] Have some sense, Flinhart!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d75287",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: At this rate,[p/] you're going to bring Lucio Steelwind down on [i]all[/i] of us!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08fdb12",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: [i]You[/i] may not value your life,[p/] but I will not become another one of his \"casualties\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:03336c0",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Flinhart: So you came all this way to convince me to stop?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a5de3",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: ...End this foolishness now,[p/] and no harm will come to you or your family.[p/] You have my word."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d056eb",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Flinhart: Hah![p/] Your \"word\" is as good as the dirt you lick off the King’s boots."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd28f4",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Flinhart: You’re a killer.[p/] As if I’d ever trust you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b89741",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0013329",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: Flinhart, please.[p/] As someone who once thought of you as a friend,[p/] I’m only going to ask you once."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e8c3b",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Flinhart: ...\"Friend\"?[p/][s/] \"[i]Friend[/i]\"?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:030c4fc",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Flinhart: I’ll be dead in the ground before I ever call the likes of you a \"friend\"!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b22e92",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Flinhart: Get out of my house.[p/] I don’t have time for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5303d",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: ...I don’t think you’ll have much time for anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:029b966",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Flinhart: GAH!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0941745",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: Damn it all!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05deb60",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: You stubborn fool![p/][s/] Why couldn’t you have just listened to me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f3865",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: Rudolf!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ed7d5",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Rhys: ...Yes, sir?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b25000",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Rhys: By the Scaled Lord![p/][s/] What did you—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c585b8",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Rhys: You...[p/][s/] killed him?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5640d",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: Alert the Inquisition.[p/] Tell them that you saw his daughter fleeing the scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0941084",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Garrick: I’m sure their neighbors heard them yelling at each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee4e7f",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Rhys: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d26f6a",
  "node": "TheMurder",
  "text": "Rhys: Understood, sir."
}

{
  "id": "line:077a35b",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What am I going to do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a4825",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/][s/]Oh...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de9b4f",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "A few hours had already passed,[p/] but I finally found her sitting under an old oak tree."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df1bbc",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "She looked just as tired as I was,[p/] probably even more so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0257b04",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Her eyes were wet and red,[p/] but she quickly wiped them with her sleeve as she stood up to meet me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0955b4a",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I've been looking for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a43ff",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh...[p/] Did we wake you up?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0adb92e",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I just wanted to make sure you were okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fefaf4",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Celeste: It’s nothing.[p/] We argue like that all of the time... [h=\"Please just go away.\" e=\"sa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:010b000",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Celeste: I’m fine.[p/] See?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c93538",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "She tried to squeeze her lips into a smile,[p/] but it didn’t reach her eyes."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f30d7",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Celeste: You should really head back.[p/] It’s not safe to be out here this late."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac5b12",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What about you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd7c6f",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I can take care of myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e2479",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "I just stood there silently for a moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9be42",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm sure he just lost his temper."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f40d2e",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Celeste: You don’t know that. [h=\"Mind your own business...\" e=\"sa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:046b16a",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Sorry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d86a07",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "She just looked down and said nothing before exhaling."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cc771",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Maybe you’re right."
}

{
  "id": "line:054d695",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "Celeste: It wouldn't feel right to let you walk back alone anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:082b61c",
  "node": "TyrFindsCel",
  "text": "She walked past me,[p/] leading me back to the tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bc8ab",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:073420f",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "We returned,[p/] but found the tavern surrounded by knights clad in plate armor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd3e02",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "Several carriages were parked outside,[p/] and I could see several lights lit within the tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:00027ab",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is that the Arcane Inquisition?"
}

{
  "id": "line:011cccf",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "Celeste: Inquisition...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:006a95c",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "Tyrion: They're an order of knights who investigate crimes committed using magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:07dd2b2",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "Celeste and I shared a glance.[p/] Without another word,[p/] both of us ran towards the tavern,[p/] but she quickly outpaced me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0064d5f",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What?[p/] N-[p/][s/]No..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2086c",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "She reached the tavern door,[p/] and the color drained from her face."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ab989",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "Her hand went to her mouth as she stumbled backwards,[p/] her body shuddering."
}

{
  "id": "line:040f3e6",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "Celeste: D-[p/][s/]Dad...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:086eb03",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "Her voice quivered.[p/] Tears began to stream down her face."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ff0ec",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "Orym: There you are!"
}

{
  "id": "line:051a940",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "As Celeste stood there, frozen,[p/] a knight stepped between her and the tavern entrance."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cb38e",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "Orym: Celeste McCoy![p/][s/] By the authority of the Wyverngarde crown,[p/][s/] I'm placing you under arrest!"
}

{
  "id": "line:024732a",
  "node": "CelArrest",
  "text": "The knight tried to grab her arm,[p/] and it was like something flipped inside of her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaec3e",
  "node": "CelArrest2",
  "text": "She slammed her palm into the knight's chest,[p/] his plate armour reverberating as he was launched several feet backwards."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c0037",
  "node": "CelArrest2",
  "text": "Three other knights rushed forward.[p/] They tried to grab her and pin her to the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df0c4d",
  "node": "CelArrest2",
  "text": "She let out a guttural scream against them,[p/] almost sounding like a feral animal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0951c51",
  "node": "CelArrest2",
  "text": "It looked like it was taking all of their strength to keep her pinned down."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d3b60",
  "node": "CelArrest2",
  "text": "It was like she was a completely different person.[p/] I stood there stunned before shaking myself out of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0094b92",
  "node": "CelArrest2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What are you doing to her?![p/][s/] Let her go!"
}

{
  "id": "line:020078e",
  "node": "CelArrest2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0927cc3",
  "node": "CelArrest2",
  "text": "Thank the Scaled Lord...[p/] Ms. Tymora was safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4d391",
  "node": "CelArrest2",
  "text": "Orym: [i]Tch[/i]![p/] I knew I recognized him from somewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7613e",
  "node": "CelArrest2",
  "text": "Orym: Stay out of our way,[p/][s/] or we’ll lock you two up right next to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f7373",
  "node": "CelArrest2",
  "text": "He left in a huff,[p/] following after the other knights as they slowly dragged Celeste away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f798ad",
  "node": "CelArrest2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora...[p/][s/] What's going on?![p/][s/] Why is the Arcane Inquisition here?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a00355",
  "node": "CelArrest2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...I'm not sure,[p/] but...[p/] Flinhart is dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a79d14",
  "node": "CelArrest2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa0562",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": ":Celeste was going to be detained in Ratholme:[p/] Wyverngarde's capital city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dadbe9",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "She was apparently the prime suspect in Flinhart’s murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:025718f",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Her case would be pushed to trial within the day.[p/] Supposedly,[p/] they discovered traces of magic at the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:05be532",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "That honestly just raised even more questions..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0735311",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Ms. Tymora and I were determined to get to the bottom of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b238f4",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "The Inquisition,[p/] on the other hand,[p/] did what they always did..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0981d48",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Ruby: This is ridiculous.[p/] She has a right to speak to an attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a1c54",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah...[p/] Well,[p/] we can’t let you see her until she’s been processed."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bec5e",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Orym White was the commander of the Arcane Inquisition.[p/] Ms. Tymora had supposedly run into him many times."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed9a75",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "He always looked like the textbook definition of someone who was \"too old for this\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0812841",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "I didn't usually accompany Ms. Tymora to her crime scenes,[p/] but the few times I had,[p/] he was always there to run interference."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a62a0",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "He always looked like he cared more about making trouble for us than actually doing his job."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e72ccb",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "The Inquisition was deep in the nobility's pockets.[p/] I'd always assumed that they were paying him to sabotage us."
}

{
  "id": "line:024774d",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Ruby: Don’t give me that.[p/] There's no way you haven't processed her with the trial this close."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b672c",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah?[p/] Well,[p/] unless you can prove it,[p/] I don’t need to do anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:056916b",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Aria: ...What’s with all of this noise?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e338d",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Orym: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/][s/] Uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0981502",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "The commander’s back straightened out,[p/] his smirk turning into a wince as the girl walked into the chambers."
}

{
  "id": "line:03117d2",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Whoever she was,[p/] she must've been younger than me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf9a03",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Despite that,[p/] her voice carried the weight of her authority[p/]—something which Orym clearly relented to."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bc52c",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Her aura was as cold and rigid as stone.[p/] Her disposition was probably equally so."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c69cf",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Ruby: Celeste McCoy has a right to counsel,[p/] and I’m—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdbb24",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Aria: I know who you are, Ruby Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfba44",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "She turned to Orym.[p/] She was almost half his size,[p/] but he was practically flinching at her every word."
}

{
  "id": "line:0357abc",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Orym: O-[p/][s/]Oh,[p/][s/] uh—[p/] Well,[p/] the girl hasn’t been processed yet—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0627d19",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "She just let out an irritated sigh as she waved him away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0533a81",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Aria: Let them through."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ac13f",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Orym: What...?[p/][s/] But—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b5419",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Aria: Let them through before I throw you into the cell next to hers."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a6b91",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Orym: Y-[p/][s/]Yes, Lady—[p/][s/] Erm...[p/][s/] I mean...[p/][s/] [i]Ms.[/i] Steelwind..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06735e9",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "...\"Steelwind\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0664a09",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "She gave me a passing glance as if she were silently appraising me.[p/] She walked out of the dungeons without another word."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a6b57",
  "node": "CelDungeon",
  "text": "Orym grumbled under his breath as he led us to Celeste’s cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:030b427",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "I had to wade through a thickening fog of emotions as we descended further into the dungeons."
}

{
  "id": "line:06617fc",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "The collective anger and sorrow of the prisoners was choking me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0617974",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "I'd always hated crowds.[p/] I could never shut out the storm of thoughts and emotions that came with them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0340bba",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "But I tried my best to keep it together.[p/] Celeste was going through a lot more than I was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da7a99",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/][s/]Oh!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c55e2",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Celeste was curled up on the cold floor,[p/] arms wrapped around her knees."
}

{
  "id": "line:080cfe9",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "When she saw us,[p/] she scrambled to her feet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e013d8",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What are you doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f171d7",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Ruby: We know about what happened to your father..."
}

{
  "id": "line:013f40f",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I’m so sorry, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:042d8bf",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Celeste: ... [h=\"I still can't believe it...\" e=\"sfa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0221ec6",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Thanks."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb9040",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Her response came out hollowly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0271597",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Ruby: You’re the Inquisition’s prime suspect in the murder,[p/] and they’re planning to push your case to trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e4226",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Ruby: You’ll be brought to court in a few hours."
}

{
  "id": "line:0192db1",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Celeste: What?![p/][s/] No one told me anything!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0075e71",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "My mentor scoffed in disgust.[p/] She was all too familiar with this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c680db",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Ruby: They were planning to convict you before you even [i]realized[/i] you were on trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d06952",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] Ms. Tymora is the best defense attorney in Wyverngarde.[p/] She can help you."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bd7e8",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Ruby: You’ve been supporting your family from your work as a mercenary.[p/] Is that correct?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d9b93",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "...Did she just say \"mercenary\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d20c5",
  "node": "RubyCel",
  "text": "Ruby: From your financial history,[p/] it appears that you can afford my services."
}

{
  "id": "line:065b74b",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Celeste: How would you even know that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0266a76",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Ruby: ...That's not important."
}

{
  "id": "line:010d5f8",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Ruby: What matters is that if I’m representing you,[p/] your case is as good as won."
}

{
  "id": "line:05efe73",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You don’t even know what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d5c09",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Ruby: Then tell me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fec83b",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Celeste hesitated,[p/] her shoulders tensing at the memory."
}

{
  "id": "line:03180cd",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i] I got into an...[p/] [i]argument[/i] with my dad,[p/] and I left to clear my head."
}

{
  "id": "line:086648c",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion found me a bit after that.[p/] I think it was a few hours after I left."
}

{
  "id": "line:0faee3c",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Celeste: When we came back,[p/] we saw the knights outside.[p/] That's when they arrested me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acc174",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Celeste.[p/] If I’m going to be your attorney,[p/] I need to know [i]everything[/i] that happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3c326",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Celeste: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0054f2f",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Ruby: They found your sword inside his body,[p/] and there were traces of [b]transmutation[/b] magic around the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f517f6",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Ruby: There aren’t any other registered mages in Kornhaven.[p/] I need you to tell me the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a27d2",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Celeste: I just told you everything that happened.[p/] What are you—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9bed3",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "She looked down, confused,[p/] before her face tightened into a scowl."
}

{
  "id": "line:0569d38",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You actually think I did it, don’t you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0434421",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Celeste: You think [i]I[/i] was the one who killed him."
}

{
  "id": "line:01af543",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait,[p/] Ms. Tymora.[p/] Before I left the tavern to look for her,[p/] I ran into Flinhart.[p/] He was still alive."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c55f6",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Ruby: ...And how much time passed between that and when you found her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc494d",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was probably about two hours,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0abc634",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Ruby: Which means there are two hours where she wasn’t accounted for."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2a1fc",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Ruby: We can work around that,[p/] but the prosecution will still—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0405e53",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Celeste: No![p/][s/] I didn’t do this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:057aa40",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Tyrion: She’s telling the truth, Ms. Tymora.[p/] Celeste would never do something like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:043aba8",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Ruby: Cuthbert, you can't just believe every innocent girl who bats her eyes at you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad11f2",
  "node": "RubyConfront",
  "text": "Tyrion: That is [i]not[/i] what this is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0513ddf",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Ruby: Well, did you [i]see[/i] that she’s innocent?[p/] Can you tell me that with certainty?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05fd777",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "...Celeste was being defensive at the moment,[p/] too guarded for me to read anything substantial with the Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfb929",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I didn’t [i]see[/i] it,[p/] but I know that she’s innocent."
}

{
  "id": "line:095e0b7",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Ruby: Look.[p/] Either way,[p/] we need to construct a proper alibi so I can—"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e936f",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Celeste: No![p/][s/] How can I work with you if you don’t even believe me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0931894",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Do you even understand the situation you're in?"
}

{
  "id": "line:048f737",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Celeste: I know exactly what’s happening!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbc229",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Celeste: My dad’s dead,[p/][s/] and whoever killed him is still out there!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00da143",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Ruby: Don’t be naive.[p/] You’re a commoner.[p/] You’re lucky [i]I’m[/i] even here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd8036",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Ruby: There isn’t a single attorney other than me who will defend someone like you."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b7c25",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah?![p/][s/] Well, what about him?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05ef9d8",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "I blinked,[p/] confused for a moment,[p/] before I realized that she was pointing at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:08207ae",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Celeste: You're also a defense attorney, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae930b",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I am,[p/][s/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b0d4a",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Ruby: He’s just a kid, McCoy.[p/] He’s never even defended a case before."
}

{
  "id": "line:01905d3",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Celeste: I don’t care![p/][s/] At least he doesn’t think I’m a murderer!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ec028",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Tyrion: C-[p/][s/]Celeste,[p/] hold on—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0755d51",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Celeste: So you can take your attitude and leave.[p/] I don’t need your help."
}

{
  "id": "line:007cd1a",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Ruby: Fine,[p/] have it your way."
}

{
  "id": "line:021c667",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Ruby: But when you’re staring down the gallows and begging me to appeal your conviction,[p/] I’ll be charging you triple my rate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0892a2f",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "Before I could understand what was going on,[p/] Ms. Tymora turned away and stormed out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf05de",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "As she reached the door,[p/] she looked back at me expectantly."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d9f9d",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "I froze.[p/] I knew I wasn't in any position to handle a case like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fe3a2",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "...That said,[p/] I also knew I couldn't leave her to face this alone."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d2530",
  "node": "RubyConfront2",
  "text": "My mentor let out a quiet sigh before quietly exiting the dungeons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0e2a4",
  "node": "TyrionReCeleste",
  "text": "Celeste: Sorry...[p/] I didn’t mean to put you in the middle of that."
}

{
  "id": "line:021459c",
  "node": "TyrionReCeleste",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I can go talk to her.[p/] I'm sure she'll come back and take your case."
}

{
  "id": "line:050d777",
  "node": "TyrionReCeleste",
  "text": "Celeste: No,[p/] I meant what I said.[p/] I don’t want her help."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9f116",
  "node": "TyrionReCeleste",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste![p/][s/] This is serious!"
}

{
  "id": "line:033c87a",
  "node": "TyrionReCeleste",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your conviction might as well be a foregone conclusion to the courts.[p/] Without Ms. Tymora,[p/] you’ll—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d077a5",
  "node": "TyrionReCeleste",
  "text": "Celeste: It'll be fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0075433",
  "node": "TyrionReCeleste",
  "text": "Celeste: I know I just pulled you into this without asking."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9b061",
  "node": "TyrionReCeleste",
  "text": "Celeste: If you want to walk away,[p/] I’ll understand.[p/] I’ll figure something out..."
}

{
  "id": "line:051b648",
  "node": "TyrionReCeleste",
  "text": "She tugged a few times at the cell door separating us.[p/] I could have sworn I saw the metal bars bending."
}

{
  "id": "line:0268d15",
  "node": "TyrionReCeleste",
  "text": "I exhaled slowly.[p/] I knew I wasn’t ready for this."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e37e0",
  "node": "TyrionReCeleste",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I can’t stand by and do nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e2e05",
  "node": "TyrionReCeleste",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’ll take your case,[p/] if you’ll have me."
}

{
  "id": "line:060aa92",
  "node": "TyrionReCeleste",
  "text": "Celeste: Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc57f8",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But there’s one thing I need you to tell me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f955cd",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "The Arcane Inquisition was called to the scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c868f",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "I had no idea how they even knew magic had been used,[p/] but their presence could only mean one thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec3e9c",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are you a mage?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db2113",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Y-[p/][s/]Yeah.[p/] I am."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e44a48",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "When that villager confronted me before,[p/] he called her a bastard.[p/] It made a lot more sense now."
}

{
  "id": "line:098ed95",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you have noble blood?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdc2eb",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What does [i]that[/i] have to do with anything?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0613c03",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: The ability to use magic is hereditary."
}

{
  "id": "line:092c061",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: Almost every mage descends from the nobility in some way."
}

{
  "id": "line:053e1d3",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you have birth parents in the nobility,[p/] we might be able to use their influence to our advantage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb0101",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't need anyone else's help.[p/] I’m a McCoy.[p/] That’s all I need to know about myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fdd26",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "It seemed best not to push that matter further then."
}

{
  "id": "line:021e540",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Even so,[p/] that’s probably why they arrested you."
}

{
  "id": "line:023e7c2",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Celeste: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0923801",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora mentioned it earlier.[p/] A town of farmers like Kornhaven wouldn’t have any other registered mages."
}

{
  "id": "line:01237da",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a good thing you registered with the kingdom.[p/] It would have just added one extra charge if you hadn't."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fd587",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: But they found traces of magic at the scene of the crime.[p/] They have no choice but to suspect you."
}

{
  "id": "line:008bb86",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Are you serious?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03db0ca",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’ll be honest.[p/] I’m not sure how much help I’ll really be."
}

{
  "id": "line:071d2f7",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora said it herself.[p/] I've never defended a client before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f81fbf",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Is everything really going to be okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:041d112",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "...Why would I say something like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9d8c9",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "A defense attorney should be putting their clients at ease."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd0891",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: B-[p/][s/]But no matter what,[p/] I'll get you an acquittal."
}

{
  "id": "line:07427f2",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: It doesn't matter who stands in my way—[p/]man,[p/] king,[p/] or god."
}

{
  "id": "line:0754977",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0305165",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Sorry.[p/][s/] I used to say that a lot as a kid...[p/][s/] Um—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce501d",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*giggle*[/i] No,[p/] it's okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0448035",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "At least it made her laugh."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddd0c0",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...A-[p/][s/]Anyways,[p/] take some time to rest up.[p/] The trial will begin in a few hours."
}

{
  "id": "line:0908848",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "I couldn’t imagine what she was going through."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f72f4b",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "She’d not only lost her father,[p/] but she was also being framed for his murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a72288",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": ":But this was exactly why I became an attorney:[p/] to defend people exactly like her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0656e6e",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "Stories like hers were far too common,[p/] but this time,[p/] I had the power to change it."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fd461",
  "node": "CelTheMage",
  "text": "She was putting her trust in me.[p/] I would make sure she wouldn't regret that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0727f4f",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "It still hadn’t sunk in yet.[p/] I was standing in a real courtroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0616100",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "I'd only ever acted as Ms. Tymora's assistant.[p/] Now I was front and center at the defense table..."
}

{
  "id": "line:094c28f",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8dae7",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "Tyrion: Y-[p/][s/]Yes.[p/][s/] Of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:057f50f",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "Maybe if I kept saying that,[p/] it would end up being true..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05382b0",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "AriaC: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef9b74",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "That woman from the dungeons was also here.[p/] She must’ve been the prosecutor for Celeste’s trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:02730b4",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "No wonder she was able to order around the Commander like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfe6a6",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "I could feel her piercing glare burrowing into me."
}

{
  "id": "line:00576a3",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "Why was she looking at me like that?[p/] Was she trying to intimidate me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7770d",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "...Because it was definitely working!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7cb20",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "Judge: Court is now in session for the trial of Celeste McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:02dce85",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "AriaC: The prosecution is ready, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e0aec",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...O-[p/][s/]Oh,[p/] uh."
}

{
  "id": "line:014553a",
  "node": "Trial1Begin",
  "text": "Tyrion: T-[p/][s/]The defense is also ready, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb5f8b",
  "node": "Trial1Begin2",
  "text": "Judge: ...Very well.[p/] Prosecutor Steelwind,[p/] could you please list the charges?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0057c59",
  "node": "Trial1Begin2",
  "text": "AriaC: The defendant is Celeste McCoy:[p/] a mercenary by trade and a registered mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0407d3b",
  "node": "Trial1Begin2",
  "text": "AriaC: She’s charged with second-degree murder and negligent misuse of the Arcane Arts."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eed79a",
  "node": "Trial1Begin2",
  "text": "AriaC: The crime occurred within the McCoy Tavern:[p/] a local inn that was shut down years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c43838",
  "node": "Trial1Begin2",
  "text": "AriaC: Those who lived nearby reported hearing a loud argument coming from within the building around 1:00 AM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b784bb",
  "node": "Trial1Begin2",
  "text": "AriaC: At 1:08 AM,[p/] a carriage driver entered the tavern to investigate the disturbance."
}

{
  "id": "line:072adc5",
  "node": "Trial1Begin2",
  "text": "AriaC: It was there that he found the victim,[p/] the defendant’s sword impaled within his body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef360b",
  "node": "Trial1Begin2",
  "text": "AriaC: The Inquisition has provided an autopsy report and documentation for the sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:066f920",
  "node": "Trial1Begin2",
  "text": "Judge: What was the defendant’s relationship with the victim?[p/] I see that they share the same last name."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f00d1",
  "node": "Trial1Begin2",
  "text": "AriaC: The defendant is the victim’s daughter,[p/] but not by blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:0689c2f",
  "node": "Trial1Begin2",
  "text": "AriaC: She was adopted into the family when she was an infant.[p/] Her birth parents are currently unknown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff72ce",
  "node": "Trial1Begin2",
  "text": "Judge: I see...[p/] What an unfortunate turn of events..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01cbbce",
  "node": "CallOrym",
  "text": "AriaC: To begin,[p/] the prosecution would like to call Commander Orym White to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4efa0",
  "node": "CallOrym",
  "text": "AriaC: Witness,[p/] please state your name and occupation for the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3598b",
  "node": "CallOrym",
  "text": "Orym: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3d1b6",
  "node": "CallOrym",
  "text": "AriaC: Witness.[p/] Name and occupation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8ba9d",
  "node": "CallOrym",
  "text": "Orym: ...Name’s Orym White.[p/] I’m the commander of the Arcane Inquisition."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc76d1",
  "node": "CallOrym",
  "text": "AriaC: Commander,[p/] please testify about the details of the Inquisition's investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0941361",
  "node": "CallOrym",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah,[p/] yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fb8b1",
  "node": "CallOrym",
  "text": "Orym: We got a call late at night.[p/] Someone found a dead body inside the McCoy Tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0d6d9",
  "node": "CallOrym",
  "text": "Orym: When we arrived on the scene,[p/] we found Flinhart McCoy dead on the floor.[p/] The defendant’s sword was still in his chest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb12f7",
  "node": "CallOrym",
  "text": "Orym: We have a bunch of witnesses who heard the victim and defendant in a loud argument before the body was called in."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fe09e",
  "node": "CallOrym",
  "text": "Orym: That argument must've turned ugly,[p/] because the defendant killed the old man using her magic sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5bbba",
  "node": "CallOrym",
  "text": "This was going to be difficult.[p/] The defendant's sword was the murder weapon."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e5047",
  "node": "CallOrym",
  "text": "It was possible that the murderer used it to frame her.[p/] That must have meant that the crime was premeditated."
}

{
  "id": "line:008844b",
  "node": "CallOrym",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert, you may begin your cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9f223",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "Tyrion: Uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f791ee",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "Judge: ...Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcb0e4",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "...Where was I supposed to start again?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad7e57",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "I needed to prove that Celeste was innocent,[p/] but they found her sword in the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:00282df",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...?[p/] This is the part where you say something, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0804531",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "The longer I stood there,[p/] the more I noticed everyone staring at me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0302afa",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "I could feel the case cracking.[p/] Each moment of silence was just another blow to my credibility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f27134",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "AriaC: [i]*sigh*[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b0bef",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "AriaC: I wanted to face Ruby Tymora today,[p/] not her bumbling sidekick."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6b20f",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b84aed",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "AriaC: Your Honor.[p/] The defense clearly has nothing to say against the prosecution’s overwhelming evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a13636",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "Orym: Yep.[p/] This whole thing’s pretty open and shut."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d84fa6",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No![p/][s/] Wait!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0722af5",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "Ruby: …"
}

{
  "id": "line:02dc96f",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "Ruby: I-[p/][s/]I’m so sorry, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:039da16",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "Ruby: I didn't do enough for Frey...[p/] Now she's—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0540fe2",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "Tyrion: M-[p/][s/]Ms. Tymora...[p/][s/] Does this mean they are going to execute her?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2dfa5",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "No... [p/]Not again..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0724113",
  "node": "TyrPanik",
  "text": "Was I seriously going to watch that happen again?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c8d1b",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:031a4ed",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Her palm cracked across my face.[p/] I stumbled back and almost fell over."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ebc6f",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "She had every right to be angry,[p/] but that wasn't what I saw on her face."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b544e",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I’m sorry...! Celeste,[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:099bb24",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Celeste: Stop.[p/] Just listen to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e523a",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Celeste: You trained for this, right?[p/] You [i]know[/i] what to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0637e61",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I’ve never done this before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0304c94",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "She cursed under her breath.[p/] She searched her mind for an answer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a59bba",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Then just treat it like something you [i]have[/i] done before!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05ac181",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Celeste: I don’t know—[p/] Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d08752",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Celeste: You’re good at chess, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbb3ed",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Celeste: So just treat this whole thing like you’re playing chess!"
}

{
  "id": "line:078bba2",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't know![p/][s/] Yesterday,[p/] you were calm and you were focused!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7a41d",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Celeste: So just...[p/][s/] [i]channel[/i] that feeling!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa483b",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Celeste: Look at the...[p/] pieces on the board...[p/] or something like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c18279",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Celeste: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f2d9d",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "He made a lot of statements."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec90d3",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Every statement that he made,[p/] every word that came out of his mouth,[p/] they were all just pieces on the board."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c27e6c",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "A match wasn't won from the first move.[p/] It came from developing the pieces I had and taking every advantage that presented itself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0384d9b",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I apologize, Your Honor.[p/] The defense is ready to begin the cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d1fa6",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Judge: ...Hmph...[p/] Seeing as this is your first trial, Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] I’ll overlook it this one time."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b409b",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Celeste: There we go. [h=\"Thank the gods|that actually worked...\" e=\"hf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbc3ba",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "I needed to carefully examine every statement he made,[p/] line by line."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fe727",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "The key to every cross-examination was identifying which statement contradicted the evidence in my NOTES."
}

{
  "id": "line:03eabe4",
  "node": "CelSlap",
  "text": "Once I did that,[p/][s/] I needed to PRESENT the contradicting evidence!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0260687",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: What time did you get this call?[p/] And who discovered the body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f662da",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Orym: The call came in at 1:08 AM,[p/] and the witness wanted to remain incognito."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca4065",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "It wasn’t unusual for a witness to request anonymity.[p/] It was well within their rights."
}

{
  "id": "line:035a4a5",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "But it would’ve been a lot easier if I could cross-examine that witness directly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a85f49",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "AriaC: What happened when you arrived, Commander?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5ed01",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: How are you so sure that the sword was my client’s?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0adf475",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Orym: Her sword is made out of some weird alloy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a22a08",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Orym: I think it was forged out of the country or something."
}

{
  "id": "line:068c7ba",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Orym: It’d be hard to mistake something like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:051f2f6",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "AriaC: We also have several eyewitnesses who verified that the sword belonged to the defendant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccac99",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "AriaC: She made no effort to hide it from the public. Quite the contrary, she was quite proud to show it off."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c224a0",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even so,[p/] that doesn’t necessarily mean that she was the one who stabbed him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e57034",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah,[p/] well..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7c39a",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How did they know it was my client who was arguing with the victim?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e58249",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Orym: You were there, weren’t you?[p/] Don’t tell me you didn’t hear them."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b6b48",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Orym: Every witness we talked to knew it was them."
}

{
  "id": "line:08715e7",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "I couldn’t really argue with him there.[p/] Celeste and Flinhart had very distinct voices, especially when they were raised."
}

{
  "id": "line:0838133",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was there when the argument took place.[p/] Flinhart was still alive when my client left the tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:078579d",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "AriaC: Perhaps,[p/] but how do you know that she didn’t return to murder her father afterwards?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0893f8f",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Weren’t there plenty of other people around who could have committed the crime?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4e244",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Orym: That tavern’s been closed for years."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e64ed1",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Orym: The defendant,[p/] the victim,[p/] and Tymora were the only ones there before the body was discovered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afc2a7",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Orym: Plus,[p/] the murder weapon was her sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e43f7f",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "It was a given that Ms. Tymora didn’t do this.[p/] Another person must have shown up at the tavern after Celeste and I left."
}

{
  "id": "line:0148546",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Could it have been the witness who discovered the body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f013b2",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Overflow"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddf76a",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "His testimony was straightforward,[p/] but that’s exactly what would help me."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e6b12",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Celeste was innocent,[p/] so there had to be a flaw in his logic."
}

{
  "id": "line:024d27c",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "I just needed to compare each statement to each piece of evidence in my NOTES."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3030c",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Once I found the contradiction,[p/] I just needed to PRESENT that piece of evidence to the contradicting statement."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f9532",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Player: Objection"
}

{
  "id": "line:0645ea7",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] It's clear that the witness's testimony is contradictory!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00646ed",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: And this piece of evidence proves it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0860f47",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Judge: I fail to see how that proves anything, Mr. Cuthbert..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f48513",
  "node": "OrymCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] I guess you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b569a",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Commander White,[p/] are you sure that the victim was killed using the defendant’s sword?"
}

{
  "id": "line:031b71c",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah...[p/] It’s pretty obvious from the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc53c6",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think I’d have to disagree with you on that."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f5870",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: If your testimony is true,[p/] the defendant’s sword couldn’t have been the murder weapon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd5195",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: What are you talking about, kid?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02d3aa6",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: The sword was inside his body."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fe43a",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: That may be,[p/] but take another look at the Autopsy Report."
}

{
  "id": "line:00059cc",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: It says that the fatal wound contained traces of [b]transmutation[/b] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:052dd67",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: You even testified that the sword was magical."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c12f17",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: So?[p/] What’s your point?"
}

{
  "id": "line:008ac15",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s simple."
}

{
  "id": "line:035be52",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: How could a non-magical blade leave traces of magic in the wound?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0805871",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4250c",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: My client’s sword may look unique,[p/][s/] but it’s entirely non-magical."
}

{
  "id": "line:009c855",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: It couldn’t have left those traces of [b]transmutation[/b] on the wound."
}

{
  "id": "line:0adaeea",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: That doesn’t make a lick of sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d234a",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: If the sword didn’t kill him,[p/] then why was it in the body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f55e20",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: There’s only one reasonable explanation."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f55d3",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: The wound was created magically,[p/][s/] and someone shoved the sword into the wound afterward."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f89ca1",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: And?[p/] That girl's a mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f92588",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: She could’ve easily whacked that old man using magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b167ba",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why would she murder the victim using a spell,[p/] only to then stab him with her sword?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08fa7b6",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: She would just be incriminating herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ad050",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: If anything,[p/][s/] this series of events proves something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:04387e3",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Someone used magic to murder the victim,[p/][s/] then pushed my client’s sword into the wound to frame her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7da1c",
  "node": "AriaRebut",
  "text": "AriaC: Don’t get ahead of yourself, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:065db02",
  "node": "AriaRebut",
  "text": "AriaC: Your Honor,[p/] the defense is suggesting that another person used the sword to frame the defendant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f791e7",
  "node": "AriaRebut",
  "text": "AriaC: But the defendant clearly cast a spell on the sword at the time of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e17cad",
  "node": "AriaRebut",
  "text": "Judge: She cast a spell?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f7301",
  "node": "AriaRebut",
  "text": "AriaC: Commander,[p/] testify as to how magic was used during the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:046e635",
  "node": "AriaRebut",
  "text": "Orym: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:048cfbb",
  "node": "AriaRebut",
  "text": "Orym: Alright, alright...[p/] I see where you’re going with this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0872d6c",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "Orym: The sword itself ain’t magical,[p/] but spells can still be cast on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:058ff2c",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "Orym: That defendant over there?[p/] Her Spell Compendium's got a spell called \"[b]Mage Blade[/b]\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bedf9",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "Orym: She must've cast it on her sword before stabbing the old man."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7a79e",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "Orym: That spell is the reason why we found traces of magic on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c66a97",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "A Spell Compendium listed every spell a mage knew how to cast."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af68db",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "It was a fundamental piece of evidence that proved which spells a mage could and couldn’t use."
}

{
  "id": "line:0916218",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] do you have your Spell Compendium with you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:053562f",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "Celeste: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] My dad was the last person who had it."
}

{
  "id": "line:015a0a9",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "What...?[p/] Why would Flinhart have her Spell Compendium?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba5560",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "Celeste: But he's right.[p/] I know how to cast [b]Mage Blade[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d9ef8",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "Celeste: It’s actually the only spell I know."
}

{
  "id": "line:07599d3",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "AriaC: I would like to add that we found traces of [b]transmutation[/b] magic on the defendant’s sword as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:060ad6f",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "AriaC: As I'm sure the court knows,[p/] magical traces stay on objects for forty-eight hours after a spell is cast on them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0993ab7",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "Those forty-eight hours really tightened the timeline for cases like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1e647",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "Because of that,[p/] crimes needed to be investigated before all the magical traces disappeared from the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f73b5c",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "...It also gave the courts the perfect excuse to push these cases through the system as quickly as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:036b973",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "The commander’s testimony was a lot vaguer this time.[p/] He probably wasn’t expecting to give a second testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbe871",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "PRESSing his statements really helped in situations like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a23112",
  "node": "OrymTest1",
  "text": "Doing that might reveal new pieces of evidence that I could use against him."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cac0f",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you accusing my client of casting a spell and channeling it through her sword?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d421a",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "AriaC: There are a vast number of spells that operate like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0728145",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "AriaC: Spells from the school of [b]transmutation[/b] are almost exclusively channeled through an object."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9b2c3",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "AriaC: Your client clearly learned a spell that would aid in her work as a mercenary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0780a1e",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "AriaC: Speaking of which..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed0264",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"[b]Mage Blade[/b]\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c99d2f",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Celeste: It’s a [b]transmutation[/b] spell that sharpens and empowers my sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:0272f67",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wouldn’t it be excessive for the defendant to use a spell like that on the victim?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d64b50",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Tyrion: He wasn’t wearing any armor or protection at the time of his death."
}

{
  "id": "line:039723c",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "AriaC: The victim and the defendant were in an intense argument."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad11f9",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "AriaC: Perhaps she used the spell in a fit of rage.[p/] Perhaps she simply cast it out of habit."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b5551",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "AriaC: What matters is that the sword undeniably has traces of [b]transmutation[/b] magic on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:054afbe",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why would she go to the trouble of doing that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e13550",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Her sword alone would have been enough to murder a defenseless person."
}

{
  "id": "line:04db682",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Orym: Mages are always looking for an excuse to throw their power around."
}

{
  "id": "line:088eb3c",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Orym: There’s no rhyme or reason to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:04933c6",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Isn’t that just your own personal bias, Commander?"
}

{
  "id": "line:067c36f",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "AriaC: We don’t need to understand why the defendant did what she did."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e118a",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "AriaC: The fact of the matter is that traces of magic were found on the body and the sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a070c",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "AriaC: Do you have any evidence of the contrary, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdee10",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Tyrion: About that...[p/] Spells only leave magical traces on the objects they target,[p/] and those traces are only detectable for forty-eight hours."
}

{
  "id": "line:0472cac",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Tyrion: If my client cast [b]Mage Blade[/b] like you said,[p/] there shouldn’t have been any magical traces on the wound.[p/] There would only be traces on the sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:085e6dc",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Orym: We always find random magical traces at crime scenes.[p/] We can’t always explain each trace we detect."
}

{
  "id": "line:093f4ba",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Tyrion: That sounds more like a failure on the Inquisition’s part than anything else."
}

{
  "id": "line:000568a",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can we really trust that your knights examined the crime scene properly?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d093e0",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Orym: You don’t believe me?[p/] Take a look at this picture."
}

{
  "id": "line:04afdc3",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "I’d seen pictures of dead bodies while studying Ms. Tymora’s past cases,[p/] but there was something unnerving about seeing someone I’d met yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:0498e3a",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "I carefully inspected the photo,[p/] taking great care to keep it out of Celeste’s view."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c88058",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Orym: You can see it here plain as day."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a815c",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Orym: The sword has the highest concentration of [b]transmutation[/b] traces."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebbd11",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "...But why didn’t those traces fully cover the weapon?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0196cb4",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Did the [b]transmutation[/b] spell damage the sword somehow?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdf4db",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Why was this picture not brought to my attention, Orym?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e6078",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Orym: What would be the point of that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce30a3",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Orym: This entire case is open and shut."
}

{
  "id": "line:089b8ff",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "AriaC: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee7142",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "The prosecutor seemed unnerved by something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e40a0f",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Orym: You can see it right in that photo.[p/] She stabbed him right through the chest using [b]Mage Blade[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0242cbc",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "He was right about the photo."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c887e0",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "It clearly showed that he was stabbed from the front."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5581d",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "...So why did that bother me so much?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d3688",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "His testimony was a little bit vague this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:016060c",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "PRESSING his statements might prove useful in a situation like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3324a",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "That would let me ask questions about his testimony and discover more details about the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0adce36",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "I might even be able to obtain new pieces of evidence to use in my cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2b4ab",
  "node": "Orym2Cross",
  "text": "Objection"
}

{
  "id": "line:0454fee",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’m sorry, Commander White,[p/] but you’ve shown us an even more glaring contradiction."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bc4b2",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Orym: Oh, yeah?"
}

{
  "id": "line:030dd71",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: In your testimony,[p/] you said that my client stabbed the victim \"right through the chest\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b515b",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Orym: You can see it right there in that picture."
}

{
  "id": "line:0590da9",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Orym: So, where’s your \"contradiction\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c946a5",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: That’s exactly the problem, Commander."
}

{
  "id": "line:0569b87",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your picture undeniably shows that my client's sword impaled the victim from the front,[p/] but if that’s really true—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad91c2",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: —Why does the Autopsy say that he died from being stabbed in his back?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee7479",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Orym: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06383b7",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "AriaC: Orym![p/][s/] You were supposed to submit [i]everything[/i] you had to me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2d4f8",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "AriaC: Why did you withhold this photo?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:068198b",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Orym: T-[p/][s/]There was no point!"
}

{
  "id": "line:068f2ad",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Orym: She's a mage![p/][s/] It couldn’t have been anyone else!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7c89b",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Murmurs rippled through the gallery.[p/] Even the judge shifted uncomfortably in his seat."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fc1a7",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Our justice system may have been corrupt,[p/] but they’d never get away with such a blatant error."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a8ac4",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Judge: Order![p/][s/] Order in the court!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07b0322",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert, what is the meaning of this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c363bb",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor,[p/] this photo clearly shows my client’s sword impaling him from the front!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4588b",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which means there's only one way for the autopsy to be true!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b95ca",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: The sword would've needed to be inserted into the wound [i]after[/i] the victim had died!"
}

{
  "id": "line:013b6e6",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Orym: T-[p/][s/]That’s crazy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:009049b",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then why don't you enlighten me, Commander White?"
}

{
  "id": "line:005662f",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you think my client impaled the victim hilt-first with her sword?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:061d48e",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Orym: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f470d",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Or do you think she stabbed him through the chest,[p/] removed it,[p/] and then placed her sword in the body to frame herself?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:016be31",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Orym: Well,[p/] [i]that's[/i]—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea507e",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: No.[p/][s/] What happened here is obvious!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d6195",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: The real murderer stuck the sword through the victim’s wound to implicate my client!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07aeb57",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Tyrion: But they made a careless mistake and stuck the sword through the opposite side!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0984917",
  "node": "Orym2Obj",
  "text": "Celeste: You’re actually pretty good at this...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f2097",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "AriaC: It appears I underestimated you,[p/] but you’ve still gotten ahead of yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a64281",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "Judge: I-[p/][s/]Is that so, Ms. Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:027dc59",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Let me ask the defense one question, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0763bec",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "AriaC: If your client didn’t kill Flinhart McCoy,[p/] then who did?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d41cc6",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How should I know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a23028",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "Tyrion: If I'm not mistaken,[p/] it's the Commander's job to figure that out."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d8307",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "AriaC: Oh,[p/] I’m well aware of the Commander’s incompetence,[p/] but one fact still stands."
}

{
  "id": "line:072df48",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "AriaC: There were magical traces on the wound and the sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b520a",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "AriaC: Would you like me to tell you how many mages live in that small town?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0725a",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "I didn't like where she was going with this."
}

{
  "id": "line:097d5ba",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "AriaC: Only one.[p/] The defendant is the only registered mage who lives in Kornhaven."
}

{
  "id": "line:036784c",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "Right...[p/] Kornhaven was a village of farmers.[p/][s/] Celeste was the only mage there!"
}

{
  "id": "line:035b843",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "AriaC: The defendant was also established to have been with the victim minutes before his time of death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0650429",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "AriaC: In addition to that,[p/] I have several witnesses who heard them arguing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0328325",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "AriaC: You,[p/] on the other hand,[p/] can only implicate an unknown assailant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae8643",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "AriaC: I doubt you could even tell me who they are."
}

{
  "id": "line:01443db",
  "node": "AriaCounter",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Even so,[p/] it’s clear that the prosecution can’t reliably prove how the victim was murdered."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e3d70",
  "node": "JudgeSuspend",
  "text": "Judge: Hm...[p/] I can’t say that the prosecution’s evidence is irrefutable,[p/] but the evidence still leans heavily against the defense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0734372",
  "node": "JudgeSuspend",
  "text": "Judge: There are far too many unanswered questions for me to pass a verdict."
}

{
  "id": "line:037b188",
  "node": "JudgeSuspend",
  "text": "Judge: We will give the Inquisition time to investigate the crime scene and clear these unknowns."
}

{
  "id": "line:07709e7",
  "node": "JudgeSuspend",
  "text": "Judge: ...I suggest that they conduct their investigation more thoroughly this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0670f39",
  "node": "JudgeSuspend",
  "text": "Judge: We will resume the trial tomorrow morning.[p/] Court is adjourned."
}

{
  "id": "line:061ca3d",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Hello, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c4b52",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0165e83",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "I tensed as she approached me.[p/] I’d been so focused on Celeste’s case,[p/] I hadn’t even thought about how I’d left things with my mentor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf08e2",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "Scaled Lord...[p/] She had probably been in the gallery too..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec0a4d",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "She must've seen how I froze up during the first cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:0424f77",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Your job is to put your client at ease,[p/] not the other way around."
}

{
  "id": "line:04939f1",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "Ruby: I'm sure she was just snapping you out of it,[p/] but everyone saw her become violent with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:032a66a",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "Ruby: That's not exactly [i]helpful[/i] if you want to prove she's not a violent murderer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0562b61",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "Ruby: Make no mistake.[p/] The prosecution will use that to their advantage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0546320",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What’s wrong with you?[p/] He did fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c9277",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "Ruby: McCoy, if the Inquisition didn’t botch the investigation,[p/] Cuthbert would’ve never been able to buy this much time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0403d31",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "Celeste: In case you’ve forgotten,[p/] he’s my defense attorney,[p/] not you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2b6c0",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "Celeste: I don’t get why he has to take notes from you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3abd5",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...No, she’s right, Celeste.[p/] I need to do better."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed917e",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can’t ever let myself freeze up like that again."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d07bc",
  "node": "RubyLobby",
  "text": "Tyrion: I might not be so lucky next time."
}

{
  "id": "line:013e631",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Ruby: Other than that,[p/] I’ll admit that you did well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3c00f",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Ruby: You cross-examined the Commander adequately,[p/] and you handled Steelwind’s rebuttals as well as you could have."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd3e9a",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "I remembered how Prosecutor Steelwind was glaring at me at the start of the trial..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d34c58",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Even thinking about it was enough to make me nauseous."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a06206",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "\"Steelwind\"...[p/] Why did that name sound so familiar?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f5169",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Wait,[p/] isn’t House Steelwind one of the Four Pillar Families?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0c0ca",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Celeste: That’s right![p/] Lucio Steelwind is the Grand General of Wyverngarde’s military!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0027a56",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Celeste: Hasn't he been caught up in a lot of scandals recently?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c130e",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Ruby: \"Scandals\"?[p/][s/] He's been having people killed by the thousands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9f0f2",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Right...[p/] I remember seeing several articles about him in the Ratholme Gazette."
}

{
  "id": "line:007a7e5",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "In recent years,[p/] groups voicing their grievances against the Crown had begun to surface in the countryside."
}

{
  "id": "line:060978e",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "King Olivier would answer their complaints by unleashing Steelwind’s soldiers on these so-called “insurrectionists”."
}

{
  "id": "line:09816af",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "More often than not,[p/] their peaceful protests turned violent,[p/] leading to bloody retaliations from Lucio's forces."
}

{
  "id": "line:0585d36",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Ruby: And Aria is Lucio Steelwind’s only heir."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0cd20",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Ruby: When I saw her name on the docket,[p/] I wrote her off as a noble roleplaying for fun."
}

{
  "id": "line:01471ae",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Ruby: But she’s good—[p/]better than most of the prosecutors [i]I’ve[/i] faced."
}

{
  "id": "line:097d173",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Ruby: She's taking this seriously,[p/] and with what Flinhart was doing,[p/] I can't help but wonder if the prosecutor is acting on her father's behalf."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e7a25",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you think Prosecutor Steelwind is protecting the real killer?"
}

{
  "id": "line:086d4fb",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Ruby: The Inquisition knights [i]were[/i] the first responders to the scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0090292",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Ruby: Didn't that strike you as odd?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e17c33",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Right.[p/][s/] In a small town like Kornhaven,[p/] the village militia would be the first people there."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e9bc8",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Ruby: For the Inquisition to respond so quickly,[p/] they would've needed to know that magic was used at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:003d1e2",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Ruby: This whole mess feels a little too staged,[p/] and with a [i]Steelwind[/i] involved,[p/] this whole situation reeks of corruption."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df8ce1",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Ruby: I'm sure locking up Flinhart's daughter would send a clear message to his allies."
}

{
  "id": "line:010a108",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "But if that were true,[p/] why did she help us in the dungeons?"
}

{
  "id": "line:025f0ae",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Either way,[p/] this works out in our favor."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e4911",
  "node": "RubyLobby2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't fight the Steelwinds on a battlefield,[p/] but I can fight them in the courtroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0218d1a",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Ruby: On that subject,[p/] I’ve been meaning to give you this."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a919a",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Celeste: My Spell Compendium?"
}

{
  "id": "line:045df24",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Ruby: I grabbed it from the dining room before the Inquisition arrived."
}

{
  "id": "line:0563bb5",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Ruby: They have a bad habit of \"misplacing\" pieces of evidence like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f8dae",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Tyrion: So...[p/] [i]this[/i] is your Spell Compendium,[p/] and it only has one spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fef836",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Celeste: [b]Mage Blade[/b]..."
}

{
  "id": "line:039ff1a",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Ruby: The prosecution will need to prove that [b]Mage Blade[/b] was used in the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0734f29",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Ruby: It will restrict their plan of attack,[p/] which will give you an edge over them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0848ba3",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I still have no idea who actually did this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:068fefa",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste.[p/] I need to talk to you about what your father was doing."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fb778",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "She glanced at the bailiff.[p/] He was looming close,[p/] staring daggers at her."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b4982",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]I should go.[p/] It looks like they can't wait to throw me back into that cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:03fd521",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]Wait,[p/] I still—"
}

{
  "id": "line:042e318",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "She turned away and quickly walked off without another word.[p/] Ms. Tymora just shook her head."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f48ff",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Ruby: She’s practically begging for a conviction at this rate..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02afe84",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Bringing up her late father may have struck a nerve.[p/] I would need to be more delicate next time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f593d2",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I can speak with her in the dungeons later."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc4c70",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right now,[p/] I want to take a look at the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b43541",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Tyrion: With how negligent the Inquisition were,[p/] I doubt they found everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f7011",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Ruby: ...If you’re planning to investigate the crime scene,[p/] you’ll need this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de4511",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "She reached into her coat and pulled out a small, blue Runestone.[p/] I froze for a moment,[p/] starring wide-eyed at it."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bda61",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]Is that—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:061bfda",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Ruby: It’s an Attorney’s Runestone.[p/] I had it commissioned for you after you passed the exam last month."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce8d97",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You’ve had one ready this entire time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f0f1e",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Ruby: Cuthbert,[p/] are you crying?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a52447",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "I wiped my eyes and delicately stored the Runestone in the pocket of my jacket."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d96cb8",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Ruby: You embarrassed them today.[p/] Don’t expect them to be that sloppy again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3bf76",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Ruby: As much as I hate to admit it,[p/] your investigative mind is sharper than mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fc0fd",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Ruby: If anyone can get through this,[p/] it’s you."
}

{
  "id": "line:00960bb",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] Um...[p/][s/] Thank you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05277b8",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "She turned to take a seat at the bench near the courtroom entrance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0ed3b",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "It looked like she would be staying here until the case was over."
}

{
  "id": "line:0418173",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "I tucked Celeste’s Spell Compendium into my jacket."
}

{
  "id": "line:09411cd",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "I hadn’t slept,[p/] and my body still ached from the carriage ride."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b16c2f",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "I still didn't know whether I was truly up to this,[p/] but none of that mattered."
}

{
  "id": "line:03109df",
  "node": "RubyGivesComp",
  "text": "Celeste was counting on me,[p/] and I wouldn't let anyone get away with killing Flinhart—[p/]even if the Steelwinds were involved."
}

{
  "id": "line:0991e78",
  "node": "TavernIntro",
  "text": "The Inquisition had set up a teleportation circle at the crime scene.[p/] As the defense attorney for this case,[p/] I was permitted to use it."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e5e1b",
  "node": "TavernIntro",
  "text": "With it,[p/] I could instantly travel back and forth between the McCoy Tavern and the capital."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d7df7",
  "node": "TavernIntro",
  "text": "It was miles better than having to travel by carriage."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fe60b",
  "node": "TavernIntro",
  "text": "Orym: Oh...[p/] It’s you..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ed279",
  "node": "TavernIntro",
  "text": "Orym: What are you doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:015d527",
  "node": "TavernIntro",
  "text": "Commander White stepped in my way as I approached the tavern entrance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aec2ac",
  "node": "TavernIntro",
  "text": "This time,[p/] I took out my Attorney’s Runestone and PRESENTED it to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b8b78",
  "node": "TavernIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’m the defense attorney in this case.[p/] I have every right to look at the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e991b",
  "node": "TavernIntro",
  "text": "Orym: Whatever...[p/] Just remember,[p/] I've got my eye on you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df52c9",
  "node": "TavernIntro",
  "text": "Orym: ...You can take that rock out of my face now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9f90f",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Bed"
}

{
  "id": "line:0545498",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a fancy-looking bed."
}

{
  "id": "line:071bb6c",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Jolene: Do you like it?[p/] Celeste had it custom-made by someone in the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eed900",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Wouldn’t something like this be really expensive?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0434808",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Jolene: It was.[p/] I was really surprised when she returned from her travels."
}

{
  "id": "line:0feb738",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Jolene: She was making a lot of gold from her job as a mercenary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e41f4a",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Jolene: I’m happy for her,[p/] but I still wish she'd do something less dangerous..."
}

{
  "id": "line:087ae1e",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Door"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae3ed0",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a door leading to the upstairs hallway."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fe918",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Table"
}

{
  "id": "line:007951c",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a table with several chairs.[p/] It’s probably used for entertaining guests."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce2ae2",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "It didn’t look like it's seen much use, though..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab1eeb",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Player: Painting"
}

{
  "id": "line:0753f84",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of a woman with a strange animal.[p/] The text says “Madeline Kipling”."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e63b80",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Jolene: Oh,[p/] I’ve always loved that painting![p/] Celeste brought it back from her travels."
}

{
  "id": "line:09656bc",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Jolene: That girl runs a wildlife sanctuary for endangered species."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8d1ca",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Jolene: I think that creature is called a \"Feykip\".[p/] They live in the swamps of the Eastern Kingdoms."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ee7e5",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "I never knew that creatures like this even existed."
}

{
  "id": "line:00161a5",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Examine",
  "text": "Back"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db3732",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Flinhart McCoy"
}

{
  "id": "line:0799255",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can you tell me more about your husband?[p/] Why did he hate magic so much?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c489f2",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I understand that magic is a symbol of the nobility,[p/] but things sounded different with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0232df7",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s as if he thought Celeste had betrayed him somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:095d725",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: ...I wasn’t there when they were arguing,[p/] but I can only imagine what he said to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:031f21a",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: He’s never had anything good to say about mages,[p/] and I could see how much his words indirectly hurt her."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e5f06",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did something happen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02d07e8",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: ...I don’t really know. [h=\"I don’t trust him enough.|I shouldn't talk about Effie.\" e=\"fs\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:04beab2",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Who was “Effie”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01fcaea",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "“Effie”"
}

{
  "id": "line:025c365",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Does Flinhart’s resentment have something to do with Effie?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5e1ad",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:093d0e2",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: ...How do you know about her?[p/][s/] There shouldn't be any records of what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5d17e",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have my ways of finding out."
}

{
  "id": "line:000995a",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: ...Of course.[p/] You work for Ruby Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:009c667",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: What did she do?[p/] Did she strong-arm one of the neighbors into talking?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03b6c64",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: We don’t need people like her going around Kornhaven and opening up old wounds."
}

{
  "id": "line:097a54e",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0639eb8",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: Flinhart always idolized her,[p/] but I could never stand her methods."
}

{
  "id": "line:09da532",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is this about the rumors?"
}

{
  "id": "line:042ca3a",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: ...”Rumors”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aff283",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: When my mentor started fighting against the justice system,[p/] the nobility started levying accusations of misconduct against her."
}

{
  "id": "line:029be10",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: They spread rumors that she engaged in bribery,[p/] forgery,[p/] and blackmail—[p/]all to discredit her."
}

{
  "id": "line:082cb0f",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: ...Is that really true?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0093560",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: She personally taught me how to defend persecuted mages like your daughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:016c8fe",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: You’ve seen how I defended Celeste.[p/] I’m doing everything honestly and legally."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f5314",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4c71f",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. McCoy,[p/] I know you don’t know who to trust right now,[p/] but I need to know more about Flinhart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b992f4",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right now,[p/] I don’t have any leads as to who might’ve done this."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f99a7",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] ...Okay,[p/] but promise me that you won't mention any of this in court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0186bef",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: I don't want Celeste being dragged into another scandal,[p/] and I sure as hell don't want any more Steelwinds showing up in town."
}

{
  "id": "line:082b9ae",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't make any promises,[p/] but my priority will always be to keep your daughter safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a458b",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: I guess that's as much as I can ask for..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d3775",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Flinhart’s Past"
}

{
  "id": "line:0041b96",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: Effie was Flinhart’s younger sister."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f4107",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: Celeste doesn't know about her.[p/] She died twenty years ago,[p/] and Flinhart never brought her up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0256f1c",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03126a0",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: She was friends with the son of the ruling noble back then,[p/] and he’d always sneak into town to see her. [h=\"...He was so different back then.\" e=\"sa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbe447",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: Effie had always loved magic.[p/] It reminded her of the fairy tales she read growing up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bce6e5",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: He’d always show her his spells by the lake,[p/] all to make her smile."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4e902",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: But he’d been warned not to use his spells without his instructor present."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1af4f",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: ...One day,[p/] he lost control of one of his spells and wounded Effie."
}

{
  "id": "line:0983497",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: We rushed her back into the town,[p/] but it was too late."
}

{
  "id": "line:067e334",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: By the time we could dress her wounds,[p/] she was already gone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0887b6a",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Stories like that were awfully common among the nobility these days..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea076a",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: The next day,[p/] the Arcane Inquisition came to investigate what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:073c43a",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: The boy’s parents used their influence to cover everything up.[p/] They even threatened Flinhart’s family into staying quiet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0085964",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: After that,[p/] they told the town that Effie had been mauled to death by a wolf."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa8590",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: Flinhart all but declared war on the nobility after that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b791d",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: He turned our tavern into a meeting place for commoners who shared his resentment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aacf1b",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: Word spread,[p/] and night after night,[p/] more and more revolutionaries started showing up to his rallies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0feb16d",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: It wasn’t long before they started planning a revolution."
}

{
  "id": "line:0753311",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: They started contacting like-minded groups in the towns nearby.[p/] They were even starting to arm themselves."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c142b2",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: I could only watch as everything unfolded.[p/] I'd heard stories about what the Steelwinds were doing to people like him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be976a",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: I begged him to stop,[p/] so did some of the other townfolk.[p/] We knew he was going to get all of us killed."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b44af",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: ...I was shocked when the knights told me he’d been murdered,[p/] but I wasn’t surprised."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fd444",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I really hoped he’d let go of his anger when Celeste showed up."
}

{
  "id": "line:041bee2",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: He was really starting to change after we adopted her."
}

{
  "id": "line:019f897",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste McCoy"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f0e26",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can you tell me more about Celeste?[p/] How did she become a part of your family?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b29f05",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: It all happened nineteen years ago,[p/] a year after Effie’s death."
}

{
  "id": "line:06997e6",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: We were closing one night when we found a baby with white hair abandoned in the dining area."
}

{
  "id": "line:07374f4",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: We waited weeks for her parents to come by,[p/] but no one ever came looking for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c510b",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: We named her “Celeste”,[p/] after the full moon that was out that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0075efa",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: We’d always wanted a child,[p/] so I thought she must have been a gift from the Scaled Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a309b7",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: But one day,[p/] I spotted Celeste practicing her magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b9c21",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: I think that’s when I realized that a noble must have abandoned her at our inn."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6996c",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: I didn’t care, though.[p/] I loved her all the same.[p/] Flinhart did too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1b5e7",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] You [i]knew[/i] that she was a mage this entire time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a15853",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: I did.[p/] You haven't known her very long,[p/] but she's a terrible liar."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4574a",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: Flinhart must have noticed it too,[p/] but I think that he didn’t want to believe it. [h=\"It’s my fault.|I should have forced him to see the truth.\" e=\"s\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a45c4",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Flinhart and Celeste"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbc107",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I spoke with Celeste earlier,[p/] and she believes her father died hating her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6b7d2",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: What?![p/][s/] He loved her more than anything in the world!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8bc30",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: They must’ve been really close."
}

{
  "id": "line:0711aea",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: More than anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:017bdeb",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: ...Do you want to hear a story?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1dadc",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: Celeste had just come from the Eastern Kingdoms.[p/] She wouldn’t stop talking about this foreign drink that she loved."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa4fa5",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: Flinhart did everything he could to have it shipped here.[p/] He even called in a bunch of favors to do it."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f2df5",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: In the end,[p/] he was only able to get a single bottle of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a304c4",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is it really that rare?"
}

{
  "id": "line:076f9b0",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: It’s a product of the Eastern Kingdoms,[p/] and it’s hard to import anything from outside of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a418f",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: I wouldn’t be surprised if it were the only bottle of Lotus Juice in this region."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e19d7",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Wait a minute,[p/] “Lotus Juice”?"
}

{
  "id": "line:084ca8b",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is this the bottle that Flinhart bought?"
}

{
  "id": "line:019ba82",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: Oh no...[p/] He was going to surprise her with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d869d",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: I wondered where it had disappeared to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a902d8",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I found it shattered on the floor of the dining area."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dea00a",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: ...That’s strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8d6e7",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: Celeste would always help herself to our pantry,[p/] so he was hiding it in our room."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f6cc3",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Really?[p/] When was the last time you saw it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3b039",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: It was right before I left the house that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0172e09",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Talk",
  "text": "Jolene: It would’ve been in his room before their argument."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a47e0",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Runestone"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b511b",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: Oh?[p/] What’s this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e3a5b",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s an Attorney’s Runestone.[p/] It identifies me as a certified attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:07be38b",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: Wow.[p/] You must have worked very hard to get that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0608439",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah,[p/] it also has a magical tool that lets me take pictures of crime scenes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e571b3",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: Wow,[p/] that’s amazing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae6b49",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Something about her overly enthusiastic tone reminded me of my late mother."
}

{
  "id": "line:046a37c",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: I can’t thank you enough for defending Celeste.[p/] I don’t know what we would’ve done without you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0092d3d",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: I'm so sorry she slapped you like that.[p/] I don't know what got into her."
}

{
  "id": "line:08721d3",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's fine...[p/] It helped me more than anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a08957",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "I just hoped I would be enough."
}

{
  "id": "line:042f066",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Celeste"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce7b3f",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: Why is this happening to us...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0188682",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: I can't imagine how Celeste is taking all of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d7c80",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry...[p/] I wish there was more I could do..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01386c3",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: She must be feeling so alone right now.[p/] I just want to see her again and let her know that everything is going to be okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:08df967",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: You will.[p/] I promise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0476f3d",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Garrick"
}

{
  "id": "line:0facaa1",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I actually saw Garrick Pierce here earlier.[p/] Did he say anything to you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc0961",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: No...[p/] I didn't even know he was here."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ba554",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: ...Maybe it's for the best.[p/] The Gary we knew is probably long gone by now."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f5657",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "“Gary\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0255b1c",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Flinhart Autopsy|Photo|Flinhart"
}

{
  "id": "line:0978680",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "She'd been through enough.[p/] I shouldn’t remind her about Flinhart unless I really needed to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eda478",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "CelComp"
}

{
  "id": "line:095831a",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: If only I'd told Flinhart about Celeste's magic...[p/] We could have avoided all of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0929948",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: You shouldn't torture yourself like that.[p/] No one could have predicted this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8deff",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Power|Power2"
}

{
  "id": "line:091eb8f",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I heard that you've been using artificery to light up your house."
}

{
  "id": "line:000a710",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: Flinhart actually hated the idea,[p/] but Celeste was so excited to buy it for us.[p/] He just couldn't say no."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f317ba",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: It is a bit of a problem, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:05eeae6",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: Sometimes the other townsfolk vandalize it when we’re out."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c6ff1",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Bottle3"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d6b15",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: It's such a shame.[p/] Flinhart was really looking forward to giving Celeste the Lotus Juice."
}

{
  "id": "line:012e08e",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "It was probably his last gift to her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bda60",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "It's too bad that it's become part of the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:06156a3",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Effie"
}

{
  "id": "line:014ddf2",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm so sorry about what happened to Effie."
}

{
  "id": "line:070c2ac",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: That must have been traumatizing."
}

{
  "id": "line:025d9f7",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: These things happen more commonly than you'd think."
}

{
  "id": "line:0305633",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Occupation|Occupation2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0311452",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm still surprised that Celeste is a mercenary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6f804",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: She doesn’t exactly look like one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e44134",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: Then you haven’t known her long enough."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6ca1b",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: Even when she was a kid,[p/] she was always picking fights with people."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f0b5e",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: She's definitely Flinhart's daughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:091238a",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Default"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c55024",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can you tell me more about this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:081735b",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Present",
  "text": "Jolene: I’m sorry,[p/] but I don't know much about these things."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c40fc",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "I slid Celeste’s key into the lock and turned it,[p/] allowing the door to creak open."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c6368",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "I heard the fumbling of objects on the other side.[p/] Someone else was there."
}

{
  "id": "line:080ccbf",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "Jolene: I’ve already told you [s/]“[i]knights[/i]” everything that I know!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cea28c",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "Jolene: What more do you—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05bfac4",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "Jolene: Oh?[p/][s/] It’s you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:038df3e",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "Something about the way the woman carried herself reminded me of Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e45d0b",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "I knew she was adopted,[p/] but she clearly took after her mother."
}

{
  "id": "line:072dfc0",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "I recognized the same bubbly warmth in the woman's posture[p/]—tempered with a subtle hint of maturity."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fee99",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Sorry if I'm intruding,[p/] but what are you doing in Celeste’s room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01bd200",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "Jolene: Oh, I’m so sorry.[p/] I'm Jolene.[p/] I'm Celeste's mother."
}

{
  "id": "line:065316b",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "Jolene: I can’t thank you enough for everything that you’ve done for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:05dc47c",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "Jolene: I really appreciate you sticking by her after she hit you like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:07741ad",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]It’s fine, really."
}

{
  "id": "line:0867ac2",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "I kind of deserved it for freezing up like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad719c",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "Anyways,[p/] Jolene was Flinhart’s wife.[p/] That meant that she knew him better than anyone else,[p/] even Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e40580",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you mind if I ask you some questions?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0320b4d",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "Jolene: ...O-[p/][s/]Of course![p/][s/] I’ll do anything to help! [h=\"He’s helped Celeste a lot.|But can I really trust him?\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb1b6c",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "The Eye revealed a hint of fear and distrust from her."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a9bf1",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "I’d investigated the tavern as much as I could,[p/] but there was still one last thing I needed to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:077ac63",
  "node": "CelesteRoom_Check",
  "text": "It was time to head back to the dungeons and TALK to Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ca2c4",
  "node": "CelesteFail",
  "text": "Celeste: I really appreciate you trying to make me feel better."
}

{
  "id": "line:032914b",
  "node": "CelesteFail",
  "text": "Celeste: But I know the truth...[p/] Nothing will change that."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a07f4",
  "node": "CelesteFail",
  "text": "Damn it all...[p/] I still wasn’t getting through to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b62f6a",
  "node": "CelesteArgue",
  "text": "That final argument with her father would be a lasting scar on Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b4f20",
  "node": "CelesteArgue",
  "text": "Throughout this entire investigation,[p/] I’d learned how much they cared for each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe4205",
  "node": "CelesteArgue",
  "text": "I couldn't leave things as they were."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e6318",
  "node": "CelesteArgue",
  "text": "Yes"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3454b",
  "node": "CelesteArgue",
  "text": "No"
}

{
  "id": "line:016da5d",
  "node": "CelesteArgue",
  "text": "Celeste: I know you’re just trying to make me feel better,[p/] but my dad has hated mages."
}

{
  "id": "line:05677bc",
  "node": "CelesteArgue",
  "text": "Celeste: I knew that better than anyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0238edb",
  "node": "CelesteArgue1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What is this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0107834",
  "node": "CelesteArgue1",
  "text": "Tyrion: This is the reason why your father hated magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0646613",
  "node": "CelesteArgue1",
  "text": "Celeste: That doesn't really make any sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6b452",
  "node": "CelesteArgue1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I guess you're right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de1e26",
  "node": "CelesteArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don’t know if it’s my place to say this,[p/] but there’s a reason why your father hated magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c17051",
  "node": "CelesteArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Decades ago,[p/] he had a sister.[p/] She was killed by a mage in a tragic accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da0150",
  "node": "CelesteArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's why he resents magic so much.[p/] It ripped away someone that he loved dearly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b77d55",
  "node": "CelesteArgue2",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]I never knew that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee76e2",
  "node": "CelesteArgue2",
  "text": "Celeste: But that just proves it then, doesn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4ef59",
  "node": "CelesteArgue2",
  "text": "Celeste: I knew how he felt about it,[p/] but I didn’t care.[p/] I just wanted to get away from my life here."
}

{
  "id": "line:054f0ac",
  "node": "CelesteArgue2",
  "text": "Celeste: He had every right to be angry at me.[p/] I was being selfish."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0a88b",
  "node": "CelesteArgue3",
  "text": "Occupation2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0407d41",
  "node": "CelesteArgue3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're not a selfish person, Celeste,[p/] and this proves it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2c49b",
  "node": "CelesteArgue3",
  "text": "Celeste: Thank you,[p/] but I don't really see how that proves anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d0011",
  "node": "CelesteArgue3",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Sorry...[p/] I meant to show you something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:09560ea",
  "node": "CelesteArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: But you didn’t learn magic just to benefit yourself, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:0568799",
  "node": "CelesteArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You used it to support your family.[p/] You gave them hope when the nobility shut down their tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:04da3c1",
  "node": "CelesteArgue4",
  "text": "Celeste: T-[p/][s/]That’s—"
}

{
  "id": "line:054d096",
  "node": "CelesteArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You didn’t have a choice."
}

{
  "id": "line:069afb1",
  "node": "CelesteArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You had a gift,[p/] and you used it to your advantage.[p/] That’s not selfish."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca9d54",
  "node": "CelesteArgue4",
  "text": "Celeste: Shut up..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05db8be",
  "node": "CelesteArgue4",
  "text": "Celeste: Just shut up, Tyrion! [h=\"Why won’t you leave me alone?!\" e=\"saf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da7c26",
  "node": "CelesteArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste—"
}

{
  "id": "line:03117bf",
  "node": "CelesteArgue4",
  "text": "Celeste: You don't know anything!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c0563",
  "node": "CelesteArgue4",
  "text": "Celeste: You weren’t there![p/][s/] You didn’t hear what he said to me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f976dc",
  "node": "CelesteArgue4",
  "text": "Celeste: You didn’t see the way he was looking at me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:019b50d",
  "node": "CelesteArgue4",
  "text": "Celeste: I knew him![p/][s/] I knew him better than anyone!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de5b94",
  "node": "CelesteArgue4",
  "text": "Celeste: He loved me![p/][s/] He took care of me,[p/][s/] and I threw it all away!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a35a1",
  "node": "CelesteArgue4",
  "text": "Celeste: I [i]chose[/i] to become a mage![p/][s/] He would never forgive me for that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:066c978",
  "node": "CelesteArgue5",
  "text": "Bottle3|Photo"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6bd4a",
  "node": "CelesteArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste...[p/] Please calm down."
}

{
  "id": "line:005e759",
  "node": "CelesteArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: This proves that your father didn't hate you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0643de7",
  "node": "CelesteArgue5",
  "text": "Celeste: Just go away.[p/] Leave me alone..."
}

{
  "id": "line:039ab1b",
  "node": "CelesteArgue5",
  "text": "That didn’t work.[p/] I needed to try something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0609aa1",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Take a look at this picture, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c02f0d",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: What's this...?[p/] Broken glass?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e2be2",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] That bottle..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06da1f2",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a bottle of Lotus Juice.[p/] These shards were on the floor of the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0351748",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: What?[p/] That can't be true..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f586de",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: They don’t even sell it in Wyverngarde..."
}

{
  "id": "line:038bd69",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your father called in a bunch of favors to have it imported for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0446f60",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...He did?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01de5d6",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: He didn’t hate you, Celeste.[p/] He imported your favorite drink just to make you happy."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c75b4",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:04977aa",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste:  No...[p/] That still doesn’t change anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cbc08",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: If he did that all for me,[p/] it was before he knew the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0304e3d",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: That’s not true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bba79d",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: Stop acting like you know anything about us![p/][s/] You only met us yesterday!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fab662",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: How could you know how he felt about me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04458df",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: Don’t you think I [i]want[/i] to believe you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01380d1",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: I know the truth![p/][s/] He hated me![p/][s/] He hated me just like he hated every other mage!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a79fa",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] your mother said the bottle was stowed in her room,[p/] but I found it shattered in the dining area near where the murder happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:063b792",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: He was holding it when he died.[p/] That means he retrieved it [i]after[/i] your argument."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff8529",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...So?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0866595",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]So[/i] why would he have your gift if he was still angry at you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:092717e",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: ... [h=\"No...|Why would he have it...?\" e=\"sfh\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb787c",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's because he loved you, Celeste![p/][s/] He knew he'd lost his temper and hurt you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03b3b9e",
  "node": "CelesteArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: So he was going to use that gift to apologize to you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0985c15",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Flinhart: ...I still don’t like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:053092b",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Flinhart: My daughter...[p/] working as a mercenary, of all things."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e6892",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Celeste: Come on, Dad.[p/] You know I can handle myself out there."
}

{
  "id": "line:060124d",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Flinhart: ...You shouldn’t have to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecdd41",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Celeste: They closed the inn.[p/] If I didn't do this,[p/] we wouldn't have made it through the last few winters."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bb5ce",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Celeste: I know you're worried,[p/] but I can do this.[p/] No one can ever beat me in a fight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5ecf8",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Flinhart: ...Just be careful.[p/] I don’t know what I’d do if anything happened to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d74b3",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Celeste: Don’t worry.[p/] Just let me do this for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:016a4b4",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Celeste: You and Mom both took me in.[p/] You took care of me for my entire life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc0dbe",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Celeste: I...[p/] know I’m not really your daughter,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d51676",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Flinhart: ...Why would you say something like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a9602",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]I’m sorry...[p/][s/] I didn’t mean—"
}

{
  "id": "line:019495d",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Flinhart: Did those idiots in the town say that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc964f",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Flinhart: Tell me who![p/][s/] I'll go knock them out right now!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4a20a",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Celeste: Dad![p/][s/] No one said that![p/][s/] it's just—"
}

{
  "id": "line:037efa2",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Flinhart: ...You’re a McCoy.[p/][s/] You’ve always been a McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afff32",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Flinhart: You’re our daughter...[p/] I won’t let anyone say otherwise,[p/] especially you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acf905",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/][s/]Okay..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0644a86",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Thanks, Dad.[p/] I love you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab21db",
  "node": "CelesteArgue7",
  "text": "Flinhart: ...I love you too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0275e4b",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Celeste: How could I ever think that—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:092646a",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "She trailed off.[p/] She had barely been keeping it together throughout the whole ARGUMENT."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f26687",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "But her voice began to break,[p/] and she broke along with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:059c3ed",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "She paused for a moment, trembling.[p/] Then she slowly fell against me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5f388",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "She gripped me tightly,[p/] everything from the last few days finally crashing down on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0611577",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "I was sure I was the last person she wanted to comfort her,[p/] but I was the only one there."
}

{
  "id": "line:039c978",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "She’d held back her grief for this long.[p/] She was strong,[p/] much stronger than I had been."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abba63",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "I hesitated,[p/] unsure of how to respond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a22976",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "I just held her as her quiet sobs echoed softly throughout the cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9dbaa",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste...[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:01339e7",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm sorry,[p/] but please don't talk right now..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a06153",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "I did as she asked.[p/] I wasn't sure if it was enough,[p/] but I held her tightly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f16635",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you feeling better?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff7d44",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] Thanks..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c6367",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "She wiped her eyes.[p/] They were still red."
}

{
  "id": "line:037387f",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "But she smiled at me,[p/] and it wasn't forced this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0b581",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0110639",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you need water?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0487667",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: I just thought—[p/] I figured you lost...[p/] fluids and I thought..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a502e9",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You might be dehydrated?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fea8a4",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "...What was I saying?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e714b4",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Celeste snorted out a laugh."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e6a5b",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "I felt silly,[p/] but something about seeing her laugh left me flustered."
}

{
  "id": "line:042eeda",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1c38b",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Celeste: Is everything really going to be okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a81dc",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: It will be.[p/] I'll get you that acquittal no matter what."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b794a",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Man, king, or god?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e4298",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]*chuckle*[/i][p/] Yes.[p/] Man,[p/] king,[p/] or god."
}

{
  "id": "line:0343f9f",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "She giggled to herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:034118f",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...A-[p/][s/]Anyways,[p/] you should rest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7e750",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: The trial is going to resume soon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f70a46",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "I learned as much as I could about what happened,[p/] but I had to assume that Steelwind had done the same."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdade2",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "Who knew what the prosecution had in store for us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa76ba",
  "node": "CelesteArgue8",
  "text": "I just had to hope that I'd stacked the board in my favor."
}

{
  "id": "line:04efe3c",
  "node": "CelesteArgue9",
  "text": "Aria: Has Pierce given you all of the details, Rudolf?[p/] Will you remember them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:085c246",
  "node": "CelesteArgue9",
  "text": "Rhys: Yes.[p/] My notes are pristine,[p/] and I pride myself on my eidetic memory."
}

{
  "id": "line:094d781",
  "node": "CelesteArgue9",
  "text": "Aria: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:053ab3a",
  "node": "CelesteArgue9",
  "text": "Aria: Just so there are no misunderstandings,[p/] I do not approve of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:06aea50",
  "node": "CelesteArgue9",
  "text": "Garrick: You said it yourself, Lady Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:059e448",
  "node": "CelesteArgue9",
  "text": "Garrick: The evidence proves that I couldn’t have murdered Flinhart,[p/] which leaves the bastard child as the only suspect."
}

{
  "id": "line:063687f",
  "node": "CelesteArgue9",
  "text": "Garrick: We don’t know what sort of tricks Tymora’s stooge may pull tomorrow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1dc8e",
  "node": "CelesteArgue9",
  "text": "Garrick: Just see this as a way of securing a just verdict."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea34ae",
  "node": "CelesteArgue9",
  "text": "Garrick: ...There will be no need for your father to intervene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd190b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "Door"
}

{
  "id": "line:0983ea3",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "There was a steel door that led into the cell.[p/] A magical mechanism covered by a steel box was placed over the lock."
}

{
  "id": "line:000b722",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "...I couldn’t help but notice that the mechanism had a dent in it."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f49b0",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "It looked like the impact had come from within the cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bf2cc",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "Torch"
}

{
  "id": "line:073ac12",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "Lit torches were hanging on the cell walls.[p/] It seemed a bit irresponsible to light a fire in here."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bd41e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "But prisoner safety was probably the last thing on the Inquisition’s mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0061ef1",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "Window"
}

{
  "id": "line:028b5a7",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "The cell had a barred window.[p/] The bars were rusted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab4fb5",
  "node": "Dungeon_Examine",
  "text": "If a prisoner tried to escape,[p/] there would be a three-story drop to freedom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9dff5",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Flinhart's Hatred (ARGUMENT)"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b8553",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "The Trial"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e269c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I’m really sorry for what happened today."
}

{
  "id": "line:06805ed",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, it all ended up okay in the end, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0513887",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "That was unusually forgiving.[p/] If she hadn't calmed me down,[p/] the trial may have ended very differently."
}

{
  "id": "line:086b02b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I still don’t understand, though.[p/] Why were there so many traces of magic at the crime scene?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b9912",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you cast [b]Mage Blade[/b] on your sword that day?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0defa48",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I used it when I was training last week.[p/] Is that where those traces came from?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c4fc4",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] Magical traces only last for forty-eight hours.[p/] After that,[p/] they disappear completely."
}

{
  "id": "line:0497ee4",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not to mention that spells only leave traces of magic on the objects that they are cast on."
}

{
  "id": "line:00872fd",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if the sword made physical contact with the body,[p/] the traces shouldn’t have spread to the wound."
}

{
  "id": "line:04eb584",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Really?[p/] What does that mean, then?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03cc1c5",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I don’t know."
}

{
  "id": "line:051b744",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: The floor next to the body had a strange texture to it, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b43f3",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: If the killer used a [b]transmutation[/b] spell,[p/] it may have changed your sword and the surrounding floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a589c3",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: That doesn’t make any sense, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4cb2c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "The Unbreakable Sword"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a1898",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know my theory sounds far-fetched,[p/] but the traces were only on parts of the sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4c45b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: That must mean that the outer layer of the sword must have broken off during the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:083ac35",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: But my sword can't be damaged like that,[p/] even when [b]transmutation[/b] magic is used on it.[p/] That’s the whole reason why I have it."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c8dcd",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: How can you be so sure?"
}

{
  "id": "line:095af49",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Back when I was traveling,[p/] I’d always break my weapons by swinging them too hard."
}

{
  "id": "line:0228b0b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: They’d end up breaking in two or three swings—[p/]maybe four if it was well-made."
}

{
  "id": "line:085d5ce",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "...How much force was she swinging these weapons with?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03984e7",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: That sword was a gift from one of my clients."
}

{
  "id": "line:059caba",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: He said it was specially carved from the bones of a Purple Worm.[p/] [b]Transmutation[/b] spells can't damage them."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c2f99",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I’ve had it for years,[p/] and it doesn’t have a single chip in it.[p/] I don't even need to sharpen it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f24fcc",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Where did you get this sword again?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0938d",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Um...[p/] The Eastern Kingdoms..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0183d70",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Isn’t travel outside of Wyverngarde illegal?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1c85e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Mercenaries don’t have a lot more legitimate options for work in Wyverngarde.[p/] I did what I had to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce549e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "I doubted I’d be able to contact the sword’s maker in time,[p/] if at all.[p/] I would just have to take her word for it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0225e2c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "But if what she was saying was true,[p/] why weren't the traces of [b]transmutation[/b] magic covering the entire sword?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0751e47",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could you tell me more about your father?"
}

{
  "id": "line:076b0e4",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’m sorry.[p/] I know this must be difficult for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eba54d",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I remember how you two were yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:019b1c9",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Is this really going to help?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3341c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Knowing more about him could help me figure out who actually did this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7cf6d",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Okay..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2e246",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I was adopted by the McCoys when I was a baby,[p/] but they always treated me like I was part of their family."
}

{
  "id": "line:07de4e9",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: The townsfolk would always shoo me away.[p/] They didn’t want anything to do with a “noble bastard”."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de6443",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: My dad got into a bunch of fights with them over that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4a60d",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ... [h=\"But I had to go and ruin everything...\" e=\"s\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:049891e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: He was a voice of dissidence,[p/] wasn't he?[p/] Did you share his views?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3f55d",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I...[p/] knew he hated the nobility,[p/] but I didn't know about his rallies until just recently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd926b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: If I knew how much danger his life was in,[p/] I'd have never left Wyverngarde.[p/] I think he knew that."
}

{
  "id": "line:010aed8",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: If I'd been there that night,[p/] he'd still be— [h=\"It's all my fault...\" e=\"s\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce224e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's not your fault.[p/] No one could have expected that."
}

{
  "id": "line:083f14c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "...I felt sorry for her,[p/] but I really needed to know more."
}

{
  "id": "line:027a380",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Any witnesses?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0376e5e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I could hear your argument from my room last night..."
}

{
  "id": "line:068fa48",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your neighbours must have overheard it, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:09850cd",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did any of them come by to check up on you two?[p/] They might have seen the person who did this."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e8105",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I doubt it.[p/] Even if they did see something,[p/] they wouldn't testify for someone like me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f76dcd",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why?[p/] I thought your father was a key figure among the dissidents."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a8092",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] But all of his supporters come from the neighbouring towns."
}

{
  "id": "line:0794945",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Everyone [i]inside[/i] the village hates our family."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e66ba",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: People could tell I was adopted.[p/] It's not as if I look like either of my parents."
}

{
  "id": "line:0541254",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Rumors spread about how some noble lord must've had a tryst with my mom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7b686",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: They were wrong, obviously,[p/] but it's hard to stop a rumor like that when it spreads."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a1e5e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's terrible..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c5758",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: It's fine.[p/] I stopped caring about it years ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f64736",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Things were manageable before,[p/] but things got worse when my dad started speaking out against the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc98fd",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: He wasn't just a pariah at that point.[p/] He was drawing a lot of attention to Kornhaven."
}

{
  "id": "line:0910701",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Everyone's heard the rumors about what the Grand General is doing in villages like ours."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ed8df",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: The neighbours tried to threaten my dad to stop, and when that didn't work, they started vandalizing our tavern.[p/] They'd even steal my parents' supplies."
}

{
  "id": "line:00925de",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I had to come back to Wyverngarde because some of the other villagers broke into the tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:02066cf",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...They were cowards.[p/] They thought they could scare your dad into stopping."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1903e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: They were scared.[p/] My dad [i]was[/i] painting a giant target on this region."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bdcc7",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: It's not as if the kingdom would care if a village like ours were destroyed."
}

{
  "id": "line:099ab86",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "...She wasn't wrong.[p/] Stories of Lucio Steelwind were circulating in the papers for months."
}

{
  "id": "line:017ca60",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Even with that,[p/] he still stood at the top of this kingdom.[p/] There were no real consequences."
}

{
  "id": "line:04426c7",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "The Argument"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d12fc0",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could you tell me why Flinhart was so angry at you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:095d55d",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i] For as long as I can remember,[p/] my dad has hated magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e9d2d",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: If you even mentioned it around him,[p/] he’d fly into a rage about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1a0f3",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And you were born a mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2713e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Ever since our tavern closed,[p/] my family’s been in a lot of debt."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1347e",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Fighting always came naturally to me,[p/] so I became a mercenary and learned how to use magic to help me fight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5c204",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Most of Wyverngarde's mages are in the nobility.[p/] People will pay a lot for a soldier who can use arcane magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a6352",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "...So [i]that's[/i] why she was a mercenary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fabaab",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: Last night,[p/] my dad found my Spell Compendium."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f0c30",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: When I saw him holding it,[p/] I finally came clean to him,[p/] and that set him off."
}

{
  "id": "line:030ed9c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: He shouted at me.[p/] He told me that I’d betrayed him and everything he stood for."
}

{
  "id": "line:09142aa",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I can't imagine how that must have felt."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de6016",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I deserved it...[p/] I knew how much he hated magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd2448",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: He was fighting for what he believed in,[p/] and I wasn't even there to protect him."
}

{
  "id": "line:02243fb",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Don’t say that.[p/] You couldn't have known what would happen."
}

{
  "id": "line:058b38a",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’m sure he still loved you.[p/] He just lost his temper."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e8627",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: No... [p/]I could see it in his eyes.[p/] He hated me. [h=\"And he died hating me...\" e=\"as\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c47b8b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "I felt a sharp pain in my chest as I read that,[p/] but I didn’t say anything more."
}

{
  "id": "line:029d295",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Locked Door"
}

{
  "id": "line:036adbd",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...There’s a locked room in the tavern.[p/] It's at the very end of the hallway upstairs."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a87af",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Inquisition probably searched it already,[p/] but it’s the only room I haven’t seen yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d31c5",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: At the end of the hallway?[p/] I think that’s my room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdae26",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you know how I could get in there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07fa7d7",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I’m your lawyer.[p/] I’m not going to do anything strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f496f",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: ...S-[p/][s/]Sorry,[p/] you’re right."
}

{
  "id": "line:01de312",
  "node": "Dungeon_Talk",
  "text": "Celeste: I always keep the key on me.[p/] You can use this to get inside."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bc6b9",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, what’s that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09dc2d7",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s an Attorney’s Runestone.[p/] It proves that I’m a certified attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c664a",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s fitted with artificery.[p/][s/] I can use it to take pictures of evidence and crime scenes!"
}

{
  "id": "line:024d380",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: You seem...[p/] really excited about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7210c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’ve just wanted one since I was a child.[p/] I can’t believe I finally have one."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e853c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Oh, that’s nice.[p/] I'm happy for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0619870",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "She was trying to be positive,[p/] but there were clearly more important things on her mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:02be364",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "I straightened my tie and stowed the Runestone back in my jacket."
}

{
  "id": "line:097a852",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Flinhart|Flinhart Autopsy|Photo"
}

{
  "id": "line:02bf57b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "I shouldn't show this to her.[p/] She's already been through enough."
}

{
  "id": "line:062ddd5",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "I shouldn't remind her about her father more than I needed to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1f481",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Sword"
}

{
  "id": "line:0efbb0c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: This is a pretty strange sword.[p/] I've never seen anything like it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0319cad",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you like it?[p/] It was a gift from an Ixian lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e73b05",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I’d like to remind you that travel outside of Wyverngarde is illegal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abab60",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: You shouldn’t make a habit of telling people where you got it from."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffc457",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah, yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05078c8",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste's Spell Compendium|Mage Blade"
}

{
  "id": "line:04c0196",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: [b]Mage Blade[/b]..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe22d3",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: It's a spell that magically sharpens my sword so that it can cut through plate armor."
}

{
  "id": "line:078dcb3",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Did you find yourself using this spell a lot?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d569f",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, it's not just for plate armor.[p/] I can cut through all kinds of things with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d52ffb",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Trees,[p/] boulders,[p/] ballistas,[p/] fortified gates—[p/]it cuts through most of those things like butter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edf7ca",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "...I was really starting to wonder what kind of life she led before today."
}

{
  "id": "line:056a811",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I didn't expect to find artificery in a village like yours."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2ca02",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] I bought it for my family to make their lives easier,[p/] but I think it just made things more complicated."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c82736",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Honestly,[p/] I was hoping it would make my dad hate magic less,[p/] but it malfunctioned a lot."
}

{
  "id": "line:06da3be",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: He’d get so angry every time it stopped working.[p/] He really hated the thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:061f91c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] Without an Arcane Power Cell,[p/] those lights aren't very useful."
}

{
  "id": "line:05327cf",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I don't know why he kept trying to use it when he hated it so much."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ef3f2",
  "node": "Dungeon_Present",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh...[p/] I don't really know what to say about that.[p/] Sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:0714959",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "I returned to the dungeons,[p/] but Celeste’s cell was empty."
}

{
  "id": "line:0048751",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "The Inquisition must’ve still been questioning her.[p/] I would need to come back later."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c6f29",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "I arrived back at the dungeons.[p/] Celeste was huddled down in the corner of her cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0173f09",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "She noticed me,[p/] and the weight from her shoulders seemed to lift,[p/] if only for a moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e9f0b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Hi..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0ab8b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "She had avoided me before,[p/] but I doubt she had seen many friendly faces since the trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:02cd025",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hi,[p/] I can’t stay for long."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6ddd5",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I just need to ask you some questions about the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0988610",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6f4c0",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, you’re back.[p/] Did you forget something?"
}

{
  "id": "line:064b93b",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...There was one last thing that I wanted to talk to you about."
}

{
  "id": "line:08acca3",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I wanted to talk to you about the argument you had with Flinhart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e67321",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "I knew what it was like to lose a parent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0354e0d",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "I’d never be able to carry that burden if I thought my mother had died hating me."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fe37f",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know he was angry at you,[p/] but after everything I’ve heard about you two,[p/] I know that he still loved you."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ed0a6",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1e17c",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even in his final moments,[p/] I’m sure that he still cared for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad7cb6",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "Celeste: I... [h=\"Shut up...|You don't know what you're talking about.\" e=\"as\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:039845a",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "It looked like it wouldn’t be that simple, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e7019",
  "node": "Dungeon_Check",
  "text": "I would need to PERSUADE her if I wanted her to believe me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c892dc",
  "node": "GarrickArgue",
  "text": "Garrick: I’ll tell you exactly what I have to say, you commoner!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e6e80",
  "node": "GarrickArgue",
  "text": "Garrick: [i]I’m[/i] not the one on trial, here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0175a75",
  "node": "GarrickArgue",
  "text": "Garrick: We’re here because that bastard child didn’t know her place!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07078fb",
  "node": "GarrickArgue",
  "text": "Garrick: That girl used our holy arts to murder her father because she lacked a noble's temperament!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bbb39",
  "node": "GarrickArgue1",
  "text": "Conjure Light|Map3"
}

{
  "id": "line:0be3fa6",
  "node": "GarrickArgue1",
  "text": "No...[p/] That wasn't right."
}

{
  "id": "line:035af35",
  "node": "GarrickArgue1",
  "text": "He claimed to have witnessed the whole murder,[p/] but I’ve already proved that he didn’t in the last testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8cdab",
  "node": "GarrickArgue1",
  "text": "All I had to do was show the evidence that proved him wrong."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f8c69",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And how, pray tell, did you see “everything\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7d206",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you recall,[p/] you testified that you only took a single step inside the inn."
}

{
  "id": "line:057b8c7",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: However,[p/] you would've needed to be within 15ft to see my client with [b]Conjure Light[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2a8ba",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Garrick: This again?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:075f1ac",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Garrick: If you’re going to keep treading on that one detail,[p/][s/] then I admit it![p/][s/] I stepped further into the inn!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7240f",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Garrick: I kept that out of my testimony![p/][s/] All because I knew that you and Tymora would use it against me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:093552d",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Judge: L-[p/][s/]Lord Pierce!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03939bf",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But you didn’t just withhold that detail from your testimony, did you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd628b",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You testified the contrary![p/][s/] You committed perjury, Pierce![p/][s/] Plain and simple!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d7747",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Garrick: That’s—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04c0c8e",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And let’s not stop there![p/] For your story to be true,[p/] you would have needed to be within 15ft of my client."
}

{
  "id": "line:02678c9",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: According to your testimony,[p/] my client had just finished murdering her father.[p/] Wouldn’t she have noticed you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ca9eb",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Garrick: I-[p/][s/]I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:027030a",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you were that close,[p/][s/] then surely you were close enough to apprehend her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8bfce",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: So why didn’t you?[p/][s/] Don’t you have a duty to your citizens you lord over?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbdb6d",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Garrick: Shut your filthy mouth!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e734ea",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Garrick: That woman was armed![p/][s/] I had no reason to put my life in danger!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1b415",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Garrick: I was terrified when I saw her holding that bloody sword!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03855b1",
  "node": "GarrickArgue2",
  "text": "Garrick: She’d just murdered a man,[p/][s/] and I might’ve very well been next!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2159c",
  "node": "GarrickArgue3",
  "text": "Photo"
}

{
  "id": "line:0016fef",
  "node": "GarrickArgue3",
  "text": "No...[p/] He claimed that Celeste was holding her sword after stabbing Flinhart."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ca5c4",
  "node": "GarrickArgue3",
  "text": "However,[p/] that proposed sequence of events shouldn't have been possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e7de9",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: But that can’t be right.[p/] Can it, Lord Pierce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d083d8",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: This photo of the crime scene shows that the sword was left inside the victim’s body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8b67c",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: How could she still be wielding it if it never left the body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c618d1",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Garrick: W-[p/][s/]What?![p/][s/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:05514b4",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Garrick: Agh![p/][s/] Damn you![p/][s/] DAMN YOU!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6c60e",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Garrick: Steelwind![p/][s/] Why aren’t you saying anything?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:012e3d1",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "AriaC: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0273a51",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "AriaC: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/][s/] I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e907f",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Steelwind froze."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b12ea0",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Even when I had the advantage,[p/] she always maintained her usual poise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfb864",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "But now she was scrambling for something to say.[p/] Nothing came to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0376856",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Judge: L-[p/][s/]Lord Pierce.[p/] Please calm down!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bce735",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Garrick: How can I remain calm when this [i]charlatan[/i] is trying to frame me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03313db",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Garrick: This is a complete travesty!"
}

{
  "id": "line:018ec5d",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Garrick: I came here to reveal the truth and testify against that criminal!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0708174",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Garrick: And what do I get instead?![p/][s/] Slander from some lowly peasant!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e29fe",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You talk about justice,[p/][s/] but you’ve committed several acts of perjury to twist the outcome of this trial!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec8e52",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You don’t care about justice![p/] You're just here to cover up your crime!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01596e6",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Garrick: You filthy little—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0047ef0",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: So admit it, Pierce![p/][s/] You created a makeshift sword with [b]Shape Liquid[/b] and used it to impale Flinhart!"
}

{
  "id": "line:070056e",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You shoved my client’s sword into the wound,[p/][s/] while the remnants of the real murder weapon melted!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed77cc",
  "node": "GarrickArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You thought it was a perfect crime, didn't you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08be8f0",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "Garrick: ... [h=\"Wait...|What did he just say?\" e=\"afh\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0176b75",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "Garrick: Haha..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a49d8d",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "Garrick: HAHAHAHAHAHA!"
}

{
  "id": "line:084864f",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "AriaC: ...?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7bd25",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "Judge: L-[p/][s/]Lord Pierce...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:085e9f4",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "Garrick: My apologies, Your Honor.[p/][s/] It’s just that I realized something absolutely hilarious!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0539998",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "Garrick: The defense has put forward an interesting theory,[p/] but there’s [i]one[/i] problem with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d47682",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: And what’s that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e1c7a",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "Garrick: I think you said it yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:00224e2",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "Garrick: You’re right![p/][s/] It [i]would[/i] have been a perfect crime!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd3b2f",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "Garrick: Because any evidence to support that theory would’ve evaporated with that melted blade!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e10b3e",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "AriaC: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e4079",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09273b1",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "He was right![p/] Magical traces don’t spread through physical contact."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba7eb9",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "They are only detected on the objects they are cast on..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0163cf6",
  "node": "GarrickArgue5",
  "text": "If he used a blade of water to kill Flinhart,[p/][s/] all of the water he used to make that sword would have evaporated by now!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd7c0e",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: That would mean..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0754a29",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Garrick: There would be [i]nothing[/i] left of the murder weapon!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07cf187",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Garrick: You’ve spun quite the tale here today,[p/] but in the end,[p/] you don’t have a shred of evidence to support it, do you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef9ab4",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Garrick: You have [i]NOTHING[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebd899",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]Isn’t there anything we can do?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:098c792",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "I became quiet.[p/] Thinking through each piece of evidence I'd found."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce488c",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "They all fit into place,[p/] except for one piece..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07132a0",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...? [h=\"Why isn’t he saying anything?!|Is it really hopeless...?\" e=\"fs\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa2bb2",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eec042",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Any worries she had disappeared.[p/] She probably saw the look on my face.[p/] It was familiar to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcf0fe",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "It expressed the same quiet certainty I had every time I defeated her."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ca055",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "I wasn’t sure how,[p/] but there was [i]something[/i] left of the murder weapon."
}

{
  "id": "line:071061d",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Otherwise,[p/] there wouldn’t have been any traces of [b]transmutation[/b] at the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0688c88",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Garrick: W-[p/][s/]What is this...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ccd8c",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Garrick: You can glare at me all you want.[p/] It won’t change the fact that you’ve lost."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aead5b",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I despise people like you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0022880",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: You twist this kingdom’s laws to serve your own ends."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e5d81",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: You trample on the lives of the people you’re supposed to be serving and protecting."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f7d2c",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But as long as I’m standing in this courtroom,[p/][s/] I will [i]never[/i] let that happen again!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8a68a",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ugh...[p/] What did I just do...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d9507",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "I could feel my head being dragged to the ground.[p/] It felt like it was about to burst."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb41e2",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "...At the same time,[p/] I felt an extreme sense of clarity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a94bdb",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "It was as if nothing could be concealed from the Eye of Horus now."
}

{
  "id": "line:091baf2",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Garrick: ... [h=\"I can’t believe that peasant...|He pushed me this far...\" e=\"hf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:039d8fd",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "Once again,[p/] I saw Pierce's thoughts,[p/] but this sensation felt sharper than it usually was."
}

{
  "id": "line:016c77b",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "I could feel his mind reacting to mine,[p/] as if it were a pond rippling around me as I stepped through it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a34645",
  "node": "GarrickArgue6",
  "text": "I wondered...[p/] Could I reach further in and pull something I could use?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad1ec0",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Shape Liquid|Bottle|Bottle2|Bottle3"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae4dd9",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: After all the trouble I went to,[p/] I can’t believe that boy figured out which spell I used."
}

{
  "id": "line:0832335",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: Well, no matter.[p/] It’s not as if there’s any evidence that implicates me."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a0037",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: I’m lucky that old fool had that bottle of water with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:059c878",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Conjure Water"
}

{
  "id": "line:00ffbbe",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: Perhaps I should have used this spell to create the blade..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2ad26",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: No...[p/] It was far safer to use that bottle he was holding..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ef769",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: Conjuring my own water could have left evidence behind."
}

{
  "id": "line:027d0c1",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Mage Blade"
}

{
  "id": "line:082c20d",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: Hmph...[p/] What a crass and basic spell.[p/] It’s no wonder that it’s the only spell that bastard knows."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bd5fb",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "That didn’t give me anything I could use..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b63dc3",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "I needed to try something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0468a84",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Conjure Light"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbbe42",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: Ugh... What kind of fool installs artificery only to leave it in disrepair?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e124e",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: I would have never had to cast [b]Conjure Light[/b] if those lights were functional."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5b63f",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "That didn’t tell me anything that I didn’t already know..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0912b7c",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "PROJECTING evidence relating to the murder was definitely the key to finding what I needed."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e8bed",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "I needed to try something else"
}

{
  "id": "line:08834c1",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Frost Wave"
}

{
  "id": "line:0999859",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: If only I could have used [b]Frost Wave[/b],[p/] things would have been much cleaner."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b06da3",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: But using such an obvious spell would have only implicated me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0325de2",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "That made sense.[p/] There wasn’t any ice at the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:057c66b",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "I doubted that he used [b]Frost Wave[/b] during the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6bfca",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: What an ornate sword...[p/] I wonder how a commoner came by such a thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4d583",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: I should ask the Inquisition for it once the girl is convicted."
}

{
  "id": "line:05eee95",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: Even now, that image is still lingering in my mind..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b78110",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: Why does it trouble me so much?[p/] He was a fool and an insurgent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd0cf2",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: ...What would Effie think of me now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2d7dc",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: Hmph...[p/] She only knows one spell?[p/] Of course, she would."
}

{
  "id": "line:0610a5f",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: It’s not as if any of the academies would admit someone like her."
}

{
  "id": "line:086dc99",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Lord Pierce's Spell Compendium"
}

{
  "id": "line:063b800",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: I really have an affinity for water magic, don’t I?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f65285",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: I should really learn some new spells.[p/] Perhaps a visit to the academy is in order."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff82b8",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: I can’t believe Flinhart,[p/] of all people,[p/] ended up taking that monster in."
}

{
  "id": "line:0058ba2",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: How blind could he be?[p/] He didn’t even know she was a mage..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0732f04",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: Is the Scaled Lord really more than a simple story...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1a43b",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: I had hoped to feign being her ally once she was convicted,[p/] but the boy ruined everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d2f22",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: I have no choice but to let her be executed now."
}

{
  "id": "line:056876d",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Flinhart"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2d804",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: Flinhart...[p/] How did it come to this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ddeff",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: No...[p/] [i]He[/i] was the one who chose to spread dissidence against the Crown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b308ae",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: He should have known what would happen.[p/] If it weren't me,[p/] it would've been someone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d47c4",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Jolene"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e181e9",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: ...I wonder how Jolie is handling all of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:028a465",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: ...What?![p/][s/] Why am I thinking of her now, of all times?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ace766",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: That weed is of no importance to me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0deb14f",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Ruby|Tyrion"
}

{
  "id": "line:016d8de",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: This lawyer is the protégé of the infamous Ruby Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a1931",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: I suppose I should have expected as much,[p/] but I never expected him to push me this far."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de3ab4",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: I’ll need to be more wary of them in the future."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a29781",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: ...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab8149",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Garrick: Why am I thinking of such a thing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f40e6b",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "Hm... That piece of evidence didn’t evoke any useful thoughts from him."
}

{
  "id": "line:099f8ab",
  "node": "GarrickEye",
  "text": "I needed to PROJECT pieces of evidence related to the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0540179",
  "node": "GarrickFinal",
  "text": "\"A bottle of water\"...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07dcd22",
  "node": "GarrickFinal",
  "text": "Garrick: Well, then...[p/] As[p/] [i]riveting[/i] as this has been,[p/] I believe it’s time for me to be on my way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7ed3a",
  "node": "GarrickFinal",
  "text": "Tyrion: Now wait a minute, Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0183269",
  "node": "GarrickFinal",
  "text": "Garrick: ...What is it now, you cretin?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c2402",
  "node": "GarrickFinal",
  "text": "Garrick: I’ll say it as many times as you need to hear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad4a59",
  "node": "GarrickFinal2",
  "text": "No...[p/] That’s not right."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a51ee",
  "node": "GarrickFinal2",
  "text": "He said that he “used a bottle\" to commit the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db13b9",
  "node": "GarrickFinal2",
  "text": "If my hunch was correct,[p/] then that bottle should be all the evidence I needed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0824c15",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You’re right, Pierce.[p/] If you used [b]Shape Liquid[/b] on a body of water,[p/] the murder weapon would have evaporated entirely."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0b202",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Garrick: Bravo.[p/] It seems you’ve finally gotten that fact through your thick head."
}

{
  "id": "line:078c508",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Tyrion: But let’s not get ahead of ourselves, Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:09511c7",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Tyrion: What if you didn’t use [b]Shape Liquid[/b] on a body of water?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffcf2e",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Tyrion: What if it were another type of liquid?"
}

{
  "id": "line:045e424",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Garrick: ...What are you going on about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ae75e",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Pierce,[p/] [b]Shape Liquid[/b] doesn’t just work on water.[p/] It works on all kinds of liquids."
}

{
  "id": "line:0908e5d",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Tyrion: There was a shattered bottle next to the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a55ab0",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Tyrion: The liquid you used to form the murder weapon—[p/]it came from that bottle, didn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03b139a",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Garrick: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0496b1f",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You were probably wary of leaving evidence at the crime scene.[p/] You must have decided to use any liquid you could find there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9630b",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Luckily for you,[p/] the victim was holding the perfect quantity of liquid in his hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0547e",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Tyrion: That begs the question:[p/] if we had someone analyze the broken pieces of this bottle—"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e36f9",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Tyrion: —would we find traces of [b]transmutation[/b] magic?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8a9da",
  "node": "GarrickFinal3",
  "text": "Garrick: H-[p/][s/]Ha![p/][s/] Do you think you can bluff me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b7271",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "Garrick: We’ve already established that any water I [i]supposedly[/i] shaped would have evaporated!"
}

{
  "id": "line:039e5aa",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Except the liquid contained in this bottle [i]wasn’t[/i] water![p/][s/] It was tea!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0077af3",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "Garrick: So?![p/][s/] What difference does that make?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a79d9",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "Tyrion: A blade of ice made out of water would have evaporated entirely..."
}

{
  "id": "line:059762b",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "Tyrion: But a blade of frozen tea would leave a dried residue![p/][s/] The tea wouldn't completely disappear!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0504120",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "Garrick: ...No."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf3f94",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I wondered why there were so many traces of [b]transmutation[b/] scattered around the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0627902",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "Tyrion: When I felt the texture of the floor,[p/] I'd thought a [b]transmutation[/b] spell had caused some sort of chemical reaction with the wood."
}

{
  "id": "line:058df59",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But the [i]real[/i] answer was a lot simpler than that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9dd85",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "Tyrion: The [b]transmutation[/b] spell didn’t alter the floor at all![p/][p/] It was just a stain from the spilled tea!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0353b8b",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I bet if we compared the tea residue on the floor to the residue inside the bottle,[p/] we’d find traces of [b]transmutation[/b] on them!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03338ff",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "Tyrion: There’s your murder weapon, Pierce!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2c59a",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You have nowhere left to go.[p/] That’s Checkmate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f123c2",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Bailiff![p/][s/] Send for Orym!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b35370",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "AriaC: The Inquisition needs to analyze the crime scene at once!"
}

{
  "id": "line:041b5c2",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "AriaC: We need to confirm the defense’s theory![p/][s/] The time window to detect traces of magic is closing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff9d0c",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "AriaC: ...I have the report from the Inquisition."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c46ac4",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "Judge: W-[p/][s/]What does it say?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d8a6f",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "AriaC: The traces on the sword,[p/] the body,[p/] even the floor—[p/]they all came from tea residue."
}

{
  "id": "line:02626db",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "AriaC: We found those same traces on the shards of the broken bottle, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0015429",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "AriaC: It’s undeniable.[p/] Someone cast a spell on the liquid contained within that bottle."
}

{
  "id": "line:04928ed",
  "node": "GarrickFinal4",
  "text": "AriaC: ...And the defendant has no such spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1463d",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You really did it, didn’t you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:088d198",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Celeste: Why...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0120924",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Garrick: As if someone like you would ever understand..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0062698",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Celeste: “Understand\"?![p/][s/] You murdered my dad!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8fad0",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Garrick: Murdered...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0508d8c",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Garrick: MURDERED?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a9e6e",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Garrick: I murdered her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd78a4",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Garrick: I can’t believe it...[p/] She’s dead..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9b641",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Garrick: Her smile...[p/] Her beautiful voice...[p/] It's all gone..."
}

{
  "id": "line:000b191",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Garrick: I deserve death..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f448cd",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Fredrick: Stop this nonsense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df73af",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Garrick: Father...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:022d07f",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Fredrick: You’re grieving,[p/] but it will pass.[p/] She was only a commoner."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0dbc3",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Garrick: No,[p/] Father...[p/] I loved her,[p/] and I [i]killed[/i] her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ad299",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Fredrick: Garrick...[p/] You sweet,[p/] innocent child."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b30c81",
  "node": "GarrickFinal5",
  "text": "Fredrick: Flowers may be beautiful and bring you joy,[p/] but do you call it “murder\" when you accidentally step on one?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01fe5af",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Fredrick: These people—[p/]these [p/][s/]peasants—[p/]they may resemble us,[p/] but you know deep in your heart that they aren’t like us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb3441",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Garrick: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca93a3",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Fredrick: We have the Scaled Lord’s favor,[p/] and they do not."
}

{
  "id": "line:012ab25",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Fredrick: They were created to serve us—[p/]to be utilized by those of us who matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d821c3",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Garrick: Father..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f6a9a",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Fredrick: So don’t fret so much over a simple commoner."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2073f",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Fredrick: By next month,[p/] you’ll have completely forgotten about that wretched thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:049ce12",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Garrick: Ha...[p/] Haha..."
}

{
  "id": "line:014f846",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Garrick: HAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA!"
}

{
  "id": "line:012ca0e",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Garrick: HOW COULD I HAVE BEEN SO BLIND?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1d1bf",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Garrick: SHE WAS A SIMPLE FLOWER![p/][s/] NOTHING BUT A WORTHLESS PEASANT!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c282fe",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Garrick: They’re all just peasants—[p/][s/]ALL OF THEM!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a1e48",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Garrick: Is it \"murder\" to protect my kingdom?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0bcbd",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Garrick: Is it \"murder\" to pull weeds before they blight my land?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b9611",
  "node": "GarrickFinal6",
  "text": "Garrick: That fool of a man was spreading [i]poison[/i],[p/][s/] and I did my duty by removing him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9339c",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "Celeste: You’re a monster..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0a492",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "Garrick: I’m a [i]NOBLEMAN[/i]—[p/][s/]a chosen vessel of the Scaled Lord’s will!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e37fc",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "Garrick: You are all [i]nothing[/i]![p/][s/] Do you honestly think you can indict [i]ME[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c918fb",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "Garrick: My word carries more power than [i]a hundred[/i] of yours!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a97e32",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "AriaC: Bailiff.[p/] Escort Pierce to a holding cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:00851cc",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "Garrick: ...S-[p/][s/]Steelwind?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f3f17",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "AriaC: First-degree murder is punishable by execution, Lord Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:067c2e7",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "AriaC: I suggest you remain silent.[p/] Lest you incriminate yourself further."
}

{
  "id": "line:07982bd",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "Garrick: Y-[p/][s/]You can’t be serious!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0933d0b",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "Garrick: [i]You[/i],[p/] of all people,[p/] must understand the position I was in!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f07231",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "Garrick: Your father knows what it takes to maintain order![p/][s/] If not for me—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf0aa3",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "AriaC: Shut your insidious mouth!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dccc8c",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "AriaC: I will never understand your sick, disgusting mind![p/][s/] I’d sooner slit my own throat!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e38f01",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "AriaC: Well?![p/][s/] What are you all waiting for?![p/][s/] Take him away!"
}

{
  "id": "line:012b7d6",
  "node": "GarrickFinal7",
  "text": "Judge: Y-[p/][s/]Yes...![p/][s/] Take him away at once!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a958b8",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Celeste: I can’t believe it...[p/][s/] We actually won..."
}

{
  "id": "line:097eddb",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Celeste: T-[p/][s/]Tyrion...[p/][s/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e16e79",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know, Celeste..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07df4ab",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1513f",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Teary-eyed,[p/] she threw her arms around me,[p/] embracing me tightly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce9b18",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "I just stood there wide-eyed,[p/] looking toward the gallery members who were staring at us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0afd4",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "...I was unsure of where to put my hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0729e89",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Ruby: That was...[p/] [i]remarkable[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0141f58",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Tyrion: M-[p/][s/]Ms. Tymora!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf9cf7",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Ruby: I’ll be honest.[p/] When I realized that the murder weapon had evaporated,[p/] I thought that the case was over."
}

{
  "id": "line:006bf79",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Ruby: You did a great job of turning that around."
}

{
  "id": "line:065a627",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was just luck...[p/] If he'd used water,[p/] things would have ended very differently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0baae95",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Ruby: It had nothing to do with luck—[p/]not this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7e482",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Ruby: You were able to deduce which liquid he used,[p/] and you did it just by looking at a few shards of broken glass."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d0590",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Ruby: I knew your deductive skills were good,[p/] but that was incredible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0769348",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "It wasn’t just deduction, though.[p/] I did something with the Eye of Horus today[p/]—something I’d never done before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0038c10",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "I had an amazing ability,[p/] but I was starting to realize that I knew next to nothing about it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:043dd9e",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "If I wanted to use it effectively,[p/] I needed to learn more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0799ce3",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Aria: You all are quite lively."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c9a9d",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: There’s no need for such hostility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9f385",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: Though, I wouldn’t expect any less from the hound of the Eyetaker."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4bacc",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01793e3",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "...What did she mean by [i]that[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07bf52a",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "I glanced at Ms. Tymora,[p/] but she avoided eye contact with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:062d0bb",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "It was subtle,[p/] but her posture stiffened,[p/] and her brow clenched ever so slightly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0992867",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "I couldn't see any thoughts through the Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:044e4b8",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: I must admit.[p/] I was hoping to test my mind against yours directly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aef868",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: However,[p/] your protégé proved to be a worthy adversary."
}

{
  "id": "line:032fc9c",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Is this some kind of game to you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0971bc4",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Ruby: You almost condemned an innocent girl to death."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d0185",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: The courts operate by having two powers of opposition."
}

{
  "id": "line:0316945",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: When those powers are balanced,[p/] justice prevails,[p/] just like it did today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0001238",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: Your victory today was just the system working as intended."
}

{
  "id": "line:0287906",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Ruby: Ha![p/][s/] “Working as intended\"!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a9523",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Ruby: You know very well our system only exists to protect your people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8afce",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Ruby: You can act as sanctimonious as you want."
}

{
  "id": "line:072c812",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Ruby: That doesn’t change that with each passing day,[p/] your father butchers more and more innocents."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da9883",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: I know."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ff4bd",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: But I'm not my father.[p/] I walk a different path."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4f9a2",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: ...I know you have no reason to believe me,[p/] so I'll let my actions speak for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9e13a",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: I look forward to doing battle with you again, Tyrion Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e998ef",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind, why [i]did[/i] you arrest Pierce at the end of the trial?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad1451",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: I don't understand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0919e3b",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He was right in a way.[p/] You didn't need to do that."
}

{
  "id": "line:026377a",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: He openly admitted to first-degree murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:079dee8",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: Why wouldn't I have him arrested?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e6475",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Nevermind then.[p/] I'm also looking forward to facing you again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0632fa9",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Aria: Good.[p/] I hope to see you soon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d357d0",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "I still couldn’t tell what she was thinking,[p/] even with the Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c61d38",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "She definitely wasn't the bloodthirsty killer that her father was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf6532",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sighs*[/i][p/] Well, that kind of killed the mood, didn’t it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3330e",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Ruby: Not at all.[p/] I think we should celebrate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9da96",
  "node": "FinalScene2",
  "text": "Celeste: What are you thinking?"
}

{
  "id": "line:001ff80",
  "node": "FinalScene3",
  "text": "Ruby: There’s this high-class restaurant in the upper quarter of Ratholme."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e8083",
  "node": "FinalScene3",
  "text": "Ruby: They usually only serve nobles,[p/] but they let anyone in if they have enough gold."
}

{
  "id": "line:03572b1",
  "node": "FinalScene3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] Do [i]we[/i] have enough gold?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bcb1c",
  "node": "FinalScene3",
  "text": "Ruby: I have some connections with the staff there.[p/] Don't worry about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3a621",
  "node": "FinalScene3",
  "text": "These last two days marked the beginning of my journey into the world of law and magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e122bc",
  "node": "FinalScene3",
  "text": "Our justice system was broken—[p/]rotten from the inside—[p/] but I had a voice now.[p/] I would never stop fighting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0288133",
  "node": "FinalScene3",
  "text": "With my skills and the Eye of Horus,[p/] I knew nothing could stop me."
}

{
  "id": "line:099bdf4",
  "node": "FinalScene3",
  "text": "...Or at least that’s what I'd hoped."
}

{
  "id": "line:0343ce2",
  "node": "FinalScene3",
  "text": "Eris: ...This feeling![p/][s/] I knew it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba9c5d",
  "node": "FinalScene3",
  "text": "Eris: His radiant soul is finally ripe for the reaping!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf6b7b",
  "node": "FinalScene3",
  "text": "Eris: Even this small speck of time has felt like an eternity!"
}

{
  "id": "line:042706d",
  "node": "FinalScene3",
  "text": "Eris: I can’t wait any longer..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cde37a",
  "node": "FinalScene3",
  "text": "Eris: I can’t wait to see that wretched light drain from his eyes..."
}

{
  "id": "line:090c3fe",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "Lloyd: W-[p/][s/]William, [i]please[/i].[p/] I implore you."
}

{
  "id": "line:04998cb",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "Lloyd: I know you're... [i]excited[/i],[p/] but don't you think we are moving far too quickly?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09f0460",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "William: Nonsense.[p/] Everything has been going according to plan."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f04272",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "Lloyd von Sanctus shifted nervously,[p/] his rat-like posture practically shuddering."
}

{
  "id": "line:081012b",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "William Frega, on the other hand,[p/] only seemed bothered by Lloyd's incessant chittering."
}

{
  "id": "line:034f9e3",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "They both held the status of Duke,[p/] but only William wore it rather than the other way around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fad992",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "Lloyd: I have advocated for the Arcurians more than anyone else,[p/] but I haven't had enough time to look into them!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0160190",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "William: The Arcurians are an efficient yet simple folk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0925c3b",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "William: The only thing they care about is filling their coffers,[p/] and I'm quite proficient in that language."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5bc6a",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...And what of the Grand General?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0078a2b",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "William: ...Who do you think pays for all of his soldiers?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ead3d",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "Lloyd: You may be able to get to the ground forces,[p/] but his extended family is something else entirely."
}

{
  "id": "line:035197f",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "Lloyd: If you threaten them like this,[p/] they will respond in kind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0777e09",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "William: Loyalty can be bought—[p/]the same as any other commodity."
}

{
  "id": "line:078b74f",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "William: Every house has a weak link.[p/] It's only a matter of time before I find his."
}

{
  "id": "line:009d1dc",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "Lloyd: [i]William[/i]—"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e1174",
  "node": "PillarMeeting",
  "text": "William: Enough.[p/] This meeting is an opportunity for us to finally pull the Minister of Justice to our side."
}

{
  "id": "line:039f4ff",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "William: I will not squander it.[p/] We [i]will[/i] take Wyverngarde from Lucio today."
}

{
  "id": "line:06913d4",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "William: ...Grow a spine, while you're at it.[p/] You're a duke for crying out loud."
}

{
  "id": "line:0776214",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "Lloyd: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ded538",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "Lloyd just exhaled deeply as he followed William to the meeting room."
}

{
  "id": "line:070c891",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "Coraline: Oh,[p/] they've arrived."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbc44e",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "Coraline: See?[p/] You had nothing to worry about, Your Grace."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a525d2",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "Remus: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b429a1",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "It seemed that the Minister of Justice and the High Speaker had already arrived."
}

{
  "id": "line:007f351",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "Coraline Sibyl and Theon Archeus were the most powerful people in this room,[p/][p/][p/] in theory..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3d6e6",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "They represented the justice system and the Church respectively,[p/] but both of their heads were always in the clouds."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c16007",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "Their dispositions made them more akin to cattle that could be distracted and coaxed with shiny trinkets."
}

{
  "id": "line:067d45e",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "Coraline was always ruminating about fate and the cosmos.[p/] She'd often confuse astrology with philosophy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b55c0c",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "Theon was blinded by his obsession with the Scaled Lord and his stories.[p/] William was almost certain that his noble house had [i]written[/i] half of those stories."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f277f4",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "Theon: Ah,[p/] I was worried that something had befallen your convoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d232c0",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "Theon: I've been praying to the Scaled Lord for your safety."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abfb6e",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "Remus: You two are late."
}

{
  "id": "line:02aba94",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "William: From the looks of it,[p/] we're not the only ones."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4cba9",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "William: Could the [i]Grand[/i] General not be arsed to show up?[p/] It's because of [i]his[/i] foolishness that we've gathered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c42b48",
  "node": "PillarMeeting2",
  "text": "Coraline: ...That's not entirely true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3155d",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: Really?[p/] And what of his recent bloodbath in the countryside?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0451c0d",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: Word on the grapevine says that his men tossed a clergyman from the top of a bell tower."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a6b4f",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: The man is so bloodthirsty,[p/] we should check his pantry for the children he's slaughtered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8597c",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "Lloyd: William!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3d905",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "Remus: We have [i]assembled[/i] here to discuss the lack of unity between the Four Pillars."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fa345",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: \"Unity\"?[p/] Spare me."
}

{
  "id": "line:088c419",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: House Frega,[p/] House von Sanctus,[p/] and House Sibyl are closer than they've ever been.[p/] The [i]Steelwinds[/i] are the odd one out."
}

{
  "id": "line:02de886",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: Unity requires trust,[p/] and he has done nothing but spill the blood of the people we've [i]trusted[/i] him to protect."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d1dde",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "Coraline: His recent actions have been...[p/] [i]excessive[/i].[p/] No one here is disputing that."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e8ca1",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: My dear Duchess,[p/] his “excess” has merchants refusing to move caravans through the countryside."
}

{
  "id": "line:069a4b2",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: The commoners are crying for justice and turning to insurrection—[p/]something that the Grand General is [i]supposed[/i] to be putting a stop to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afc9e3",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: The other nations whisper about us like we're a barbarian state dressed in fancy robes."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fec17",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "Theon: ...Trade [i]has[/i] slowed.[p/] The Scaled Lord teaches that prosperity is a covenant between every man in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d62b6d",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "Remus: House Steelwind carries the burden of protecting Wyverngarde’s borders."
}

{
  "id": "line:080a75d",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "Remus: As mishandled as these situations have been,[p/] he's not massacring these villages for his own amusement."
}

{
  "id": "line:05657a6",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: Hmph...[p/] He could have fooled me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb0e59",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: A leader wins respect and loyalty.[p/] He doesn't hold his people hostage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef0e42",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: Mark my words.[p/] If this bloodshed continues,[p/] the commoners [i]will[/i] revolt."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ffb6c",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: These recent insurrections are just the start,[p/] and this will only continue if we allow Lucio's daughter to take the throne."
}

{
  "id": "line:08dd47d",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "Coraline: ...If we're discussing Lady Steelwind's marriage to the Crown Prince,[p/] surely he should be a part of this meeting as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9de8d",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: Please.[p/] What can that bright-eyed boy contribute to this conversation?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c18d1",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: The only thing he's good for is holding fundraisers and cutting red ribbons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0790dd9",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "Coraline: ...William.[p/] He's the heir to the throne."
}

{
  "id": "line:06122fd",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "William: Come now...[p/] The [i]true[/i] rulers of Wyverngarde are all assembled in this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:039798a",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "Coraline: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae2d32",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "Coraline: I'll admit,[p/] the House of Lords has received more petitions against Lucio than any other general in Wyverngarde's history."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd002f",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "Theon: The Church has also been unable to collect as many tithes as before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c34475",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "Theon: Even the most faithful are asking whether the Scaled Lord would support such cruelty."
}

{
  "id": "line:035576a",
  "node": "PillarMeeting3",
  "text": "Theon: Their faith is faltering.[p/] This cannot be allowed to continue."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ae630",
  "node": "PillarMeeting4",
  "text": "William: ...Oh, look who [i]finally[/i] decided to show up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0891e11",
  "node": "PillarMeeting4",
  "text": "Lucio: I know I'm late.[p/] I was caught in a debrief."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cc374",
  "node": "PillarMeeting4",
  "text": "Lucio: I find this gathering to be pointless anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3eba6",
  "node": "PillarMeeting4",
  "text": "Lloyd: How [i]dare[/i] you, Grand General?![p/][s/] Have you no sense of respect?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:045a693",
  "node": "PillarMeeting4",
  "text": "Lucio: What use would respect be to ones who can't command it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07afc17",
  "node": "PillarMeeting4",
  "text": "Lucio: ...Will [i]you[/i] demand my respect, Master of [b]Abjuration[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4d8f1",
  "node": "PillarMeeting4",
  "text": "Lloyd: W-[p/][s/]Well,[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dea884",
  "node": "PillarMeeting4",
  "text": "Remus: Leave him alone, Lucio."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf0897",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "William: We were just discussing your recent catastrophe in the countryside."
}

{
  "id": "line:02afc32",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "William: From what I've heard,[p/] the death toll has been astronomical.[p/] Did you beat your record?"
}

{
  "id": "line:001254c",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Lucio: If you have something to say,[p/] than say it plainly, Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0330035",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "William: House Frega would like to move to have the Steelwinds stripped of their authority and control of Wyverngarde's military."
}

{
  "id": "line:0773d4c",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "William: Lloyd,[p/] Coraline,[p/] and the Church agree with me on this matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0670bc2",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Lucio: ...Is that so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07966af",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Lloyd: I-[p/][s/]I—[p/][s/] Er,[p/][s/] I mean—[p/][s/] [i]We[/i] of House von Sanctus stand with House Frega on this matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a3233",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Coraline: I'm sorry, Lucio,[p/] but it's difficult to argue against what the reports have been saying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0119624",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Lucio: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7e846",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Coraline: I will bring this matter to the House of Lords.[p/] We'll hold a vote."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df309e",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Lucio: Then the House of Lords should know about what my agents have discovered."
}

{
  "id": "line:071d097",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Lucio: The Eastern Kingdoms have joined the Union."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bdb19",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "William: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:018b8b4",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Coraline: ...Surely,[p/] this can't be true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bced2c",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Lucio: It is.[p/] I'm sure the Ordo Astralis will be announcing it publicly within the week."
}

{
  "id": "line:00abf28",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Theon: ...Wyverngarde is now the only nation in the world that hasn't joined their alliance."
}

{
  "id": "line:046f72c",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Lucio: Correct.[p/] The only thing acting as a deterrent to our enemies is the high [b]evocation[/b] magic of House Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca4cba",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Lucio: Do you think the House of Lords will be willing to oust the most powerful war mages from our ranks?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6fc8b",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "William: ...Lucio."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc0e33",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Lucio: Now,[p/] if you're done gnashing your teeth, William,[p/] I have to meet with the rest of my house."
}

{
  "id": "line:0294852",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Lucio: We'll need to prepare in case the Luminites become bold enough to bring war to the western border."
}

{
  "id": "line:07edff2",
  "node": "PillarMeeting5",
  "text": "Remus: Lucio,[p/] wait!"
}

{
  "id": "line:005abd3",
  "node": "PillarMeeting6",
  "text": "William: Damn it all![p/][s/] Since when were those orientals so friendly with the Ordo Astralis?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:092a316",
  "node": "PillarMeeting6",
  "text": "William: I can't believe the Luminites would suffer the company of those mud-eating savages!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c57fa3",
  "node": "PillarMeeting6",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...Actually,[p/] their culture is very rich."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8911b",
  "node": "PillarMeeting6",
  "text": "Lloyd: [i]I[/i],[p/] for one,[p/] quite enjoy many of their—"
}

{
  "id": "line:01237ae",
  "node": "PillarMeeting6",
  "text": "William: Shut [i]up[/i], Lloyd!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0056e90",
  "node": "PillarMeeting6",
  "text": "William: ...We'll need to expedite our plans."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ce13e",
  "node": "PillarMeeting6",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00bde3d",
  "node": "PillarMeeting6",
  "text": "William: Get the Arcarians on the line.[p/] I will have words with them."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a4584",
  "node": "PillarMeeting6",
  "text": "Coraline: You have business with Arcarus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b2f56",
  "node": "PillarMeeting6",
  "text": "William: ...We're brokering a trade deal.[p/] I'm sure the House of Lords will be seeing it soon."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bce6b",
  "node": "PillarMeeting6",
  "text": "Coraline: It seems the Cosmos is in our favor then."
}

{
  "id": "line:077af22",
  "node": "PillarMeeting6",
  "text": "Coraline: They're the only ally we have left."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4120f",
  "node": "PillarMeeting6",
  "text": "Lloyd: Stay safe, Coraline."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ed620",
  "node": "PillarMeeting6",
  "text": "Coraline: You too, Lloyd."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ad447",
  "node": "PillarMeeting7",
  "text": "Remus: Please tell me these stories aren't true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d50d0f",
  "node": "PillarMeeting7",
  "text": "Remus: Lucio!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffa72a",
  "node": "PillarMeeting7",
  "text": "Lucio: ...You already know the answer, Your Grace."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6f0ca",
  "node": "PillarMeeting7",
  "text": "Remus: ...H-[p/][s/]How could you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:027e366",
  "node": "PillarMeeting7",
  "text": "Lucio: I thought you never got involved in matters of the state."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d644eb",
  "node": "PillarMeeting7",
  "text": "Remus: People are dying, Lucio![p/][s/] [i]Children[/i] are dying under your watch!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdcf90",
  "node": "PillarMeeting7",
  "text": "Lucio: Do you truly think me capable of such atrocities, Your Grace?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b97c50",
  "node": "PillarMeeting7",
  "text": "Lucio: If you do,[p/] then strike me down now.[p/] You have the power to do so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc30e4",
  "node": "PillarMeeting7",
  "text": "Remus: You know I won't do that, Lucio."
}

{
  "id": "line:042044c",
  "node": "PillarMeeting7",
  "text": "Lucio: Then stay out of my way."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b59d8",
  "node": "PillarMeeting7",
  "text": "Remus: What has become of all of you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3ff8b",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Knight: Pierce,[p/] you have a visitor."
}

{
  "id": "line:028cabe",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Garrick: Hmph...[p/] Steelwind's brat again?[p/] I’m in no mood for another sanctimonious lecture."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b56032",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Jolene: Gary."
}

{
  "id": "line:04028a5",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Garrick: ...Jolene?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06e8236",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Garrick: Ha...[P/] Time has not been kind to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d8091",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Jolene: Excuse you![p/] I'll have you know that I still get mistaken for twenty everywhere I go."
}

{
  "id": "line:07eac30",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Garrick: Hmph...[p/] I suppose some things never change."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d50f4",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Garrick: ...Let’s get on with it, then."
}

{
  "id": "line:005b7e6",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Jolene: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08da2c2",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Garrick: Go on.[p/] Yell at me.[p/] Curse at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0840147",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Garrick: I doubt anyone would lift a finger if you opened this cell and beat me half to death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0042bf7",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Garrick: So...?[p/][s/] Do it."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cb2f2",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Jolene: [i]*sigh*[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8db1c",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Jolene: ...I forgive you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec22e4",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Jolene: I forgive you for killing my husband, Garrick."
}

{
  "id": "line:047ab78",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Garrick: ...Have you lost your mind?[p/] Do you think I feel [i]any[/i] remorse?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1ef7c",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Garrick: Do you think I’m still that weak child?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc6709",
  "node": "GarrickJol",
  "text": "Jolene: ...I just don’t have the energy for it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0325788",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Jolene: I saw what that resentment did to my husband.[p/] It festered inside of him like an infection."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f66e8",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Jolene: ...I’m the only family Celeste has left."
}

{
  "id": "line:094d385",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Garrick: ...If only you knew where she really came from."
}

{
  "id": "line:0740bc6",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Jolene: I don’t need to.[p/] She’s reckless,[p/] stubborn,[p/] and a little spoiled, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f14cb",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Jolene: She takes after me in a lot of ways,[p/] and she takes a little too much after her father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f00a32",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Jolene: But she’s a good person.[p/] She’s the kindest person I’ve ever known,[p/] and I’m proud to call her my daughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0393dab",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Garrick: Then you’re a fool."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aee9c3",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Jolene: Gary,[p/] Flinhart didn’t blame you for what happened to Effie."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ceebab",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Garrick: ...That’s a lie.[p/] All he ever [i]did[/i] was blame me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0872fcb",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Jolene: He didn’t blame you until you shut yourself away in your manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:06303ad",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Jolene: We were all in so much pain over what happened,[p/] and you abandoned us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c24eef",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Garrick: ...And you expect me to apologize for that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ec1b1",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Jolene: Effie always loved that spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed53b6",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Jolene: Do you remember how she’d dance in the lake while you shaped the water around her feet?"
}

{
  "id": "line:003f511",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Jolene: She thought that spell was the most beautiful thing she’d ever seen."
}

{
  "id": "line:08038fb",
  "node": "GarrickJol2",
  "text": "Garrick: ...That person died a long time ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:08baf0b",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Jolene: Effie or you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0222b7f",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Garrick: You’re a weed."
}

{
  "id": "line:048a229",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Jolene: ...Excuse me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:079ce48",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Garrick: That’s all you are, Jolene!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b71b1",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Garrick: A wilting weed on the road,[p/][s/] waiting to be trampled over by this cold, wretched world!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0157a89",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Garrick: Do you think yourself virtuous for spewing out such empty platitudes?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d355c8",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Garrick: Admit it![p/][s/] You hate me![p/][s/] You despise me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0561b45",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Garrick: If you could stomach it,[p/][s/] you’d climb into this cell and plunge a blade into my chest—[p/][s/]just like [i]I[/i] did to your husband!"
}

{
  "id": "line:070d195",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Jolene: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] No...[p/] Right now,[p/] I only feel sorry for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:033ae5f",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Jolene: I never thought you were weak.[p/] You were the kindest person I knew."
}

{
  "id": "line:002100e",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Jolene: I miss that man,[p/] but you're right.[p/] He's gone now."
}

{
  "id": "line:08308aa",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Jolene: Good luck with your trial, Garrick."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e92c1a",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Garrick: Ha![p/][s/] I don’t need luck!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5e976",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Garrick: With [i]my[/i] connections,[p/][s/] I’ll be out of this cell by week’s end!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f9765",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Garrick: AGH!"
}

{
  "id": "line:064c9e1",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Garrick: I'll show you...[p/] I'll show all of you..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03aba73",
  "node": "GarrickJol3",
  "text": "Garrick: Your daughter will be of use to me yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0727402",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "Painting 1"
}

{
  "id": "line:056ce23",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of a knight.[p/] There's some text under it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0beb716",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Sir Diogo:[p/] former Commander of the Arcane Inquisition.[p/] Well-beloved by both the people and his fellow knights.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcd17b",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"After many years of service,[p/] Commander Diogo retired with honors.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:082fe7f",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"With this plaque,[p/] we thank and honor him for his dedication and commitment to the kingdom of Wyverngarde.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:041dd08",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "Painting 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:040d5d7",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of a knight."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a196b",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's some text under it."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b951c",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"General David Serrano:[p/] former Chief of the Kingsguard.[p/] A beloved ally of House Steelwind who served during the Great Luminite War.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0fecf2d",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"The annals of history have countless tales of his courage,[p/] wit,[p/] and heroism.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:043b667",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"With this plaque,[p/] we thank and honor him for coming to the defense of our kingdom during one of our greatest times of need.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:051b681",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "Bench"
}

{
  "id": "line:040b7fe",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "There was a bench outside the courtroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:088b7b3",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "When I was a child,[p/] I used to sit there during Ms. Tymora’s trials."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6c4bf",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "This door led to the courtroom."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b053c",
  "node": "Lobby_Examine",
  "text": "Beyond these doors,[p/] the fates of countless people had been decided."
}

{
  "id": "line:089c472",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "The Investigation"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da8fa9",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Ruby: You should really head to the crime scene and gather as much information as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:065e7e2",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] I still have no idea what happened the night of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:084c1ac",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I found a lot of clues,[p/] but I still don’t know what really happened that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e182d",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Ruby: Knowing the state of a crime scene will be instrumental to cross-examining witnesses in the trial tomorrow."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b3d4b",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Ruby: Each piece of evidence gives you a weapon you can use to cut through the prosecution’s lies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0851fbd",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Right...[p/] I needed to consider each piece of evidence that I’d gathered.[p/] They would be powerful tools in my cross-examinations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0069ff8",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Flinhart was a complicated man..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f4645",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Ruby: It's not uncommon for people like him to despise magic.[p/] To them,[p/] magic is a symbol of the nobility and the King."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2b101",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don’t know...[p/] His hatred sounds like it was really personal for some reason.[p/] I think something else may have happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8d83b",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Ruby: You've definitely learned a lot.[p/] You did as well as you could have with so little time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6a539",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I just hope it’s enough..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3deeb",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Only time would tell if it was all worth it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c45dac",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "But there was one last thing I needed to do.[p/] I needed to talk to Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b6f1a",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "It wouldn’t be right to leave things as they are."
}

{
  "id": "line:050f497",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Next Lead"
}

{
  "id": "line:0372bd2",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Where should I go next, Ms. Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb5d5b",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Ruby: ...You haven't really gone anywhere.[p/] You should really head to the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:089eb12",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right...[p/] Of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cfccd",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Ruby: The Inquisition should be done questioning Celeste by now.[p/] It might be helpful to talk to her and find out why she was arguing with Flinhart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e87332",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Hopefully,[p/] she’ll actually cooperate with you this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0737350",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Ruby: McCoy gave you the key to her room. I doubt you’ll find anything,[p/] but it's the only room in the tavern that you haven't checked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4a4b1",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Ruby: You might find something useful there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0793c5d",
  "node": "Lobby_Talk",
  "text": "Ruby: You've learned a lot.[p/] I think you've collected enough evidence for the upcoming trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:01babb6",
  "node": "Lobby_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can’t believe it...[p/] I finally have an Attorney’s Runestone..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa50f7",
  "node": "Lobby_Present",
  "text": "Ruby: You worked hard for it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b45b0d",
  "node": "Lobby_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I never got a chance to thank you."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f24b7",
  "node": "Lobby_Present",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Just focus on your current case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bea974",
  "node": "Lobby_Present",
  "text": "Ruby: It has a lot of different functions.[p/] I can go over the manual with you after you acquit McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a3a37",
  "node": "Lobby_Present",
  "text": "Ruby: ...I’m not going to go over every piece of evidence with you.[p/] You'll learn nothing if I do that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4d290",
  "node": "Lobby_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Can you at least give me a hint?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0edb256",
  "node": "Lobby_Present",
  "text": "Ruby: No."
}

{
  "id": "line:018b5f6",
  "node": "Lobby_Check",
  "text": "Ruby: Oh, Cuthbert.[p/] You're back?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02379ca",
  "node": "Lobby_Check",
  "text": "Tyrion: Sorry...[p/] I guess I'm just a little lost about where to go."
}

{
  "id": "line:077b1be",
  "node": "Lobby_Check",
  "text": "Ruby: Hm...[p/] Well,[p/] I guess I can give you [i]some[/i] guidance."
}

{
  "id": "line:05cd9ac",
  "node": "OrymFail",
  "text": "Orym: Look,[p/] we can talk about this all day, kid.[p/] You’re getting nothing out of me."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e086f",
  "node": "OrymFail",
  "text": "Damn it...[p/] I still couldn’t get through to him..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02026e1",
  "node": "OrymArgue",
  "text": "Commander White was being hostile towards me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0165121",
  "node": "OrymArgue",
  "text": "At first,[p/] I'd thought he was just being corrupt or apathetic."
}

{
  "id": "line:005eaf7",
  "node": "OrymArgue",
  "text": "But he seemed to have a personal grudge against Ms. Tymora and me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecab85",
  "node": "OrymArgue",
  "text": "If I could clear up this misunderstanding,[p/] he might help me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab4553",
  "node": "OrymArgue",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you have an issue with me, Commander White?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4c62f",
  "node": "OrymArgue",
  "text": "Orym: Don’t give me that crap![p/][s/] I’ve seen who you work for."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eaf442",
  "node": "OrymArgue",
  "text": "Orym: You think I don't know what you're doing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:044f54e",
  "node": "OrymArgue",
  "text": "Orym: I'll be dead in the ground before I help you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e55f3",
  "node": "OrymArgue1",
  "text": "Deflect [c=\"Regardless of what Ms. Tymora has done, [i]I'm[/i] the one heading this case.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:099b383",
  "node": "OrymArgue1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Regardless of what Ms. Tymora has done,[p/] [i]I'm[/i] the one heading this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:017fbc5",
  "node": "OrymArgue1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You don’t even know me.[p/] Whatever problems you have with her,[p/] they have nothing to do with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e8ab9",
  "node": "OrymArgue1",
  "text": "Rationalize [c=\"My client deserves a fair trial with fair representation. All I’m trying to do is give that to her\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:09134e2",
  "node": "OrymArgue1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It doesn't matter how you feel about Ms. Tymora or me.[p/] My client deserves a fair trial with fair representation."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c2206",
  "node": "OrymArgue1",
  "text": "Tyrion: All I’m trying to do is give that to her,[p/] and I can’t do that if you withhold information from me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2a765",
  "node": "OrymArgue1",
  "text": "Defend [c=\"You have no right to throw baseless accusations against Ms. Tymora or me!\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0667147",
  "node": "OrymArgue1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You have no right to throw baseless accusations against Ms. Tymora or me![p/][s/] Whatever you think she’s done,[p/][s/] you’re mistaken!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0054b0e",
  "node": "OrymArgue1",
  "text": "Orym: Ha![p/][s/] You’re pretty good liar![p/][s/] You think I’m going to fall for your act?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c14ab",
  "node": "OrymArgue1",
  "text": "Orym: I know that woman’s hands are dirty.[p/] Nothing you say is going to change my mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:070dc8e",
  "node": "OrymArgue1",
  "text": "That wasn't the right way to respond to his claim."
}

{
  "id": "line:0767fdb",
  "node": "OrymArgue1",
  "text": "I needed to remember.[p/] Orym's PSYCHOLOGICAL PROFILE would help me determine the best way to respond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7fb2d",
  "node": "OrymArgue2",
  "text": "Orym: ...I’ve seen how she defends her clients."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b59644",
  "node": "OrymArgue2",
  "text": "Orym: Forgery,[p/] bribery,[p/] blackmail—[p/]she’ll do whatever it takes to win."
}

{
  "id": "line:0671226",
  "node": "OrymArgue2",
  "text": "Orym: It doesn’t matter what you say.[p/] I know you’re just like her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0709f3c",
  "node": "OrymArgue3",
  "text": "Deflect [c=\"I’m not Ruby Tymora. What you think of her isn’t relevant here. Regardless of what you’ve seen her do, [i]I’m[/i] trying to run an honest case.\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a1226",
  "node": "OrymArgue3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’m not Ruby Tymora.[p/] What you think of her isn’t relevant here."
}

{
  "id": "line:02be84f",
  "node": "OrymArgue3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Regardless of what you’ve seen her do,[p/] [i]I’m[/i] trying to run an honest case."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ae75d",
  "node": "OrymArgue3",
  "text": "Rationalize [c=\"“Forgery, bribery, blackmail”? Have you seen me do any of those things? I’ve only defended my client by pointing out [i]your[/i] mistakes.\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b24b0a",
  "node": "OrymArgue3",
  "text": "Tyrion: “Forgery,[p/] bribery,[p/] blackmail”?[p/] Have you seen me do any of those things?"
}

{
  "id": "line:020a104",
  "node": "OrymArgue3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Because the way I see it,[p/] I’ve only defended my client by pointing out [i]your[/i] mistakes."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f81d1",
  "node": "OrymArgue3",
  "text": "Defend [c=\"Me being her successor has nothing to do with it. You know that helping me is the right thing to do.\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0844f3f",
  "node": "OrymArgue3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Me being her successor has nothing to do with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8270b",
  "node": "OrymArgue3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You know that helping me is the right thing to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:08376d1",
  "node": "OrymArgue3",
  "text": "Orym: Don’t dodge the question![p/][s/] You want me to trust you when you can’t even give me a straight answer?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ca031",
  "node": "OrymArgue3",
  "text": "Deflecting his claim didn’t seem to be effective this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0783477",
  "node": "OrymArgue4",
  "text": "Orym: Look, kid.[p/] After what I’ve seen her pull in court,[p/] I’m not going to fall for it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2eb8e",
  "node": "OrymArgue4",
  "text": "Orym: No matter what,[p/] I know you’re a crooked lawyer raised by the biggest crook of them all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0916a44",
  "node": "OrymArgue5",
  "text": "Deflect [c=\"I’m just a defense attorney who’s asking you for information about the case. Nothing that I’ve done has given you any reason to suspect me.\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bda174",
  "node": "OrymArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’m just a defense attorney who’s asking you for information about the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fcee2",
  "node": "OrymArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Nothing that I’ve done has given you any reason to suspect me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0178dac",
  "node": "OrymArgue5",
  "text": "Rationalize [c=\"But the only thing that she taught me was how to practice law. Have you seen me engage in any crooked behavior?\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:04cf41d",
  "node": "OrymArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Her way of teaching me was ruthless,[p/] I’ll give you that."
}

{
  "id": "line:007ec0d",
  "node": "OrymArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: But the only thing that she taught me was how to practice law."
}

{
  "id": "line:070ce01",
  "node": "OrymArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Have you seen me engage in any crooked behavior?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a51284",
  "node": "OrymArgue5",
  "text": "Defend [c=\"You have no proof that she’s a “crook”, and you certainly don’t have any proof that I’m one either.\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:073a160",
  "node": "OrymArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: You’ve made accusation after accusation against her with nothing to prove it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0081264",
  "node": "OrymArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: You have no proof that she’s a “crook”,[p/] and you certainly don’t have any proof that I’m one either."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6cc4b",
  "node": "OrymArgue5",
  "text": "Orym: Like I’ve been saying,[p/] I don’t need any “proof”."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f66865",
  "node": "OrymArgue5",
  "text": "Orym: I’ve seen how she works,[p/] and I know you’re both dirty."
}

{
  "id": "line:098bd61",
  "node": "OrymArgue5",
  "text": "It seemed that defending Ms. Tymora would always end badly with the commander.[p/] I needed to try something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a57493",
  "node": "OrymArgue6",
  "text": "He spent some time searching for a rebuttal,[p/] but after a while,[p/] he just let out a resigned sigh."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f6b1b",
  "node": "OrymArgue6",
  "text": "Orym: ...You just want info on the case, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:024b058",
  "node": "OrymArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yes.[p/] That’s all I’m asking for."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4a53f",
  "node": "OrymArgue6",
  "text": "Orym: ...Alright, fine.[p/] I’ll answer your questions."
}

{
  "id": "line:065039e",
  "node": "OrymArgue6",
  "text": "Orym: But you better not make me regret this."
}

{
  "id": "line:03aa616",
  "node": "OrymArgue6",
  "text": "I successfully PERSUADED Orym White."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf0bf2",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a portrait of someone.[p/] There's some text on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c3037",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Adam Eveleigh:[p/] Politician of the Pedantic.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0e36e96",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Orym: I've heard of this guy.[p/] He's some kind of politician from one of the nations south of here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e76879",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Orym: I heard he's pretty much a shoo-in to win whatever election they have going there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f75ac1",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "An \"election\"?[p/] Had Flinhart been studying alternate forms of government for his little \"revolution\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f08e8",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of a mage?[p/] There's some text on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ce5a2",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Somala Daghlian:[p/] a legendary practitioner of the Arcane Arts.[p/] He mysteriously disappeared one day.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:093fafa",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"It's rumored that he was developing a formula for a new [b]transmutation[/b] spell.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0c602ab",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Daghlian was reckless in casting the spell,[p/] however,[p/] and he quickly lost control of it.[p/] His body was never found.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0660733",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: “Many speculate that he didn't die during the accident,[p/] but if that were true,[p/] where did the spell take him?\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee3cd0",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Orym: Hmph...[p/] Sounds like a cautionary tale against using magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0625f7f",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "...That might have explained why Flinhart kept it in his tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:0daaa67",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Candles"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b33b19",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "There were candles on each of the tables in the dining area,[p/] but there were also lamps mounted on the walls."
}

{
  "id": "line:046b0f9",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": ":On closer inspection,[p/] they appeared to be artificery:[p/] machines that could reproduce the effects of magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b06d80",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Why wasn’t the Inquisition using those instead?"
}

{
  "id": "line:068a227",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Body"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f2618",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "There was a chalk outline on the ground of the tavern,[p/] creating a rough silhouette of Flinhart’s body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffd13b",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "The chalk lines matched the crime scene photo in my Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4ffa2",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "I noticed the traces of transmutation magic on the ground in the photo.[p/] I traced my finger over the areas where they had been detected."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b846ee",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "The texture was rougher and almost sticky.[p/] Did someone use transmutation magic to alter the floor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0b2b2",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Bottle"
}

{
  "id": "line:0941b11",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Shards of a broken bottle were next to the chalk outline."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbe2a5",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: This shard has a label on it.[p/] It says “Lotus Juice”..."
}

{
  "id": "line:087e3a3",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Orym: I’ve never heard of that brand before."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ca19f",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Light"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa0d3d",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "There was a lamp mounted on the wall.[p/] It seemed to be built into the tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4e424",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is this an artificery machine?[p/] I didn’t expect to find something this sophisticated in a town like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c376b2",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Orym: Bah![p/] “Artificery” is just magic with a different name..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ced191",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Tyrion: Actually,[p/] these machines draw aether from surrounding ley lines to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e79c93",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Orym: I didn’t ask for a science lesson."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d8e60",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Orym: Anyways,[p/] look where artificery got these folks."
}

{
  "id": "line:0483785",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Orym: The energy cell broke,[p/] and they haven’t had any power for weeks."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d25e51",
  "node": "Tavern_Examine",
  "text": "Orym: Just goes to show that nothing can beat good old oil and flame."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c604b",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Help (Argument)"
}

{
  "id": "line:0302533",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Questions"
}

{
  "id": "line:055995c",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Commander White,[p/] I was wondering if I could ask you some questions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d59bae",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Ha![p/] You seriously think I’m going to help you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:001c519",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: I know who your boss is,[p/] and I know what you’re up to. [h=\"She probably sent you here to con me.\" e=\"af\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0982ce1",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I just need information about the crime scene,[p/] as is my right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfa665",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah...[p/] Sure you do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0420fb9",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "At first,[p/] I thought that he was just another corrupt knight,[p/] but this felt oddly personal."
}

{
  "id": "line:050c517",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "I wondered if this could all just be a misunderstanding.[p/] I might be able to PERSUADE him to cooperate with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0082b95",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "The Inquisition"
}

{
  "id": "line:0365de1",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: So, what does the Arcane Inquisition do exactly?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d967ce",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: ...You trying to pick a fight with me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f23979",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: No.[p/] I’m genuinely curious."
}

{
  "id": "line:048ba21",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Well, we’re called in whenever they find traces of magic at a crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:07442d7",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do crimes like this happen often?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04c0318",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Nah...[p/] Maybe once in a blue moon."
}

{
  "id": "line:005dd86",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "It made sense.[p/] Most mages were in the nobility after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ad4db",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "The ones who made a habit of falling into scandals didn't last very long."
}

{
  "id": "line:085b467",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: You must have an easy job, then."
}

{
  "id": "line:006c504",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: ...You got that right. [h=\"That's the only reason we exist|—to clean up the nobility’s messes.\" e=\"as\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb7d85",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "He didn’t seem very happy about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f5384",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Mages"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b85d4",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: You seem to speak negatively about magic.[p/] Do you have a personal grudge against mages?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f771d",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Hmph...[p/] It ain't a grudge.[p/] It's just common sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:015aebf",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: All it takes is one spell.[p/] Some rich kid just needs to wave their hands and mutter some magical nonsense."
}

{
  "id": "line:074fbaa",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Then the next thing you know, someone’s dead on the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:018017e",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Not to mention,[p/] if some bonehead [i]really[/i] overuses their magic,[p/] they end up snapping and going on a rampage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d08447",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you talking about Mageblight?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f73119",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Yep.[p/] It's what happens when a mage gets too arrogant,[p/] and nobles have that in spades."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e6aa0",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't know if this is going too far,[p/] but why would you join the Inquisition if you hate mages so much?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0ae6f",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Considering the fact that—"
}

{
  "id": "line:01a27fa",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: My [i]“job”[/i] is to sweep the nobility’s crimes under the rug?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0084c16",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I didn’t mean to insinuate—"
}

{
  "id": "line:091c9dd",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Nope.[p/] You have the right of it.[p/] Anytime a noble screws up,[p/] I’m told to look the other way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa50ae",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: ...But every once in a while,[p/] I’m allowed to put a criminal mage behind bars."
}

{
  "id": "line:080484d",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: We can’t go after the nobles,[p/] but any other mage is fair game."
}

{
  "id": "line:01308cb",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Or at least,[p/] they were before your boss showed up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0898a69",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "My “boss”?[p/] Did he have something against what Ms. Tymora was doing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe0c21",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Ruby Tymora"
}

{
  "id": "line:03cd2c0",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Murder Weapon"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8a088",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’m not entirely sure that the sword was the real murder weapon."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ea2f8",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Right...[p/] I guess you want to prove that someone else stuck the sword in the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:04355f9",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did the Inquisition find anything suspicious on the scene?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3b70f",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: If you’re asking if we found another bloody weapon lying around,[p/] we didn’t."
}

{
  "id": "line:05185c2",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "That would’ve been a little too convenient, wouldn’t it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04339d1",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: If there [i]was[/i] another murder weapon,[p/] the killer probably walked out with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:007d3c3",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you think they could have hidden it somewhere in the tavern?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac2a02",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Doubt it.[p/] After the trial,[p/] Steelwind turned the place upside-down and scanned it with her magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f33db",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: If there was something hidden here,[p/] we would’ve found it already."
}

{
  "id": "line:082ce79",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym's Mistake"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1bf0c",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can’t believe you overlooked something so obvious."
}

{
  "id": "line:002b985",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Oh, shut it with that.[p/] I already got an earful about that mess from Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2831e",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Well, you don’t have to worry about me screwing things up.[p/] Steelwind’s taken over the entire investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb994c",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do prosecutors normally do that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:025f3b6",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Nope,[p/] but she ain’t no prosecutor.[p/] She’s a Steelwind.[p/] I know better than to go against orders from her sort."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd0cc6",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: [i]*sigh*[/i] I know we made a mistake,[p/] but she’s taking this too far.[p/] She even had my men draft a map of the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0049f5e",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Tyrion: Really?[p/] Could I see it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6223e",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Orym: Knock yourself out.[p/] I have a bunch of copies.[p/] Don’t know how much good it’ll do you, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfecef",
  "node": "Tavern_Talk",
  "text": "Aria Steelwind"
}

{
  "id": "line:0802b63",
  "node": "OrymRubyTalk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have to ask...[p/] Did something happen between you and Ms. Tymora?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f221d",
  "node": "OrymRubyTalk",
  "text": "Orym: Hah![p/][s/] “[i]Ms.[/i] Tymora”.[p/] You really are her lackey, through and through."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ade9f",
  "node": "OrymRubyTalk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She's my legal guardian.[p/] I owe a lot to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d25a77",
  "node": "OrymRubyTalk",
  "text": "Orym: ...Oh.[p/] [i]That's[/i] who you were this whole time?[p/] I didn’t even know she had a kid..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c35e7",
  "node": "OrymRubyTalk",
  "text": "Orym: Look,[p/] I don’t know what she’s told you,[p/] but she ain’t the hero you think she is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d11bb8",
  "node": "OrymRubyTalk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...This is about the rumors, isn’t it?[p/] They're just lies spread by the nobility to discredit her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0606f9c",
  "node": "OrymRubyTalk",
  "text": "Orym: They ain’t lies, kid.[p/] I’ve seen it for myself.[p/] That woman's a criminal."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e6973",
  "node": "OrymRubyTalk",
  "text": "My hand clenched into a fist before I calmed myself down.[p/] This wasn’t the time for emotion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3fa89",
  "node": "OrymRubyTalk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She defends mages who don’t have the protection of the nobility.[p/] She hates the aristocracy just as much as you do."
}

{
  "id": "line:038fa4c",
  "node": "OrymRubyTalk",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah,[p/] whatever..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c531c",
  "node": "OrymAriaTalk",
  "text": "Tyrion: I heard that this was Prosecutor Steelwind’s first trial.[p/] She must be pretty talented if that’s true."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cc8ba",
  "node": "OrymAriaTalk",
  "text": "Orym: A pain in my ass is what she is."
}

{
  "id": "line:048e1a6",
  "node": "OrymAriaTalk",
  "text": "Orym: That damn noble comes in here,[p/] telling me how to do [i]my[/i] job?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e247b",
  "node": "OrymAriaTalk",
  "text": "Orym: Lord knows what she's even doing here."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cda8c",
  "node": "OrymAriaTalk",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you think she's here on behalf of her father?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00bfd8a",
  "node": "OrymAriaTalk",
  "text": "Orym: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I honestly don't know.[p/] My men are on edge 'cause of that."
}

{
  "id": "line:077cec4",
  "node": "OrymAriaTalk",
  "text": "Orym: ...You know,[p/] we were deployed to one of those regions—[p/]the ones where her old man was squashing those \"rebellions\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:01df15b",
  "node": "OrymAriaTalk",
  "text": "Orym: They said we needed to \"investigate\" the terrorists there,[p/] but by the time we got there,[p/] they just had us clean up the bodies."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d27e7",
  "node": "OrymAriaTalk",
  "text": "Orym: Doesn't matter if it's women or children,[p/] Lucio Steelwind will kill them all the same."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bd77c",
  "node": "OrymAriaTalk",
  "text": "Orym: A bunch of my men quit after that.[p/] They couldn't stomach working for a monster like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:081506c",
  "node": "OrymAriaTalk",
  "text": "Tyrion: What about you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07462a0",
  "node": "OrymAriaTalk",
  "text": "Orym: ...We all gotta get paid somehow. [h=\"Not like I can do anything...|He's basically a duke...\" e=\"saf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0adf4ea",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Kid, you already showed this thing to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:057a4db",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah![p/] It’s an Attorney’s Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cb2c9",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: ...I know. [h=\"He looks like a little kid|showing his mom a drawing.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bd627",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "I cleared my throat as I stowed the Runestone back in my jacket."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ce68d",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: I never knew you were Tymora’s kid.[p/] I always figured you were her intern or something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c99d79",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She doesn’t really talk about it that much."
}

{
  "id": "line:07142b2",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: I've only ever seen her in court.[p/] It's hard to picture a woman like that raising a kid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bca75d",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": ":There wasn’t much to picture.[p/] She raised me the same way she built a case:[p/] sternly,[p/] stoicly,[p/] and always in control."
}

{
  "id": "line:013c459",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: I never expected a mercenary to look like that,[p/] but after seeing how many men it took to arrest her,[p/] I can kind of see it."
}

{
  "id": "line:070fb82",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: What the hell are they feeding that girl?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c39e9",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Bear meat,[p/] from what I’ve seen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0354fda",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Huh...[p/] I guess that makes sense.[p/] You are what you eat. [h=\"I wonder if we can get bear meat|in the Inquisition’s mess hall.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0721e19",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Aria"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a76427",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": ":Autopsy Report: Flinhart McCoy"
}

{
  "id": "line:05dc08e",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Autopsy Report seems to be pretty detailed in some aspects and vague in others.[p/] Why is that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b3951",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: The autopsies are created using [b]divination[/b] magic.[p/] Those spells give us details about how someone died."
}

{
  "id": "line:049d42c",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: There's always a few blind spots, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:0656bef",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Blind spots?[p/] Like what?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5f0ca",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Well,[p/] for one thing,[p/] their magic only tells us the exact time and cause of death.[p/] Everything else can get muddied depending on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:079a177",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I suppose the report can get confusing if someone manipulates the body after death."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d74d1",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah,[p/] I guess this whole trial has proved that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0891929",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Which meant it would be that much harder to figure out what originally killed Flinhart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f10f3b",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Celeste's Sword"
}

{
  "id": "line:08cd09a",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: The girl's sword is really strange.[p/] It's almost a shame that we had to confiscate it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c830e2",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is it really that abnormal?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed7802",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: It's definitely not made out of steel.[p/] It’s almost like a rock or something."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fa187",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: I tried to ask her where she got it,[p/] but she told me I should take it and stick it right up my—"
}

{
  "id": "line:01453e6",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thanks,[p/] I get the picture."
}

{
  "id": "line:08dd1b1",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Celeste's Spell Compendium"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d67bff",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've never seen a real Spell Compendium before.[p/] I'm still not exactly sure how they work."
}

{
  "id": "line:035aee4",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: They’re magical devices that show us which spells a mage can cast."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9883b",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: That tells us exactly what spells a mage has.[p/] The Inquisition uses these things all the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4910b",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right.[p/] Having that information must be a blessing for the defense and the prosecution."
}

{
  "id": "line:09468ee",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Crime Scene Map (McCoy Tavern)"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f49974",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: Prosecutor Steelwind is going into a lot of detail for her case."
}

{
  "id": "line:051258b",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Bah...[p/] It's a real headache."
}

{
  "id": "line:078519a",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Did you know that this map is [i]scaled[/i]?[p/] It's got a legend and everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c13bf",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "The Inquisition’s mistake must have really bothered her.[p/] Is she worried about her reputation?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2b5a3",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Broken Power Cell"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb8607",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: This place has been without power for about a week."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c3a49",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: They've been using candles to keep the place lit."
}

{
  "id": "line:064a610",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: This is exactly why you can't rely on magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0891633",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Shattered Bottle of Lotus Juice"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b0208",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: I wonder what \"Lotus Juice\" is..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b94da",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: It's not any drink that I've heard of.[p/] It must be some kind of foreign brand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8a180",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: I wonder how they got their hands on something like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e16ed",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:026171a",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "Orym: Uh...[p/] I don't know what you're expecting me to say."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a8e74",
  "node": "Tavern_Present",
  "text": "...It'd be best to try something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0373fa3",
  "node": "TavernDeduce",
  "text": "I’d found everything that I could in the dining area,[p/] but what did it all mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8041f",
  "node": "TavernDeduce",
  "text": "No other murder weapon was found,[p/] and there wasn’t any evidence of another person at the scene either..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de0364",
  "node": "TavernDeduce",
  "text": "I only knew about the anonymous witness who discovered the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f3df7",
  "node": "TavernDeduce",
  "text": "Orym: Hey...[p/] You okay, kid?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2bcfe",
  "node": "TavernDeduce",
  "text": "Once again,[p/] I let everything else disappear from the world."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c34ab",
  "node": "TavernDeduce",
  "text": "Orym: ...You listening?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eed854",
  "node": "TavernDeduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: There’s no clear evidence pointing to another killer.[p/] There is,[p/] however,[p/] evidence pointing to whether or not Flinhart moved when he was attacked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc2577",
  "node": "TavernDeduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: There’s no blood trail leading to or from the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:051a12a",
  "node": "TavernDeduce",
  "text": "Tyrion: That fact implies something about the location of Flinhart's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a85376",
  "node": "TavernDeduce1",
  "text": "0"
}

{
  "id": "line:03bacb9",
  "node": "TavernDeduce1",
  "text": "Fail"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d4859",
  "node": "TavernDeduce1",
  "text": "No...[p/] I didn't see a blood trail leading from Flinhart's body.[p/] That told me something important."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b4c9e",
  "node": "TavernDeduce1",
  "text": "Namely,[p/] where Flinhart was throughout the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2b1ae",
  "node": "TavernDeduce1b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Flinhart died where he was attacked.[p/] He didn’t move from his position at all.[p/] He might’ve even died instantaneously."
}

{
  "id": "line:070becf",
  "node": "TavernDeduce1b",
  "text": "Orym: Um...[p/] Yeah,[p/] I guess that makes sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddb52a",
  "node": "TavernDeduce1b",
  "text": "Tyrion: There’s also the Autopsy Report,[p/] which says that he died from a stab from behind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2cab3",
  "node": "TavernDeduce1b",
  "text": "Tyrion: He must’ve been facing away from his attacker."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c9b03",
  "node": "TavernDeduce1b",
  "text": "Tyrion: He was probably caught off-guard,[p/] and he would’ve been in shock and too incapacitated to move."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2e7b6",
  "node": "TavernDeduce1b",
  "text": "Tyrion: It also doesn’t look like his body was dragged anywhere either.[p/] He was definitely attacked right where this chalk outline is."
}

{
  "id": "line:03dc06c",
  "node": "TavernDeduce1b",
  "text": "Tyrion: There’s also the shattered bottle of “Lotus Juice”."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2b64c",
  "node": "TavernDeduce1b",
  "text": "Tyrion: The fragments are right next to the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa6ac3",
  "node": "TavernDeduce1b",
  "text": "Tyrion: The bottle must have only been shattered hours ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:00002f5",
  "node": "TavernDeduce2",
  "text": "No...[p/] I already knew that Flinhart died where he stood,[p/] and the shattered bottle was right next to his body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0560d33",
  "node": "TavernDeduce2",
  "text": "Which means that Flinhart must’ve been holding it at some point."
}

{
  "id": "line:0713bc0",
  "node": "TavernDeduce2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Flinhart dropped the bottle exactly when he was attacked.[p/] Which implies that he was holding it when the attack occurred."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df8f62",
  "node": "TavernDeduce2b",
  "text": "Orym: What’s so strange about that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d212e",
  "node": "TavernDeduce2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: These details may seem insignificant,[p/] but together,[p/] they’ll give me a better idea of what the board looked like."
}

{
  "id": "line:059ddc8",
  "node": "TavernDeduce2b",
  "text": "Orym: The “board”...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0063cf9",
  "node": "TavernDeduce2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: There’s also the fact that the lights were out.[p/] Were these candles here when you arrived at the crime scene, Orym?"
}

{
  "id": "line:067ba96",
  "node": "TavernDeduce2b",
  "text": "Orym: No. We had to light some so we could see the crime scene properly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abed8b",
  "node": "TavernDeduce2b",
  "text": "Orym: We thought it was weird too.[p/] The girl and her father must’ve had their argument in the dark."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe6f40",
  "node": "TavernDeduce2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: So, they didn’t light any candles to make up for the broken lights..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f52af7",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3",
  "text": "No...[p/] The candles were lit by the Inquisition after they came to investigate the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:011dc76",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3",
  "text": "Furthermore,[p/] the dining room lights haven’t been operational for the last week."
}

{
  "id": "line:044f0df",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3",
  "text": "It might've been a strange conclusion to draw,[p/] but this could only mean one thing about the room’s lighting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0897946",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "Tyrion: If there was any lighting during the attack,[p/] it could have been produced by the murderer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a75e15",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "I could slowly see the position of the pieces,[p/] but there were still areas I was unsure of."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6902b",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "Tyrion: They might have used a torch or a lantern of some kind."
}

{
  "id": "line:079e4dd",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Additionally,[p/] the argument that Celeste had with Flinhart must have been sparked by something.[p/] Things seemed fine between them before I went to bed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3e6d2",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was spontaneous.[p/] They weren’t planning to have a conversation in this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:028f957",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "Orym: Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04bcdd9",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "Tyrion: In this darkness,[p/] Flinhart wouldn’t have a lot of visibility.[p/] He probably never saw the attack coming.[p/] He would’ve been surprised and in too much shock to run away."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fb56a",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "Orym: Kid...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:068e32c",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "Tyrion: The bottle may seem insignificant,[p/] but he was holding it when he was attacked.[p/] Was he pouring a drink for himself or a visitor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:077e2b1",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "Orym: Kid!"
}

{
  "id": "line:082a1a9",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "I was in a frenzy,[p/] but the commander snapped me back to reality."
}

{
  "id": "line:012f90c",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "Orym: What was that all about?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0017bea",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Sorry.[p/] I just get lost in my head sometimes..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0432f63",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah, well...[p/] Cut it out.[p/] You were mumbling like a crazy person."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecce07",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]right.[p/] Sorry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0848956",
  "node": "TavernDeduce3b",
  "text": "It felt like I’d found everything I could here.[p/] It was time to MOVE somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed995c",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hi, Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f09c35",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Ruby: Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0666f37",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...How did the investigation go?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2ba08",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I feel more prepared at the very least."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b62778",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don’t know exactly what happened,[p/] but I have a clearer picture of the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d9c94",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Ruby: What did you find out?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0852648",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Ruby: So...[p/] There are still no clues directly pointing to another suspect..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f0449",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Ruby: Have you been able to coax any new details from McCoy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7c362",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Tyrion: She’s already told me everything she knows."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3f223",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Tyrion: She’s not the one who killed Flinhart, Ms. Tymora.[p/] I’m sure of that now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0915ace",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...You trust people far too easily, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cdd5d",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You say that like it’s a bad thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f12d91",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Ruby: It's going to get you hurt one of these days.[p/] People are never as innocent as they appear."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a3128",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Does that include you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e88a33",
  "node": "Trial2",
  "text": "Ruby: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0ee3c",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Commander White had a lot of things to say about you.[p/] Should I have listened to him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7aa23",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "Ruby: ...What are you trying to say?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0596e70",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’m saying that I’ve never believed the rumors about you,[p/] not for a second."
}

{
  "id": "line:0966256",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: You saved me when I had nothing,[p/] and taught me how to fight against the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc2621",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Everyone told me that you were a criminal.[p/] I wouldn’t be here right now if I’d listened to them."
}

{
  "id": "line:08085e5",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "Ruby: Cuthbert..."
}

{
  "id": "line:009805c",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’m not going to stop trying to see the best in people."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fd568",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste is innocent,[p/] and I’ll prove that to everyone, including you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f657c8",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "Ruby: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] You can be really stubborn sometimes.[p/] You know that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0085894",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: I get it from you."
}

{
  "id": "line:067acb0",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "That seemed to get a chuckle out of her."
}

{
  "id": "line:046e4bb",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "Ruby: I wish I could see the world the way you do, Cuthbert,[p/] but the truth isn't always what you want it to be."
}

{
  "id": "line:004c10f",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know,[p/] but I'm not going to let that change me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0248b32",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "I took a deep breath and readied myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf1f83",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "I was approaching the endgame now.[p/] All I had to do was move the final pieces into place and end this once and for all."
}

{
  "id": "line:079e5e9",
  "node": "Trial2b",
  "text": "The bailiff led Celeste into the courtroom,[p/] and I followed closely behind them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5f171",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "Judge: Court is now resumed for the trial of Celeste McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ebbbf",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "Judge: Let us review the proceedings from yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f226d",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "Judge: The defense presented some...[p/] unfortunate oversights made during the investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ec967",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "AriaC: I personally saw to it that the crime scene was thoroughly inspected this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bdcb2",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "Judge: ...I see.[p/] I suppose that puts my mind at ease if nothing else."
}

{
  "id": "line:02237cd",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "AriaC: At yesterday’s trial,[p/] we found an inconsistency between the crime scene photo and the Autopsy Report."
}

{
  "id": "line:0878be2",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "AriaC: Because of this,[p/] the defense argued that a third party must have interfered with the crime scene to frame the defendant."
}

{
  "id": "line:082217b",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "AriaC: To clear any doubts you may have,[p/] the individual who discovered the body has decided to testify today."
}

{
  "id": "line:041d054",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "Judge: Really?[p/] It was my understanding that they wanted to remain anonymous."
}

{
  "id": "line:0550734",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "AriaC: The witness in question was within the gallery of the trial yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba730b",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "AriaC: After yesterday’s proceedings,[p/] he felt that he couldn’t stay silent any longer."
}

{
  "id": "line:022d80c",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "Judge: Very well.[p/] Let’s hear from this witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:077b59a",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "Judge: Witness,[p/] please state your name and occupation for the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edb189",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "Rhys: My name is Rhys Reginald Rudolf.[p/] I am a chauffeur."
}

{
  "id": "line:0720acf",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "Rudolf appeared to be writing something in a notebook."
}

{
  "id": "line:039d1c6",
  "node": "Trial2c",
  "text": "His pen glided across the page,[p/] filling line after line within seconds."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9c0f3",
  "node": "Trial2d",
  "text": "Judge: ...Mr. Rudolf?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0566bb0",
  "node": "Trial2d",
  "text": "Rhys: Ah...[p/] Forgive me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a86335",
  "node": "Trial2d",
  "text": "Rhys: I was merely recording everyone present in this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d1376",
  "node": "Trial2d",
  "text": "Judge: ...You’re taking notes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e71bd9",
  "node": "Trial2d",
  "text": "Rhys: I always keep clear and detailed records of my actions each day."
}

{
  "id": "line:05699ce",
  "node": "Trial2d",
  "text": "Rhys: I’ve found that ordering the present naturally brings order to the future."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfcfaf",
  "node": "Trial2d",
  "text": "Judge: ...With such detailed records,[p/] your testimony about the defendant must be thorough indeed."
}

{
  "id": "line:07543ff",
  "node": "Trial2d",
  "text": "Rhys: Actually,[p/] I witnessed much more than just the defendant."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d7997",
  "node": "Trial2d",
  "text": "Rhys: I saw the crime as it was being committed,[p/] and I wrote down everything that I witnessed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0dea6",
  "node": "Trial2d",
  "text": "Judge: If what you're saying is true,[p/] why have you waited until now to testify?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d556e",
  "node": "Trial2d",
  "text": "AriaC: We had initially concluded that the evidence alone was decisive enough."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af66f0",
  "node": "Trial2d",
  "text": "AriaC: We saw no need for Mr. Rudolf to testify.[p/] However,[p/] that clearly changed after yesterday’s trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d23b4b",
  "node": "Trial2d",
  "text": "There was no way the prosecution wouldn’t use eyewitness testimony from the start.[p/] There had to be another reason why he didn’t take the stand yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2f774",
  "node": "Trial2d",
  "text": "Judge: Very well.[p/] Mr. Rudolf,[p/] please testify to the court about what you saw that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0943fb6",
  "node": "Trial2e",
  "text": "Rhys: We were driving by the McCoy Tavern when we heard a disturbance.[p/] This occurred at 1:08 AM."
}

{
  "id": "line:038e0bc",
  "node": "Trial2e",
  "text": "Rhys: She pulled her sword from Flinhart’s back.[p/] As he turned to face her,[p/][s/] she stabbed him again in his chest!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d91be",
  "node": "Trial2e",
  "text": "Rhys: She soon realized that I had witnessed her heinous crime.[p/] She dropped her weapon,[p/] still impaled in Flinhart,[p/] and fled the scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0742a89",
  "node": "Trial2e",
  "text": "Judge: Incredible![p/] If everything occurred as the witness described,[p/] then I see no room for debate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0549a3f",
  "node": "Trial2e",
  "text": "AriaC: Of course,[p/] the evidence has always been irrefutable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe646a",
  "node": "Trial2e",
  "text": "I didn’t remember seeing another carriage when I left to look for Celeste,[p/] but it was pretty dark.[p/] I could've just missed him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7b007",
  "node": "Trial2e",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] did you see him when you left the tavern?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bace34",
  "node": "Trial2e",
  "text": "Celeste: No.[p/] I don’t think I’ve ever even met him before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9c210",
  "node": "Trial2e",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Does that mean what I think it means?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d37fbc",
  "node": "Trial2e",
  "text": "Tyrion: We shouldn’t jump to conclusions,[p/] but if he testified that you saw him,[p/] he’s clearly lying."
}

{
  "id": "line:090a2f9",
  "node": "Trial2e",
  "text": "I just needed to find out why."
}

{
  "id": "line:079fb27",
  "node": "Trial2e",
  "text": "Judge: The defense may now begin their cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4d9ec",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Who was the passenger in your carriage?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0caef48",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Rhys: Ah...[p/] well—"
}

{
  "id": "line:03aca3e",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "AriaC: The identity of the passenger is irrelevant.[p/] The current witness is the person who observed the crime."
}

{
  "id": "line:068b3d2",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: If there was another person at the scene,[p/] they may also have crucial testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d182b4",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "AriaC: The passenger is under no obligation to testify before the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:066d749",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "AriaC: The current witness’s account of the events is more than adequate."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ed598",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Judge: I agree.[p/] I see no reason for Mr. Rudolf to disclose the identity of his client."
}

{
  "id": "line:0009d80",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Rhys: We were driving by the McCoy Tavern when we heard a disturbance. This occurred at 1:08 AM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cef9b7",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can I assume this “disturbance\" was the argument between my client and her father?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09698b2",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Rhys: Yes.[p/] I heard two distinct voices:[p/] one young woman and an older man."
}

{
  "id": "line:004be36",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Right...[p/] That also matched up with what the neighbors heard."
}

{
  "id": "line:043071d",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "AriaC: What did you do after hearing this disturbance, Mr. Rudolf?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d142d4",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Rhys: Worried that something was amiss, I walked into the establishment to see what the commotion was about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a47ae6",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: You stopped your carriage in the middle of a job?[p/] What did your passenger think of this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5a043",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Rhys: He took no issue with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e837c0",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: What kind of passenger would be okay with stopping mid-drive?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05fe098",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "AriaC: The passenger’s thoughts on the matter are irrelevant to his testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a72c8",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "AriaC: ...Unless you have any hard evidence to prove otherwise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0404901",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "She objected whenever I brought up the passenger.[p/] There was something more there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0003f00",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "AriaC: Now then.[p/] Please tell us what you saw in the establishment, Mr. Rudolf."
}

{
  "id": "line:000f10a",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Rhys: That was when I saw the defendant, lit by the blue glow of the dining room lights! She had stabbed Flinhart, her sword shining with magical energy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09c2f35",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: You sound certain that you saw my client and the victim.[p/] How were you so sure it was them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e24127",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Rhys: Flinhart McCoy and his daughter were well known within the town."
}

{
  "id": "line:053c8f6",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Rhys: Flinhart made himself quite known in the region through his... social activism."
}

{
  "id": "line:06eaf0b",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Rhys: And young Celeste tends to stand out whenever she walks through the streets."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f6bd1",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Is he hitting on me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09bcb9a",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: It does make sense.[p/] You don’t really look like the average commoner."
}

{
  "id": "line:034c2dc",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Celeste: Are [i]you[/i] hitting on me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec4ff3",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Be serious..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4a105",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] Mr. Rudolf,[p/] do you live in Kornhaven?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a37e6f",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Rhys: I don’t live there,[p/] but my work brings me into town quite frequently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d41cb6",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "AriaC: The witness’s place of residence has no bearing on his testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc04b9",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "AriaC: What matters is that he was there when the murder occurred."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d26625",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "...Steelwind kept deflecting questions about his life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0749cb1",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Rhys: She pulled her sword from Flinhart’s back. As he turned to face her, she stabbed him again in his chest!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0698778",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: So, you’re saying that my defendant stabbed him twice with her sword?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f174bf",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Rhys: Y-[p/][s/]Yes...[p/] That’s exactly what I saw."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b66b87",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: There’s only one visible wound on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0856a1d",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: If what you say is true,[p/] then that means that she stabbed him through the same wound.[p/] Isn’t that extremely improbable?"
}

{
  "id": "line:021ac83",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "AriaC: Improbable,[p/] but not impossible. It may be strange,[p/] but that’s what the witness saw happen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0712e4e",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "She was reaching with that,[p/] but I wouldn’t get anywhere unless I could [i]prove[/i] he was lying."
}

{
  "id": "line:069e704",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Rhys: She soon realized that I had witnessed her heinous crime. She dropped her weapon, still impaled in Flinhart, and fled the scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6f90b",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: You supposedly witnessed a murder,[p/] and you let the perpetrator get away?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f6c52",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Rhys: I’m just a simple carriage driver.[p/] I have no way of combating an armed assailant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0119322",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "AriaC: The witness also saw the defendant using magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d2195",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "AriaC: Would you really expect a chauffeur to subdue an armed mercenary?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0233520",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: I guess not..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0118a4f",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: He probably came up with a detailed story beforehand and wrote everything down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0739f23",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: His quirk is the perfect cover for him to read over his notes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0363030",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Celeste: It’ll probably be hard to catch him lying if he has a way to keep his story straight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0208954",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s actually just the opposite."
}

{
  "id": "line:0301f0c",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: With this many details,[p/] it will be that much easier to find an inconsistency."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d49aeb",
  "node": "RhysCross",
  "text": "I just needed to find it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef69c6",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rudolf,[p/] you testified that you saw my client murdering the victim."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c5656",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: And you supposedly saw her casting magic while doing so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbdaa4",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Rhys: Yes...[p/] I could never forget such a grisly sight.[p/] That moment was burned into my memory."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2a9c4",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I see...[p/] Well, it’s funny that you say that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1f7ac",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Rhys: ...What makes you say that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f53e1a",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "AriaC: Are you accusing the witness of perjury?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d214c1",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "AriaC: Surely you know that such accusations can't be made lightly, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0310391",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Steelwind,[p/] the dining room lights are artificery devices that are powered by an arcane power cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:07eb048",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: However,[p/] that same arcane power cell was broken during the time of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e6bd8",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Those lights had no energy,[p/][s/] and the room would’ve been pitch black!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a40741",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: The witness couldn’t have seen [i]anything[/i], much less a homicide!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e9c7e",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Rhys: W-[p/][s/]Wait![p/][s/] I can explain!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f10b2",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "AriaC: There’s no need, witness.[p/] You could have easily seen another source of light."
}

{
  "id": "line:0970a05",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "AriaC: The McCoys probably lit a candle or lantern because of the blackout."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e53629",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: The witness clearly described a source of “[i]blue[/i] light\"![p/][s/] A rudimentary candle or lantern wouldn’t emit a color like that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:072d4d4",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "AriaC: Then the witness was clearly mistaken."
}

{
  "id": "line:04235d4",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: The witness records everything he sees in his notebook!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0418d76",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: He even remembers the exact time that this encounter occurred!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc36b1",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: So why would he be incorrect about such a clear and obvious detail?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0869da9",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] What the witness saw was some form of magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:023388c",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Due to the lack of power,[p/][s/] it [i]couldn’t[/i] have been artificery![p/][s/] It must have been an arcane spell!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae70d5",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Rhys: That’s it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:082f51b",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Judge: Witness?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3fda9",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Rhys: I was mistaken about something![p/][s/] Please allow me to revise my testimony!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00867e6",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Judge: ...Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] what are your thoughts?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d601a8",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: If he thinks he saw something different,[p/] then it's only fair to hear him out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e314cc",
  "node": "RhysObj",
  "text": "It didn’t matter.[p/] No matter what he came up with,[p/] I’d tear through each of his lies."
}

{
  "id": "line:073bb01",
  "node": "RhysTestimony2",
  "text": "Rhys: I remember now![p/][s/] Yesterday,[p/] they said that Flinhart was killed using magic, yes?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0be4349",
  "node": "RhysTestimony2",
  "text": "Rhys: I must have seen Ms. McCoy channeling a magic spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0960057",
  "node": "RhysTestimony2",
  "text": "Rhys: The spell was called “[b]Mage Blade[/b]\",[p/] wasn’t it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:085562d",
  "node": "RhysTestimony2",
  "text": "Rhys: That’s it![p/] The blue glow that I saw was created by [b]Mage Blade[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a553aa",
  "node": "RhysTestimony2",
  "text": "Judge: Hm...[p/] I see.[p/] So the “blue light\" that you saw came from the defendant’s magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:005015e",
  "node": "RhysTestimony2",
  "text": "Judge: Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] you may proceed with your cross-examination."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e2c8c",
  "node": "RhysTestimony2",
  "text": "Tyrion: With pleasure."
}

{
  "id": "line:037e37a",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you changing your testimony based on yesterday’s trial?"
}

{
  "id": "line:051205f",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Rhys: No![p/][s/] That’s not what this is!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e42a5f",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Rhys: It’s just that after thinking about it,[p/][s/] I finally understood what I saw!"
}

{
  "id": "line:005334a",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wouldn’t that be pretty noticeable and distinct?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09228ef",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "AriaC: The crime took place in a village of farmers,[p/] and the defendant’s magic wasn’t known to many until that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c819f",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "AriaC: What reason would the witness have to think that he was witnessing magic?"
}

{
  "id": "line:011828e",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "AriaC: He would just think that the sword was wreathed in a glow by some other means."
}

{
  "id": "line:0458a38",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "That last part was a bit far-fetched,[p/] but I’d need something concrete to refute it."
}

{
  "id": "line:032f438",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Rhys: The spell was called “[b]Mage Blade[/b]\", yes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b964df",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You seem uncertain about the spell you saw."
}

{
  "id": "line:0139dd6",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Tyrion: How can we trust the rest of your testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03b83e9",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "AriaC: It doesn’t matter if he was unable to identify the specific spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b69ac7",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "AriaC: The only thing that matters is that he saw it happen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f33315",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "I wouldn’t get anywhere unless I could PRESENT a clear contradiction."
}

{
  "id": "line:015b8ac",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Rhys: That’s it! The blue glow that I saw was created by [b]Mage Blade[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8a217",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You still don’t sound so sure of it yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:069f8f4",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Rhys: I-[p/][s/]I wasn’t sure of it at first."
}

{
  "id": "line:00386d7",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Rhys: But then I remembered that they found traces of magic at the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de4aab",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Rhys: I didn’t realize I was looking at a magic spell.[p/] Is it really so hard to believe?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0caecbd",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I suppose not."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edd44c",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Not that I actually believed him."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b01e9",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Celeste: He just keeps telling lie after lie..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b9b7b",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "She was trying to keep her composure,[p/] but her fists were firmly clenched."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fab0d6",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He’s trying to cover up his mistake.[p/] I’m sure he’s just making things up on the spot now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5c3f7",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Celeste: He doesn’t know how magic works.[p/] I bet he barely understands what [b]Mage Blade[/b] even does."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e075e",
  "node": "RhysCross2",
  "text": "Which meant that there had to be a flaw with his testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f8d19",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rudolf,[p/] you don’t know much about magic, do you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:009a9fb",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Rhys: Of course not![p/] Are you trying to say that I should have recognized Celeste's [b]Mage Blade[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab1651",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] I admit that you probably wouldn’t know what [b]Mage Blade[b/] looks like..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a27349",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But that’s exactly where you made your mistake!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0905e85",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Rhys: M-[p/][s/]My mistake?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0737d84",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rudolf,[p/] if you were aware of how [b]Mage Blade[/b] works,[p/] then you would know that the spell emits a [i]yellow[/i] radiant glow."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c47e5",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which means the “blue glow\" you saw couldn’t have possibly been [b]Mage Blade[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:036737c",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: This is ridiculous.[p/] What’s the significance of seeing a blue glow instead of a yellow one?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0927b1b",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s extremely significant, Prosecutor!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1df95",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: If the witness saw a blue magical glow,[p/][s/] then he must have witnessed a [i]different[/i] spell at the scene!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d573ad",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Preposterous![p/][s/] You don’t have any evidence to support that claim!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c9cc8",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That blue light made a large impression on the witness!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf76f5",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He wrote it down in his notebook![p/][s/] He even mentioned the color in [i]both[/i] of his testimonies!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0383718",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I find it hard to believe that he’d be mistaken about something like that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2cd41",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: So, what did you see, Mr. Rudolf?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f9d80",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you see my client at the scene,[p/][s/] casting a spell that she couldn’t possibly cast?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcb192",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Or did you actually see [i]another[/i] mage at the scene?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d444b",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Rhys: Um...[p/][s/] W-[p/][s/]Well..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0017a87",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: Your Honor![p/][s/] The defense is completely out of line!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02fe1e1",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let me remind you that perjury is a crime, Rudolf!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7bbfd",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you are found to have lied in your testimony,[p/][s/] I will personally see to it that you’re prosecuted!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a0f2e",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Rhys: N-[p/][s/]No![p/][s/] Wait!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0877384",
  "node": "RhysObj2",
  "text": "Garrick: Now that is quite enough of that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0892875",
  "node": "RhysObj2b",
  "text": "Garrick Pierce had stood up from within the gallery and walked to the witness stand,[p/] shoving Rudolf out of his way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f73e8c",
  "node": "RhysObj2b",
  "text": "He’d broken several laws with that one act alone,[p/] but no one moved to stop him."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a8273",
  "node": "RhysObj2b",
  "text": "The bailiff looked to the judge wearily and awaited instruction."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac64f8",
  "node": "RhysObj2b",
  "text": "The judge said nothing.[p/] His eyes simply narrowed as he waited for Pierce’s next move."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e7a41",
  "node": "RhysObj2b",
  "text": "AriaC: Pierce![p/][s/] There is no need for you to take the stand!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0783c3c",
  "node": "RhysObj2b",
  "text": "Garrick: Nonsense,[p/] I have nothing to hide."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bcd30",
  "node": "RhysObj2b",
  "text": "Garrick: I will not stand idly by while your case falls apart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d93014",
  "node": "RhysObj2b",
  "text": "It seemed that for the first time,[p/] the Prosecutor had lost control of the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aef58e",
  "node": "RhysObj2b",
  "text": "Judge: ...What is the meaning of this, Ms. Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09bf6d0",
  "node": "RhysObj2b",
  "text": "AriaC: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] This is Garrick Pierce, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acf0cb",
  "node": "RhysObj2b",
  "text": "Garrick: I am the honorable lord of Kornhaven and many other villages in that region."
}

{
  "id": "line:0481cc3",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Garrick: I’m afraid I must apologize.[p/] These...[p/] misunderstandings have been entirely my fault."
}

{
  "id": "line:0734562",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Judge: What do you mean, Lord Pierce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0184392",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Garrick: You see...[p/] Rudolf was not the one who witnessed the crime that fateful night."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f67b6f",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Garrick: It was me.[p/] I was the one who saw that gruesome attack.[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e73ef1",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Garrick: I had my driver report the body so that I could remain anonymous."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7d72f",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you saying that you had Rudolf [i]lie[/i] for you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03871a1",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Garrick: I simply dictated to him what I saw and had him repeat that to law enforcement."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bf4b6",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Garrick: With what's been in the news lately, [p/] it simply wouldn’t do for a member of the nobility to appear publicly in court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4392c",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Garrick: But alas,[p/] it appears the time for discretion has passed."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e6520",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Judge: Lord Pierce![p/][s/] Regardless of your good intentions,[p/][s/] this is a very clear act of perjury!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc2485",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Garrick: I understand,[p/] and I will accept the consequences of that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c279be",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Garrick: However,[p/] I would be remiss if Rudolf’s shoddy testimony allowed that girl to escape justice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de1b75",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Garrick: Please, Your Honor.[p/] Allow me to testify as to what I saw that night."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b3a1c",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Judge: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:029a8d1",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Judge: Very well.[p/] This is highly irregular,[p/] but I believe the court will benefit from your testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed0b75",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Judge: However,[p/] know that this misconduct will not be without consequences."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f28879",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "Garrick: Very well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0deba43",
  "node": "RhysObj2c",
  "text": "From the look on the lord's face,[p/] it was clear he would only get off with a slap on the wrist."
}

{
  "id": "line:034c667",
  "node": "GarTestimony",
  "text": "Garrick: On the night of the murder,[p/] I found myself unable to sleep.[p/] So, I took a leisurely carriage ride around Kornhaven."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7d11b",
  "node": "GarTestimony",
  "text": "Garrick: I happened to be passing by the McCoy tavern when I heard a loud commotion from within the building."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf9acd",
  "node": "GarTestimony",
  "text": "Garrick: Curious,[p/] I stopped my carriage and took a single step inside the establishment.[p/] That is when I saw the scene inside."
}

{
  "id": "line:023a2cd",
  "node": "GarTestimony",
  "text": "Garrick: I saw the defendant stabbing that poor man with her sword!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0194ad3",
  "node": "GarTestimony",
  "text": "Tyrion: Garrick Pierce...[p/] He’s a member of the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0991ff9",
  "node": "GarTestimony",
  "text": "Celeste: That also means that he’s a mage."
}

{
  "id": "line:068fb10",
  "node": "GarTestimony",
  "text": "Celeste: Does that mean...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06fe2ed",
  "node": "GarTestimony",
  "text": "Tyrion: There’s no doubt about it.[p/] He’s the only other person who could have left those traces of [b]transmutation[/b] at the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:027f93a",
  "node": "GarTestimony",
  "text": "Tyrion: He has to be the mage that we’re looking for."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a3ede",
  "node": "GarTestimony",
  "text": "Celeste: ... [h=\"He killed my Dad...|He's a murderer...\" e=\"as\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0661265",
  "node": "GarTestimony",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Sorry,[p/] this must be a lot for you right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b24c3a",
  "node": "GarTestimony",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Don't worry about me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0436cb4",
  "node": "GarTestimony",
  "text": "Celeste: Just take him down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0208167",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: On the night of the murder, I found myself unable to sleep. So, I took a leisurely carriage ride around Kornhaven."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c4047",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: That seems like a...[p/] strange way to pass the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ab7b6",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Not that I believed him for a second."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ab07d",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "AriaC: The witness’s eccentricities are beside the point."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc581d",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "AriaC: What matters is that he was clearly at the scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e46e00",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: ...I wouldn’t quite put it that way,[p/] however..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a3b95",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’m guessing this “commotion\" was the argument between my client and the victim?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0880ab1",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: One would conclude that. Yes."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f4a5c",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "AriaC: We’ve gone over this point several times,[p/] but their voices were raised loudly during their argument."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e1a77",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "AriaC: It’s not unreasonable to say that the witness heard them from his carriage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0933a58",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: Curious, I stopped my carriage and took a single step inside the establishment. That is when I saw the scene inside!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ac355",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "If he was at the tavern entrance,[p/] then that would mean he would be where the \"W\" token is."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b1a06",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: You saw the entire scene from the entrance?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04808b5",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: It would be quite dark considering that the lights weren’t operational—[p/]even [i]if[/i] my client was using [b]Mage Blade[/b] at the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce4983",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: Ah, of course.[p/] I’d forgotten that detail."
}

{
  "id": "line:0734024",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: I couldn’t see what was happening,[p/] so I used my magic to illuminate the scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e936b",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: You used magic at the crime scene?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ec1ba",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: Yes.[p/] I remember it clearly.[p/] I conjured a blue light to illuminate the scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:0309efa",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: That same blue light must have been what my driver saw."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa75d0",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: I thought that Rudolf didn’t witness the crime at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a2f27",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "AriaC: If I had to guess,[p/] Mr. Rudolf must have seen the blue light from the carriage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d425b5",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "AriaC: Because of that,[p/] he made that detail a part of his testimony earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed55fe",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "That made sense.[p/] Rudolf was so sure that he saw a blue light.[p/] It would’ve been strange if he were lying about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:02479f6",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which spell did you use to illuminate the crime scene?"
}

{
  "id": "line:059fa8e",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: It was the [b]Conjure Light[/b] spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f2399",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor,[p/] if the witness used magic at the crime scene,[p/] then I’d like for his Spell Compendium to be added to the court record."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d805e",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "AriaC: I see no reason to invade the witness’s privacy over a trivial illumination spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0775c04",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Judge: I agree.[p/] The defense will need a stronger reason to requisition the witness’s Spell Compendium."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fddf4",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: Right you are, Your Honor.[p/] Your wisdom is truly fitting of your station."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e32c2",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Oh, shut up..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5e250",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: I used [b]Conjure Light[/b] to illuminate the scene from the tavern entrance. From there, I clearly saw the crime unfold!"
}

{
  "id": "line:041ecf2",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Casting a spell seems like a pretty significant detail to forget."
}

{
  "id": "line:0faf86c",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: For you, maybe,[p/] but for a practiced mage like myself,[p/] using magic is as natural as moving my arm."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aba31e",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "That could be possible...[p/] I use the Eye of Horus so much that I'm barely conscious of it half the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:08363be",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let me guess.[p/] Did she stab him from opposite sides each time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:040899f",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: Yes.[p/] Now that you mention it,[p/] I do recall that happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d50b4",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: Although, I have no idea why she would do that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0089d74",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Garrick: Unless you can prove that she didn’t do exactly what I described?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbbf9d",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: I suppose not..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c47eae",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "At least not yet, anyway..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acbbb5",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Player: Overflow"
}

{
  "id": "line:02886be",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Celeste: He keeps saying that he stood at the entrance the entire time.[p/] That has to be a lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a18055",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] If he stabbed Flinhart,[p/] he would’ve been a lot closer to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0906874",
  "node": "GarrickCross",
  "text": "How would I prove that, though?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbab73",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Pierce,[p/] you said that you illuminated the scene from the tavern entrance?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f750ab",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you take a single step inside the building?"
}

{
  "id": "line:081ad40",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Garrick: Of course not.[p/] I remember it very clearly.[p/] I only stood at the entrance."
}

{
  "id": "line:048f6e3",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then maybe you can help me go over this map of the tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a65240",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Tyrion: If we take a look at this map,[p/] that would place you right here,[p/] where the \"W\" is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c81a91",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Garrick: Of course.[p/] Do I need to repeat myself?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d61b8",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well, I find it interesting that you illuminated the crime scene from all the way back there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0363686",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Considering,[p/] that [b]Conjure Light[/b] only illuminates an area within 15ft of the caster!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a25d8e",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Garrick: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0654a67",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Pierce,[p/] [b]Conjure Light[/b] doesn’t behave like a normal light source!"
}

{
  "id": "line:099487d",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It only provides illumination up to 15ft of the caster!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2df90",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you had stayed at the entrance,[p/][s/] your spell wouldn’t have shown you anything!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0082cbd",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "AriaC: The spell’s range is irrelevant.[p/] We’ve already established that the victim would have been illuminated by [b]Mage Blade[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0811799",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The witness clearly stated that he couldn’t see what was happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0583827",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]That[/i] was why he cast [b]Conjure Light[/b] in the first place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0514d65",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Judge: But what does this mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04fcae9",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Judge: Lord Pierce,[p/] did you illuminate the crime scene or not?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f76e8",
  "node": "GarObj1",
  "text": "Garrick : W-[p/][s/]well,[p/][s/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:021cf3d",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can answer that question for you, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ae5c4",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: The witness [i]did[/i] illuminate the scene of the crime!"
}

{
  "id": "line:032b685",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He illuminated it because he was standing right where it happened!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02142b7",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Judge: ...Mr. Cuthbert?[p/][s/] W-[p/][s/]What are you getting at?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0662445",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] The defense would like to formally accuse Garrick Pierce of murdering Flinhart McCoy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:064df5c",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Garrick: Hold on for a moment![p/][s/] This is absurd!"
}

{
  "id": "line:035f722",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Garrick: I-[p/][s/]I could have easily used a different spell to illuminate the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd7371",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And which spell would that be, Pierce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab9ef6",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Garrick: I-[p/][s/]I...[p/][s/] Uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04bd5a8",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Garrick: The specific spell escapes me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0941181",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Garrick: I’m not sure which one I used now that I think about it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b7310",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: ...You idiot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0111da6",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well, maybe we can figure it out together."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c8e03",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...When you relinquish your Spell Compendium to the court!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5c29a",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Garrick: Steelwind![p/][s/] Say something!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb24dd",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: If you had listened to my instructions,[p/] you wouldn’t be in this situation."
}

{
  "id": "line:052874f",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "AriaC: You’ve made your bed.[p/][s/] Now lie in it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce91a4",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Garrick: Steelwind,[p/][s/] you treacherous-!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c03fb1",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Judge: That’s enough![p/] It appears that the prosecution has no objections."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b20188",
  "node": "GarObj2",
  "text": "Judge: With everything that has occurred,[p/] I’m afraid I must ask Lord Pierce to relinquish his Spell Compendium to the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:00550de",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Celeste: We did it![p/][s/] We got his Spell Compendium!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e1ee5",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "With that,[p/] the case was as good as ours."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a5318",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "...Or was it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08af325",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "She didn’t even try to stop me from taking his Spell Compendium."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3530d",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "I doubted she’d do that just to spite Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:032771f",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor,[p/] I’ve looked at the spells in Lord Pierce’s Compendium."
}

{
  "id": "line:0219f1d",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: [b]Conjure Light[/b] is the only spell that he can cast that would shed a blue light."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a48ef7",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's clear that his testimony and many of his statements were false."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a76f25",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Garrick: ...! [h=\"This little brat!|Such insolence!\" e=\"af\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:049482e",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lord Pierce could very well be a suspect in the murder of Flinhart McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f1b0f",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I’d argue that this presents enough reasonable doubt to acquit the defendant."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ebc95",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Judge: ...Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] I acknowledge that Lord Pierce’s actions are quite suspect."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee8f0a",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Judge: However,[p/] I will not pass a verdict just yet.[p/] There is much more we need to learn."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff231d",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Celeste: What?[p/][s/] That’s not how it works!"
}

{
  "id": "line:056b3a5",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Celeste: We proved that there’s reasonable doubt![p/][s/] That should be enough to acquit me, right?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0820291",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...In a normal case, maybe,[p/] but the situation is different for this trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa68bb",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: The public won’t accept an unsolved homicide involving magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0912c66",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Unless we can unequivocally prove your innocence,[p/] the court will keep drawing things out."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ccde3",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Celeste: What!?[p/] But...[p/][s/] that’s not fair!"
}

{
  "id": "line:012ffc1",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: That’s just how our system works..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8dece",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: The kingdom has always cared more about easing public tension than delivering justice."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c7b9b",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you serious...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0218c10",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Judge: The court will be suspending the trial of Celeste McCoy until further notice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a22505",
  "node": "GarObj3",
  "text": "Judge: We have no choice but to give the Inquisition time to investigate Lord Pierce as a possible suspect."
}

{
  "id": "line:016ea7d",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "AriaC: A “possible suspect\"?[p/] The very idea of that is preposterous, Your Honor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0542cc1",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "What else did she have up her sleeve?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02cba7a",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "AriaC: Let’s revisit the basic facts of this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd1cf6",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "AriaC: Flinhart McCoy was murdered using a blade with a [b]transmutation[/b] spell active on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d07df",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "AriaC: Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] why don’t you tell me the spells that Lord Pierce knows?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e9049",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: His spells are: [b]Prestidigitation[/b], [b]Conjure Light[/b], [b]Conjure Water[/b], [b]Frost Wave[/b], and [b]Shape Liquid[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0910db4",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "Wait a minute..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09dc961",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "AriaC: You’ve realized it too,[p/] haven’t you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a2609",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "AriaC: The witness doesn’t know any [b]transmutation[/b] spells that can be channeled through a solid object!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3b058",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: That can't be right!"
}

{
  "id": "line:028636d",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "Garrick: Ha![p/][s/] You’re right![p/][s/] You’re absolutely right, Steelwind!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0964f91",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "Judge: I see...[p/] If all of that is true,[p/] that would still leave the defendant as the only possible killer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2d138",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "Celeste: But he was the only other mage there![p/][s/] It has to be him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:032683d",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: But he doesn’t know any [b]transmutation[/b] spells that could be cast on your sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:0145804",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: We can’t prove that he stabbed him while using magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:028e47a",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] How did he do it then?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0028d79",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "She was right![p/] How [i]did[/i] he do it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:054f672",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "Since the beginning,[p/] I’d been bothered by the traces of [b]transmutation[/b] magic surrounding Flinhart’s body."
}

{
  "id": "line:00cb67b",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "Originally,[p/] I’d thought that the killer had somehow magically altered the sword and the surrounding wooden floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0228e9b",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "But none of Pierce's spells could do something like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d6ae5",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "Those [b]transmutation[/b] traces were scattered all over the place.[p/] They didn’t even fully cover the sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f0ef4",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "So what if he didn’t use a sword?[p/] What if he used something else?"
}

{
  "id": "line:049224c",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "Judge: The defense did cast some doubt on this witness’s testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a81e93",
  "node": "GarObj4",
  "text": "Judge: Nevertheless,[p/] I must conclude that he could not have possibly committed the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d653e",
  "node": "GarObj5",
  "text": "Judge: With that in mind—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a371ce",
  "node": "GarObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Please wait, Your Honor!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09f01c6",
  "node": "GarObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: We still can’t rule out Pierce as a suspect just yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c720f",
  "node": "GarObj5",
  "text": "Garrick: What are you on about?[p/][s/] Lady Steelwind said it herself!"
}

{
  "id": "line:041a34a",
  "node": "GarObj5",
  "text": "Garrick: I don’t know any spells that can be channeled through a blade!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f475f4",
  "node": "GarObj6",
  "text": "Shape Liquid"
}

{
  "id": "line:07408a8",
  "node": "GarObj6",
  "text": "No...[p/] Pierce didn't have a spell that could be channeled through Celeste's sword."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f264b",
  "node": "GarObj6",
  "text": "Which meant that those traces of [b]transmutation[/b] magic must have come from somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:005bca5",
  "node": "GarObj6",
  "text": "Not only that,[p/] they must have come from the spell that Pierce used to stab Flinhart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0548227",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But you didn’t use a metal blade, did you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfa1ac",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "AriaC: What nonsense is this?[p/] The autopsy report clearly states that the wound was created by a blade."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae0d5b",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "AriaC: If he didn’t channel magic through a blade,[p/] how could he have possibly committed the crime?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0f334",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind,[p/] Garrick Pierce didn’t kill the victim using a sword..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0746900",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: He killed him using an object shaped exactly like a sword!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03b72c5",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "Garrick: ...?! [h=\"No...|Does he know the truth?!\" e=\"fa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:021cfe5",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "AriaC: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0599f23",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "Judge: I’m afraid I don’t quite understand, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:014192a",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor,[p/] I'd like to bring your attention to Pierce’s Spell Compendium."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce5b2e",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Garrick Pierce knows a seemingly insignificant spell called [b]Shape Liquid[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea65a6",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: With it,[p/] he can control any liquid and mold it into any complex shape he wants."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fea7bd",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: He can even freeze it.[p/][s/] Locking that shape in place!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0affa54",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: If he had enough water,[p/][s/] he could create a sword made [i]purely[/i] out of ice!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0184bc9",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "AriaC: No...[p/] Is it possible that he...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01efe97",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you have to say for yourself, \"Lord\" Pierce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d2e92",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "Garrick: ... [h=\"This stubborn little brat!\" e=\"af\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a3402",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "Pierce’s breathing became frantic.[p/] He clearly wasn’t prepared to be backed into a corner like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0319e25",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "I could feel his frustration,[p/] stress,[p/] and fear emanating through the Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf4f95",
  "node": "GarObj7",
  "text": "...The board was set.[p/] I just had to deliver the final blow."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e0e01",
  "node": "Upstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Candle"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3e593",
  "node": "Upstairs_Examine",
  "text": "There were some candles lighting up the hallway.[p/] It looked like they were a part of the old architecture."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c4143",
  "node": "Upstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Several doors led to guest rooms."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed9be5",
  "node": "Upstairs_Examine",
  "text": "Aside from the rooms that Ms. Tymora and I used,[p/] they didn't look like they'd been opened for quite some time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fec79a",
  "node": "Upstairs_Examine",
  "text": "End Door"
}

{
  "id": "line:04db3fa",
  "node": "Upstairs_Examine",
  "text": "There was a door at the end of the hallway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0820d0e",
  "node": "Upstairs_Examine",
  "text": "I saw light from under the door.[p/] Someone was inside."
}

{
  "id": "line:0406dca",
  "node": "Upstairs_Examine",
  "text": "I tried to open the door,[p/] but it seemed to be locked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0355a",
  "node": "Upstairs_Examine",
  "text": "I knocked on the door,[p/] but received no answer in return."
}

{
  "id": "line:073aaec",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "As I made my way up the stairs,[p/] I overheard Steelwind arguing with someone."
}

{
  "id": "line:02cab98",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Aria: If you keep showing your face here,[p/] people will start asking questions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfd5dd",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Aria: I have the investigation under control now.[p/] All you have to do is stay quiet until this is over."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c15d62",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Garrick: You may be a Steelwind,[p/] but this is my land.[p/] I will do as I see fit."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b50f5",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "As I turned down the hallway,[p/] I bumped into what appeared to be a nobleman."
}

{
  "id": "line:042ebcc",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "With a quick motion,[p/] he drew a handkerchief to clean the parts of his clothes that had brushed against me,[p/] his cold gaze hardening into a contemptuous glare."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6e917",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "He gave me the same look he'd probably give to a rotting pile of excrement on the Kornhaven streets."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bc347",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh, sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae259b",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Garrick: Watch where you’re going, you weed."
}

{
  "id": "line:031f820",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Garrick: ...Ah![p/][p/] You're that defense attorney from the trial, aren’t you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d3f0e",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And you are?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef8328",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Garrick: I am Garrick Pierce,[p/] the ruling noble of this land."
}

{
  "id": "line:0940569",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Garrick: I suppose I should thank you for playing your role in the current trial. [h=\"If only you weren’t|such a stubborn nuisance...\" e=\"af\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f0a10",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I suppose that you also believe my client is guilty?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b90c28",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Garrick: I never said that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a05a09",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I'm not wrong, am I?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c77bb",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Garrick: ...It matters not what I believe.[p/] This entire scandal has done nothing but rile up the public."
}

{
  "id": "line:0295780",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Garrick: Magic is a gift for the nobility and the nobility alone.[p/] It is a symbol of our cosmic right to rule."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5775d",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Garrick: Bastards like that girl should know their place."
}

{
  "id": "line:01aff80",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Garrick: This is what happens when the gift of magic is used by those of impure blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:069d4a5",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She's just an innocent woman who got wrapped up in all of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d8826",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Garrick: Ha![p/] I must commend you.[p/] You almost had me fooled."
}

{
  "id": "line:0466d0f",
  "node": "PierceAppears",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Excuse me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0067425",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Garrick: Wait...[p/] Do you actually [i]believe[/i] her little story?"
}

{
  "id": "line:073a184",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What good is a defense attorney if they don't believe in their clients?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f26d26",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Garrick: Scaled Lord...[p/] And here [i]I[/i] took you for another envious commoner,[p/] but you actually [i]believe[/i] that trite."
}

{
  "id": "line:0736069",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Garrick: Are you sure you’re Tymora’s brat?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c07175",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "I knew I had to pick my battles,[p/] but I really weighed the legal consequences of punching him square in the face."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e22b99",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Garrick: Let me tell you something,[p/][s/] [i]boy[/i].[p/] Even if that bastard is innocent,[p/] the charges have been laid and made public."
}

{
  "id": "line:026b506",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Garrick: Someone must take the fall,[p/] lest the public accuse the justice system of corruption."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b965b7",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Garrick: If the King believes there is any unrest here,[p/] even for a moment,[p/] he will unleash Lucio Steelwind and his soldiers upon this region."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1621b",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Garrick: I'm sure you're well aware of what tends to follow after."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1d240",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That doesn't mean my client should be convicted of a crime she didn't commit."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ab041",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Garrick: What is one insignificant girl when compared to the stability and wellbeing of the people in this land?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdba0e",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Garrick: You're far too short-sighted."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ed1e0",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Aria: That's enough.[p/] Stop antagonizing him, Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee9cf2",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "He glanced at the Prosecutor for a moment and then back at me."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cfad4",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "For a moment,[p/] I caught a flicker of fear in his eyes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc12ca",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "I suppose that even House Pierce had reason to fear the Steelwinds."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6457a",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Garrick: Hmph..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de70bb",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Without another word,[p/] he walked down the stairs."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d5775",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Aria: I don’t agree with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:004626a",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Aria: Our system should exist to deliver truth and justice,[p/] not quell public opinion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f26c4c",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...If you really believed that,[p/] you wouldn't be working against my client."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd3732",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you honestly think she's the kind of monster who would murder her own father?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0348fbd",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Aria: ...I’m not so superficial that I’d judge someone based on their appearance."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e6d91",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Aria: The only thing I trust is evidence,[p/] and all of it points to her as the only possible killer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d13c3f",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is that really what you believe?"
}

{
  "id": "line:058b58d",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Or are you just hiding the fact that you're here on your father's behalf?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a535d9",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Aria: I am [i]not[/i] working with my father! [h=\"I'm working against him|just as much as you are!\" e=\"sa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b87243",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "What?[p/] She's working [i]against[/i] her father?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e63e88",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Aria: My apologies.[p/] I don't know what came over me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b961b7",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's fine..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04dbbdd",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Aria: I respect you, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:098e3ce",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "Aria: You should fight according to your own ideals.[p/] Just as I will fight for mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf8b63",
  "node": "PierceAppears2",
  "text": "I tried to think of a retort,[p/] but said nothing as she walked past me."
}
